var book = {
	"name": "Jeremiah",
	"numChapters": 52,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The words of Jeremiah, the son of Hilkiah, one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18948A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18948A\"></sup>of the priests who were in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18948B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18948B\"></sup>Anathoth in the land of Benjamin,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>to whom the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18949C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18949C\"></sup>Josiah the son of Amon, king of Judah, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18949D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18949D\"></sup>the thirteenth year of his reign.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It came also in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18950E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18950E\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18950F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18950F\"></sup>until the end of the eleventh year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18950G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18950G\"></sup>Zedekiah, the son of Josiah, king of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18950H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18950H\"></sup>until the captivity of Jerusalem in the fifth month.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18952I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18952I\"></sup>“Before I formed you in the womb I knew you,and before you were born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18952J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18952J\"></sup>I consecrated you;I appointed you a prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18952K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18952K\"></sup>to the nations.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I said, “Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18953L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18953L\"></sup>I do not know how to speak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18953M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18953M\"></sup>for I am only a youth.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,“Do not say, ‘I am only a youth’;for to all to whom I send you, you shall go,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18954N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18954N\"></sup>whatever I command you, you shall speak.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18955O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18955O\"></sup>Do not be afraid of them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18955P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18955P\"></sup>for I am with you to deliver you,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18956Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18956Q\"></sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> put out his hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18956R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18956R\"></sup>touched my mouth. And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me,“Behold, I have put <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18956S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18956S\"></sup>my words in your mouth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>See, I have set you this day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18957T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18957T\"></sup>over nations and over kingdoms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18957U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18957U\"></sup>to pluck up and to break down,to destroy and to overthrow,to build and to plant.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18958V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18958V\"></sup>“Jeremiah, what do you see?” And I said, “I see an almond branch.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “You have seen well, for I am watching over my word to perform it.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me a second time, saying, “What do you see?” And I said, “I see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18960W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18960W\"></sup>a boiling pot, facing away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18960X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18960X\"></sup>from the north.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18961Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18961Y\"></sup>“Out of the north disaster shall be let loose upon all the inhabitants of the land.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18962Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18962Z\"></sup>I am calling all the tribes of the kingdoms of the north, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18962AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18962AA\"></sup>and they shall come, and every one shall set his throne at the entrance of the gates of Jerusalem, against all its walls all around and against all the cities of Judah.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18963AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18963AB\"></sup>I will declare my judgments against them, for all their evil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18963AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18963AC\"></sup>in forsaking me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18963AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18963AD\"></sup>They have made offerings to other gods and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18963AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18963AE\"></sup>worshiped the works of their own hands.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18964AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18964AF\"></sup>dress yourself for work; arise, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18964AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18964AG\"></sup>say to them everything that I command you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18964AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18964AH\"></sup>Do not be dismayed by them, lest I dismay you before them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And I, behold, I make you this day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18965AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18965AI\"></sup>a fortified city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18965AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18965AJ\"></sup>an iron pillar, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18965AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18965AK\"></sup>bronze walls, against the whole land, against the kings of Judah, its officials, its priests, and the people of the land.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18966AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18966AL\"></sup>They will fight against you, but they shall not prevail against you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18966AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18966AM\"></sup>I am with you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, to deliver you.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go and proclaim in the hearing of Jerusalem, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I remember the devotion of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18968A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18968A\"></sup>your youth,your love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18968B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18968B\"></sup>as a bride,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18968C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18968C\"></sup>how you followed me in the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18968D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18968D\"></sup>in a land not sown.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18969E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18969E\"></sup>Israel was holy to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18969F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18969F\"></sup>the firstfruits of his harvest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18969G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18969G\"></sup>All who ate of it incurred guilt;disaster came upon them,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O house of Jacob, and all the clans of the house of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18971H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18971H\"></sup>“What wrong did your fathers find in methat they went far from me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18971I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18971I\"></sup>and went after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18971J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18971J\"></sup>worthlessness, and became worthless?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They did not say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18972K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18972K\"></sup>‘Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>who brought us up from the land of Egypt,who led us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18972L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18972L\"></sup>in the wilderness,in a land of deserts and pits,in a land of drought and deep darkness,in a land that none passes through,where no man dwells?’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18973M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18973M\"></sup>And I brought you into a plentiful landto enjoy its fruits and its good things.But when you came in, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18973N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18973N\"></sup>you defiled my landand made my heritage an abomination.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The priests did not say, ‘Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18974O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18974O\"></sup>Those who handle the law did not know me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18974P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18974P\"></sup>the shepherds transgressed against me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18974Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18974Q\"></sup>the prophets prophesied by Baaland went after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18974R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18974R\"></sup>things that do not profit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18975S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18975S\"></sup>I still contend with you,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18975T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18975T\"></sup>with your children's children I will contend.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For cross to the coasts of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18976U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18976U\"></sup>Cyprus and see,or send to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18976V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18976V\"></sup>Kedar and examine with care;see if there has been such a thing.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18977W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18977W\"></sup>Has a nation changed its gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18977X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18977X\"></sup>even though they are no gods?But my people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18977Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18977Y\"></sup>have changed their gloryfor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18977Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18977Z\"></sup>that which does not profit.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Be appalled, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18978AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18978AA\"></sup>O heavens, at this;be shocked, be utterly desolate,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>for my people have committed two evils:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18979AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18979AB\"></sup>they have forsaken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18979AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18979AC\"></sup>me,the fountain of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18979AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18979AD\"></sup>living waters,and hewed out cisterns for themselves,broken cisterns that can hold no water.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18980AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18980AE\"></sup>“Is Israel a slave? Is he a homeborn servant?Why then has he become a prey?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18981AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18981AF\"></sup>The lions have roared against him;they have roared loudly.They have made his land a waste;his cities are in ruins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18981AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18981AG\"></sup>without inhabitant.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Moreover, the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18982AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18982AH\"></sup>Memphis and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18982AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18982AI\"></sup>Tahpanhes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18982AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18982AJ\"></sup>have shaved the crown of your head.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18983AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18983AK\"></sup>Have you not brought this upon yourselfby forsaking the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18983AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18983AL\"></sup>he led you in the way?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18984AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18984AM\"></sup>And now what do you gain by going to Egyptto drink the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18984AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18984AN\"></sup>the Nile?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18984AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18984AO\"></sup>Or what do you gain by going to Assyriato drink the waters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18984AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18984AP\"></sup>the Euphrates?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18985AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18985AQ\"></sup>Your evil will chastise you,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18985AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18985AR\"></sup>your apostasy will reprove you.Know and see that it is evil and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18985AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18985AS\"></sup>bitterfor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18985AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18985AT\"></sup>you to forsake the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God;the fear of me is not in you,declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“For long ago I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18986AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18986AU\"></sup>broke your yokeand burst your bonds;but you said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18986AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18986AV\"></sup>‘I will not serve.’Yes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18986AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18986AW\"></sup>on every high hilland under every green treeyou bowed down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18986AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18986AX\"></sup>like a whore.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18987AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18987AY\"></sup>Yet I planted you a choice vine,wholly of pure seed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18987AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18987AZ\"></sup>How then have you turned degenerateand become a wild vine?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Though you wash yourself with lyeand use much soap,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18988BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18988BA\"></sup>the stain of your guilt is still before me,declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18989BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18989BB\"></sup>How can you say, ‘I am not unclean,I have not gone after the Baals’?Look at your way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18989BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18989BC\"></sup>in the valley;know what you have done—a restless young camel running here and there,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18990BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18990BD\"></sup>a wild donkey used to the wilderness,in her heat sniffing the wind!Who can restrain her lust?None who seek her need weary themselves;in her month they will find her.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Keep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18991BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18991BE\"></sup>your feet from going unshodand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18991BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18991BF\"></sup>your throat from thirst.But you said, ‘It is hopeless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18991BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18991BG\"></sup>for I have loved foreigners,and after them I will go.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“As a thief is shamed when caught,so the house of Israel shall be shamed:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18992BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18992BH\"></sup>they, their kings, their officials,their priests, and their prophets,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>who say to a tree, ‘You are my father,’and to a stone, ‘You gave me birth.’For they have turned their back to me,and not their face.But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18993BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18993BI\"></sup>in the time of their trouble they say,‘Arise and save us!’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18994BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18994BJ\"></sup>where are your godsthat you made for yourself?Let them arise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18994BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18994BK\"></sup>if they can save you,in your time of trouble;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18994BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18994BL\"></sup>as many as your citiesare your gods, O Judah.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Why do you contend with me?You have all transgressed against me,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>In vain have I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18996BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18996BM\"></sup>struck your children;they took no correction;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18996BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18996BN\"></sup>your own sword devoured your prophetslike a ravening lion.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And you, O generation, behold the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Have I been a wilderness to Israel,or a land of thick darkness?Why then do my people say, ‘We are free,we will come no more to you’?",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18998BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18998BO\"></sup>Can a virgin forget her ornaments,or a bride her attire?Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-18998BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-18998BP\"></sup>my people have forgotten medays without number.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“How well you direct your courseto seek love!So that even to wicked womenyou have taught your ways.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Also on your skirts is found<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19000BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19000BQ\"></sup>the lifeblood of the guiltless poor;you did not find them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19000BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19000BR\"></sup>breaking in.Yet in spite of all these things",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>you say, ‘I am innocent;surely his anger has turned from me.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19001BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19001BS\"></sup>Behold, I will bring you to judgmentfor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19001BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19001BT\"></sup>saying, ‘I have not sinned.’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19002BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19002BU\"></sup>How much you go about,changing your way!You shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19002BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19002BV\"></sup>put to shame by Egyptas you were put to shame by Assyria.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>From it too you will come awaywith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19003BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19003BW\"></sup>your hands on your head,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected those in whom you trust,and you will not prosper by them."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19004A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19004A\"></sup>“If a man divorces his wifeand she goes from himand becomes another man's wife,will he return to her?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19004B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19004B\"></sup>Would not that land be greatly polluted?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19004C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19004C\"></sup>You have played the whore with many lovers;and would you return to me?declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Lift up your eyes to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19005D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19005D\"></sup>the bare heights, and see!Where have you not been ravished?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19005E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19005E\"></sup>By the waysides you have sat awaiting loverslike an Arab in the wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19005F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19005F\"></sup>You have polluted the landwith your vile whoredom.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19006G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19006G\"></sup>Therefore the showers have been withheld,and the spring rain has not come;yet you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19006H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19006H\"></sup>the forehead of a whore;you refuse to be ashamed.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Have you not just now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19007I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19007I\"></sup>called to me,‘My father, you are the friend of my youth—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19008J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19008J\"></sup>will he be angry forever,will he be indignant to the end?’Behold, you have spoken,but you have done all the evil that you could.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19009K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19009K\"></sup>King Josiah: “Have you seen what she did, that faithless one, Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19009L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19009L\"></sup>how she went up on every high hill and under every green tree, and there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19009M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19009M\"></sup>played the whore?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I thought, ‘After she has done all this she will return to me,’ but she did not return, and her treacherous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19010N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19010N\"></sup>sister Judah saw it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>She saw that for all the adulteries of that faithless one, Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19011O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19011O\"></sup>I had sent her away with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19011P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19011P\"></sup>a decree of divorce. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19011Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19011Q\"></sup>Yet her treacherous sister Judah did not fear, but she too went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19011R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19011R\"></sup>and played the whore.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Because she took her whoredom lightly, she polluted the land, committing adultery with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19012S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19012S\"></sup>stone and tree.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet for all this her treacherous sister Judah did not return to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19013T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19013T\"></sup>with her whole heart, but in pretense, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19014U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19014U\"></sup>“Faithless Israel has shown herself more righteous than treacherous Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Go, and proclaim these words toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19015V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19015V\"></sup>the north, and say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19015W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19015W\"></sup>“‘Return, faithless Israel,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.I will not look on you in anger,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19015X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19015X\"></sup>I am merciful,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19015Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19015Y\"></sup>I will not be angry forever.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19016Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19016Z\"></sup>Only acknowledge your guilt,that you rebelled against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godand scattered your favors among foreigners under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19016AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19016AA\"></sup>every green tree,and that you have not obeyed my voice,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19017AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19017AB\"></sup>Return, O faithless children,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19017AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19017AC\"></sup>for I am your master;I will take you, one from a city and two from a family,and I will bring you to Zion.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19018AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19018AD\"></sup>I will give you shepherds after my own heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19018AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19018AE\"></sup>who will feed you with knowledge and understanding.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And when you have multiplied and been fruitful in the land, in those days, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, they shall no more say, “The ark of the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.” It shall not come to mind or be remembered or missed; it shall not be made again.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>At that time Jerusalem shall be called the throne of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19020AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19020AF\"></sup>and all nations shall gather to it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19020AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19020AG\"></sup>to the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in Jerusalem, and they shall no more stubbornly follow their own evil heart.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19021AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19021AH\"></sup>In those days the house of Judah shall join the house of Israel, and together they shall come from the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19021AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19021AI\"></sup>of the north to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19021AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19021AJ\"></sup>the land that I gave your fathers for a heritage.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“‘I said,How I would set you among my sons,and give you a pleasant land,a heritage most beautiful of all nations.And I thought you would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19022AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19022AK\"></sup>call me, My Father,and would not turn from following me.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19023AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19023AL\"></sup>Surely, as a treacherous wife leaves her husband,so have you been treacherous to me, O house of Israel,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A voice on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19024AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19024AM\"></sup>bare heights is heard,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19024AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19024AN\"></sup>the weeping and pleading of Israel's sonsbecause they have perverted their way;they have forgotten the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19025AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19025AO\"></sup>“Return, O faithless sons;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19025AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19025AP\"></sup>I will heal your faithlessness.”“Behold, we come to you,for you are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19026AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19026AQ\"></sup>the hills are a delusion,the orgies on the mountains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19026AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19026AR\"></sup>Truly in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our Godis the salvation of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“But from our youth the shameful thing has devoured all for which our fathers labored, their flocks and their herds, their sons and their daughters.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19028AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19028AS\"></sup>Let us lie down in our shame, and let our dishonor cover us. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19028AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19028AT\"></sup>we have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, we and our fathers, from our youth even to this day, and we have not obeyed the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“If you return, O Israel,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19029A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19029A\"></sup>to me you should return.If you remove your detestable things from my presence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19029B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19029B\"></sup>and do not waver,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19030C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19030C\"></sup>and if you swear, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’in truth, in justice, and in righteousness,then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19030D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19030D\"></sup>nations shall bless themselves in him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19030E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19030E\"></sup>and in him shall they glory.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to the men of Judah and Jerusalem:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19031F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19031F\"></sup>“Break up your fallow ground,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19031G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19031G\"></sup>sow not among thorns.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19032H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19032H\"></sup>Circumcise yourselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;remove the foreskin of your hearts,O men of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19032I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19032I\"></sup>lest my wrath go forth like fire,and burn with none to quench it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19032J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19032J\"></sup>because of the evil of your deeds.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Declare in Judah, and proclaim in Jerusalem, and say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19033K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19033K\"></sup>“Blow the trumpet through the land;cry aloud and say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19033L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19033L\"></sup>‘Assemble, and let us gointo the fortified cities!’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19034M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19034M\"></sup>Raise a standard toward Zion,flee for safety, stay not,for I bring disaster from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19034N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19034N\"></sup>the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19034O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19034O\"></sup>and great destruction.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19035P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19035P\"></sup>A lion has gone up from his thicket,a destroyer of nations has set out;he has gone out from his placeto make your land a waste;your cities will be ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19035Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19035Q\"></sup>without inhabitant.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19036R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19036R\"></sup>put on sackcloth,lament and wail,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19036S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19036S\"></sup>the fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>has not turned back from us.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“In that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19037T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19037T\"></sup>courage shall fail both king and officials. The priests shall be appalled and the prophets astounded.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I said, “Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19038U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19038U\"></sup>surely you have utterly deceived this people and Jerusalem, saying, ‘It shall be well with you,’ whereas the sword has reached their very life.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>At that time it will be said to this people and to Jerusalem, “A hot wind from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19039V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19039V\"></sup>the bare heights in the desert toward the daughter of my people, not to winnow or cleanse,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>a wind too full for this comes for me. Now it is I who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19040W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19040W\"></sup>speak in judgment upon them.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Behold, he comes up like clouds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19041X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19041X\"></sup>his chariots like the whirlwind;his horses are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19041Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19041Y\"></sup>swifter than eagles—woe to us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19041Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19041Z\"></sup>for we are ruined!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>O Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19042AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19042AA\"></sup>wash your heart from evil,that you may be saved.How long shall your wicked thoughtslodge within you?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For a voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19043AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19043AB\"></sup>declares from Danand proclaims trouble from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19043AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19043AC\"></sup>Mount Ephraim.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Warn the nations that he is coming;announce to Jerusalem,“Besiegers come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19044AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19044AD\"></sup>from a distant land;they shout against the cities of Judah.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Like keepers of a field <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19045AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19045AE\"></sup>are they against her all around,because she has rebelled against me,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Your ways and your deedshave brought this upon you.This is your doom, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19046AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19046AF\"></sup>it is bitter;it has reached your very heart.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19047AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19047AG\"></sup>My anguish, my anguish! I writhe in pain!Oh the walls of my heart!My heart is beating wildly;I cannot keep silent,for I hear the sound of the trumpet,the alarm of war.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19048AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19048AH\"></sup>Crash follows hard on crash;the whole land is laid waste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19048AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19048AI\"></sup>Suddenly my tents are laid waste,my curtains in a moment.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>How long must I see the standardand hear the sound of the trumpet?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19050AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19050AJ\"></sup>my people are foolish;they know me not;they are stupid children;they have no understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19050AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19050AK\"></sup>They are ‘wise’—in doing evil!But how to do good they know not.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I looked on the earth, and behold, it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19051AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19051AL\"></sup>without form and void;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19051AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19051AM\"></sup>and to the heavens, and they had no light.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I looked on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19052AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19052AN\"></sup>the mountains, and behold, they were quaking,and all the hills moved to and fro.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19053AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19053AO\"></sup>I looked, and behold, there was no man,and all the birds of the air had fled.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I looked, and behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19054AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19054AP\"></sup>fruitful land was a desert,and all its cities were laid in ruinsbefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19054AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19054AQ\"></sup>his fierce anger.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “The whole land shall be a desolation; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19055AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19055AR\"></sup>yet I will not make a full end.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19056AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19056AS\"></sup>“For this the earth shall mourn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19056AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19056AT\"></sup>and the heavens above be dark;for I have spoken; I have purposed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19056AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19056AU\"></sup>I have not relented, nor will I turn back.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At the noise of horseman and archerevery city takes to flight;they enter thickets; they climb among rocks;all the cities are forsaken,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19057AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19057AV\"></sup>no man dwells in them.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And you, O desolate one,what do you mean that you dress in scarlet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19058AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19058AW\"></sup>that you adorn yourself with ornaments of gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19058AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19058AX\"></sup>that you enlarge your eyes with paint?In vain you beautify yourself.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19058AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19058AY\"></sup>Your lovers despise you;they seek your life.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19059AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19059AZ\"></sup>a cry as of a woman in labor,anguish as of one giving birth to her first child,the cry of the daughter of Zion gasping for breath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19059BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19059BA\"></sup>stretching out her hands,“Woe is me! I am fainting before murderers.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19060A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19060A\"></sup>Run to and fro through the streets of Jerusalem,look and take note!Search her squares to see<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19060B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19060B\"></sup>if you can find a man,one who does justiceand seeks truth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19060C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19060C\"></sup>that I may pardon her.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19061D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19061D\"></sup>Though they say, “As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19061E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19061E\"></sup>yet they swear falsely.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do not your eyes look for truth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19062F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19062F\"></sup>You have struck them down,but they felt no anguish;you have consumed them,but they refused to take correction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19062G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19062G\"></sup>They have made their faces harder than rock;they have refused to repent.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I said, “These are only the poor;they have no sense;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19063H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19063H\"></sup>for they do not know the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the justice of their God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will go to the greatand will speak to them,for they know the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the justice of their God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19064I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19064I\"></sup>But they all alike had broken the yoke;they had burst the bonds.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19065J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19065J\"></sup>a lion from the forest shall strike them down;a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19065K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19065K\"></sup>wolf from the desert shall devastate them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19065L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19065L\"></sup>A leopard is watching their cities;everyone who goes out of them shall be torn in pieces,because their transgressions are many,their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19065M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19065M\"></sup>apostasies are great.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19066N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19066N\"></sup>“How can I pardon you?Your children have forsaken me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19066O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19066O\"></sup>and have sworn by those who are no gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19066P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19066P\"></sup>When I fed them to the full,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19066Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19066Q\"></sup>they committed adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19066R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19066R\"></sup>and trooped to the houses of whores.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They were well-fed, lusty stallions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19067S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19067S\"></sup>each neighing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19067T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19067T\"></sup>for his neighbor's wife.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19068U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19068U\"></sup>Shall I not punish them for these things?declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;and shall I not avenge myselfon a nation such as this?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19069V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19069V\"></sup>“Go up through her vine rows and destroy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19069W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19069W\"></sup>but make not a full end;strip away her branches,for they are not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19070X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19070X\"></sup>For the house of Israel and the house of Judahhave been utterly treacherous to me,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They have spoken falsely of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and have said, ‘He will do nothing;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19071Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19071Y\"></sup>no disaster will come upon us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19071Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19071Z\"></sup>nor shall we see sword or famine.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The prophets will become wind;the word is not in them.Thus shall it be done to them!’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts:“Because you have spoken this word,behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19073AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19073AA\"></sup>I am making my words in your mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19073AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19073AB\"></sup>a fire,and this people wood, and the fire shall consume them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19074AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19074AC\"></sup>Behold, I am bringing against youa nation from afar, O house of Israel,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.It is an enduring nation;it is an ancient nation,a nation whose language you do not know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19074AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19074AD\"></sup>nor can you understand what they say.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19075AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19075AE\"></sup>Their quiver is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19075AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19075AF\"></sup>an open tomb;they are all mighty warriors.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19076AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19076AG\"></sup>They shall eat up your harvest and your food;they shall eat up your sons and your daughters;they shall eat up your flocks and your herds;they shall eat up your vines and your fig trees;your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19076AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19076AH\"></sup>fortified cities in which you trustthey shall beat down with the sword.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But even in those days, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19077AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19077AI\"></sup>I will not make a full end of you.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And when your people say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19078AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19078AJ\"></sup>‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God done all these things to us?’ you shall say to them, ‘As you have forsaken me and served foreign gods in your land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19078AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19078AK\"></sup>so you shall serve foreigners in a land that is not yours.’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Declare this in the house of Jacob;proclaim it in Judah:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Hear this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19080AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19080AL\"></sup>O foolish and senseless people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19080AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19080AM\"></sup>who have eyes, but see not,who have ears, but hear not.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19081AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19081AN\"></sup>Do you not fear me? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Do you not tremble before me?I placed the sand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19081AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19081AO\"></sup>as the boundary for the sea,a perpetual barrier that it cannot pass;though the waves toss, they cannot prevail;though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19081AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19081AP\"></sup>they roar, they cannot pass over it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19082AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19082AQ\"></sup>But this people has a stubborn and rebellious heart;they have turned aside and gone away.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They do not say in their hearts,‘Let us fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19083AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19083AR\"></sup>who gives the rain in its season,the autumn rain and the spring rain,and keeps for us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19083AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19083AS\"></sup>the weeks appointed for the harvest.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19084AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19084AT\"></sup>Your iniquities have turned these away,and your sins have kept good from you.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For wicked men are found among my people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19085AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19085AU\"></sup>they lurk like fowlers lying in wait.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19085AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19085AV\"></sup>They set a trap;they catch men.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Like a cage full of birds,their houses are full of deceit;therefore they have become great and rich;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19087AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19087AW\"></sup>they have grown fat and sleek.They know no bounds in deeds of evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19087AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19087AX\"></sup>they judge not with justicethe cause of the fatherless, to make it prosper,and they do not defend the rights of the needy.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19088AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19088AY\"></sup>Shall I not punish them for these things?declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and shall I not avenge myselfon a nation such as this?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>An appalling and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19089AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19089AZ\"></sup>horrible thinghas happened in the land:",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19090BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19090BA\"></sup>the prophets prophesy falsely,and the priests rule at their direction;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19090BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19090BB\"></sup>my people love to have it so,but what will you do when the end comes?"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Flee for safety, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19091A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19091A\"></sup>O people of Benjamin,from the midst of Jerusalem!Blow the trumpet in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19091B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19091B\"></sup>Tekoa,and raise a signal on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19091C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19091C\"></sup>Beth-haccherem,for disaster looms <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19091D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19091D\"></sup>out of the north,and great destruction.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The lovely and delicately bred I will destroy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19092E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19092E\"></sup>the daughter of Zion.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19093F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19093F\"></sup>Shepherds with their flocks shall come against her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19093G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19093G\"></sup>they shall pitch their tents around her;they shall pasture, each in his place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19094H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19094H\"></sup>“Prepare war against her;arise, and let us attack <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19094I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19094I\"></sup>at noon!Woe to us, for the day declines,for the shadows of evening lengthen!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Arise, and let us attack by nightand destroy her palaces!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19096J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19096J\"></sup>“Cut down her trees;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19096K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19096K\"></sup>cast up a siege mound against Jerusalem.This is the city that must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19096L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19096L\"></sup>punished;there is nothing but oppression within her.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19097M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19097M\"></sup>As a well keeps its water fresh,so she keeps fresh her evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19097N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19097N\"></sup>violence and destruction are heard within her;sickness and wounds are ever before me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Be warned, O Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19098O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19098O\"></sup>lest I turn from you in disgust,lest I make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19098P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19098P\"></sup>a desolation,an uninhabited land.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19099Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19099Q\"></sup>“They shall glean thoroughly as a vinethe remnant of Israel;like a grape gatherer pass your hand againover its branches.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19100R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19100R\"></sup>To whom shall I speak and give warning,that they may hear?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19100S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19100S\"></sup>Behold, their ears are uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19100T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19100T\"></sup>they cannot listen;behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19100U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19100U\"></sup>the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is to them an object of scorn;they take no pleasure in it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore I am full of the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19101V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19101V\"></sup>I am weary of holding it in.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19101W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19101W\"></sup>“Pour it out upon the children in the street,and upon the gatherings of young men, also;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19101X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19101X\"></sup>both husband and wife <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19101Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19101Y\"></sup>shall be taken,the elderly and the very aged.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19102Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19102Z\"></sup>Their houses shall be turned over to others,their fields and wives together,for I will stretch out my handagainst the inhabitants of the land,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19103AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19103AA\"></sup>“For from the least to the greatest of them,everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19103AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19103AB\"></sup>is greedy for unjust gain;and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19103AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19103AC\"></sup>prophet to priest,everyone deals falsely.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They have healed the wound of my people lightly,saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19104AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19104AD\"></sup>‘Peace, peace,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19104AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19104AE\"></sup>when there is no peace.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19105AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19105AF\"></sup>Were they ashamed when they committed abomination?No, they were not at all ashamed;they did not know how to blush.Therefore they shall fall among those who fall;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19105AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19105AG\"></sup>at the time that I punish them, they shall be overthrown,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Stand by the roads, and look,and ask for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19106AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19106AH\"></sup>the ancient paths,where the good way is; and walk in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19106AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19106AI\"></sup>and find rest for your souls.But they said, ‘We will not walk in it.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19107AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19107AJ\"></sup>I set watchmen over you, saying,‘Pay attention to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19107AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19107AK\"></sup>the sound of the trumpet!’But they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19107AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19107AL\"></sup>‘We will not pay attention.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore hear, O nations,and know, O congregation, what will happen to them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Hear, O earth; behold, I am bringing disaster upon this people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19109AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19109AM\"></sup>the fruit of their devices,because they have not paid attention to my words;and as for my law, they have rejected it.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19110AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19110AN\"></sup>What use to me is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19110AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19110AO\"></sup>frankincense that comes from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19110AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19110AP\"></sup>Sheba,or sweet cane from a distant land?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19110AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19110AQ\"></sup>Your burnt offerings are not acceptable,nor your sacrifices pleasing to me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19111AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19111AR\"></sup>‘Behold, I will lay before this peoplestumbling blocks against which they shall stumble;fathers and sons together,neighbor and friend shall perish.’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19112AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19112AS\"></sup>“Behold, a people is coming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19112AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19112AT\"></sup>from the north country,a great nation is stirring from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19112AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19112AU\"></sup>the farthest parts of the earth.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They lay hold on bow and javelin;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19113AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19113AV\"></sup>cruel and have no mercy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19113AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19113AW\"></sup>the sound of them is like the roaring sea;they ride on horses,set in array as a man for battle,against you, O daughter of Zion!”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>We have heard the report of it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19114AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19114AX\"></sup>our hands fall helpless;anguish has taken hold of us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19114AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19114AY\"></sup>pain as of a woman in labor.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Go not out into the field,nor walk on the road,for the enemy has a sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19115AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19115AZ\"></sup>terror is on every side.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>O daughter of my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19116BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19116BA\"></sup>put on sackcloth,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19116BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19116BB\"></sup>roll in ashes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19116BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19116BC\"></sup>make mourning as for an only son,most bitter lamentation,for suddenly the destroyerwill come upon us.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I have made you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19117BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19117BD\"></sup>a tester of metals among my people,that you may know and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19117BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19117BE\"></sup>test their ways.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19118BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19118BF\"></sup>They are all stubbornly rebellious,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19118BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19118BG\"></sup>going about with slanders;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19118BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19118BH\"></sup>bronze and iron;all of them act corruptly.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19119BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19119BI\"></sup>bellows blow fiercely;the lead is consumed by the fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19119BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19119BJ\"></sup>in vain the refining goes on,for the wicked are not removed.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19120BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19120BK\"></sup>Rejected silver they are called,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected them.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19122A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19122A\"></sup>“Stand in the gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house, and proclaim there this word, and say, Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you men of Judah who enter these gates to worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19123B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19123B\"></sup>Amend your ways and your deeds, and I will let you dwell in this place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19124C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19124C\"></sup>Do not trust in these deceptive words: ‘This is the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For if you truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19125D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19125D\"></sup>amend your ways and your deeds, if you truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19125E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19125E\"></sup>execute justice one with another,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19126F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19126F\"></sup>do not oppress the sojourner, the fatherless, or the widow, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19126G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19126G\"></sup>or shed innocent blood in this place, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19126H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19126H\"></sup>and if you do not go after other gods to your own harm,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19127I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19127I\"></sup>then I will let you dwell in this place, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19127J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19127J\"></sup>in the land that I gave of old to your fathers forever.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Behold, you trust in deceptive words to no avail.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19129K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19129K\"></sup>Will you steal, murder, commit adultery, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19129L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19129L\"></sup>swear falsely, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19129M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19129M\"></sup>make offerings to Baal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19129N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19129N\"></sup>and go after other gods that you have not known,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and then come and stand before me in this house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19130O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19130O\"></sup>which is called by my name, and say, ‘We are delivered!’—only to go on doing all these abominations?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19131P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19131P\"></sup>Has this house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19131Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19131Q\"></sup>which is called by my name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19131R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19131R\"></sup>become a den of robbers in your eyes? Behold, I myself have seen it, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Go now to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19132S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19132S\"></sup>my place that was in Shiloh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19132T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19132T\"></sup>where I made my name dwell at first, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19132U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19132U\"></sup>see what I did to it because of the evil of my people Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And now, because you have done all these things, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19133V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19133V\"></sup>when I spoke to you persistently you did not listen, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19133W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19133W\"></sup>when I called you, you did not answer,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>therefore I will do to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19134X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19134X\"></sup>the house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19134Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19134Y\"></sup>that is called by my name, and in which you trust, and to the place that I gave to you and to your fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19134Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19134Z\"></sup>as I did to Shiloh.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19135AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19135AA\"></sup>And I will cast you out of my sight, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19135AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19135AB\"></sup>as I cast out all your kinsmen, all the offspring of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19135AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19135AC\"></sup>Ephraim.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“As for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19136AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19136AD\"></sup>do not pray for this people, or lift up a cry or prayer for them, and do not intercede with me, for I will not hear you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do you not see what they are doing in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The children gather wood, the fathers kindle fire, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19138AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19138AE\"></sup>and the women knead dough, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19138AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19138AF\"></sup>make cakes for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19138AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19138AG\"></sup>the queen of heaven. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19138AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19138AH\"></sup>they pour out drink offerings to other gods, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19138AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19138AI\"></sup>to provoke me to anger.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19139AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19139AJ\"></sup>Is it I whom they provoke? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Is it not themselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19139AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19139AK\"></sup>to their own shame?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>: Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19140AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19140AL\"></sup>my anger and my wrath will be poured out on this place, upon man and beast, upon the trees of the field and the fruit of the ground; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19140AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19140AM\"></sup>it will burn and not be quenched.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19141AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19141AN\"></sup>“Add your burnt offerings to your sacrifices, and eat the flesh.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For in the day that I brought them out of the land of Egypt, I did not speak to your fathers or command them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19142AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19142AO\"></sup>concerning burnt offerings and sacrifices.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But this command I gave them: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19143AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19143AP\"></sup>‘Obey my voice, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19143AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19143AQ\"></sup>I will be your God, and you shall be my people. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19143AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19143AR\"></sup>And walk in all the way that I command you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19143AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19143AS\"></sup>that it may be well with you.’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19144AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19144AT\"></sup>But they did not obey or incline their ear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19144AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19144AU\"></sup>but walked in their own counsels and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19144AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19144AV\"></sup>the stubbornness of their evil hearts, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19144AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19144AW\"></sup>went backward and not forward.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>From the day that your fathers came out of the land of Egypt to this day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19145AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19145AX\"></sup>I have persistently sent all my servants the prophets to them, day after day.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19146AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19146AY\"></sup>Yet they did not listen to me or incline their ear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19146AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19146AZ\"></sup>but stiffened their neck. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19146BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19146BA\"></sup>They did worse than their fathers.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19147BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19147BB\"></sup>“So you shall speak all these words to them, but they will not listen to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19147BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19147BC\"></sup>You shall call to them, but they will not answer you.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And you shall say to them, ‘This is the nation that did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, and did not accept discipline; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19148BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19148BD\"></sup>truth has perished; it is cut off from their lips.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19149BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19149BE\"></sup>“‘Cut off your hair and cast it away;raise a lamentation on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19149BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19149BF\"></sup>the bare heights,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected and forsakenthe generation of his wrath.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“For the sons of Judah have done evil in my sight, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. They have set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19150BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19150BG\"></sup>their detestable things in the house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19150BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19150BH\"></sup>that is called by my name, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19150BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19150BI\"></sup>defile it.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And they have built the high places of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19151BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19151BJ\"></sup>Topheth, which is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19151BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19151BK\"></sup>the Valley of the Son of Hinnom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19151BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19151BL\"></sup>to burn their sons and their daughters in the fire, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19151BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19151BM\"></sup>which I did not command, nor did it come into my mind.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19152BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19152BN\"></sup>Therefore, behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when it will no more be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19152BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19152BO\"></sup>Topheth, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19152BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19152BP\"></sup>the Valley of the Son of Hinnom, but the Valley of Slaughter; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19152BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19152BQ\"></sup>for they will bury in Topheth, because there is no room elsewhere.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19153BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19153BR\"></sup>And the dead bodies of this people will be food for the birds of the air, and for the beasts of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19153BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19153BS\"></sup>and none will frighten them away.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19154BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19154BT\"></sup>And I will silence in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem the voice of mirth and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19154BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19154BU\"></sup>for the land shall become a waste."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>“At that time, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the bones of the kings of Judah, the bones of its officials, the bones of the priests, the bones of the prophets, and the bones of the inhabitants of Jerusalem shall be brought out of their tombs.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And they shall be spread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19156A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19156A\"></sup>before the sun and the moon and all the host of heaven, which they have loved and served, which they have gone after, and which they have sought and worshiped. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19156B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19156B\"></sup>And they shall not be gathered or buried. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19156C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19156C\"></sup>They shall be as dung on the surface of the ground.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19157D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19157D\"></sup>Death shall be preferred to life by all the remnant that remains of this evil family <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19157E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19157E\"></sup>in all the places where I have driven them, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“You shall say to them, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19158F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19158F\"></sup>When men fall, do they not rise again?If one turns away, does he not return?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Why then has this people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19159G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19159G\"></sup>turned awayin perpetual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19159H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19159H\"></sup>backsliding?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19159I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19159I\"></sup>They hold fast to deceit;they refuse to return.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19160J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19160J\"></sup>I have paid attention and listened,but they have not spoken rightly;no man relents of his evil,saying, ‘What have I done?’Everyone turns to his own course,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19160K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19160K\"></sup>like a horse plunging headlong into battle.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Even the stork in the heavensknows her times,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19161L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19161L\"></sup>the turtledove, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19161M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19161M\"></sup>swallow, and cranekeep the time of their coming,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19161N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19161N\"></sup>but my people know notthe rules of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19162O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19162O\"></sup>“How can you say, ‘We are wise,and the law of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with us’?But behold, the lying pen of the scribeshas made it into a lie.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19163P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19163P\"></sup>The wise men shall be put to shame;they shall be dismayed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19163Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19163Q\"></sup>and taken;behold, they have rejected the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,so what wisdom is in them?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19164R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19164R\"></sup>Therefore I will give their wives to othersand their fields to conquerors,because from the least to the greatesteveryone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19164S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19164S\"></sup>is greedy for unjust gain;from prophet to priest,everyone deals falsely.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They have healed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19165T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19165T\"></sup>the wound of my people lightly,saying, ‘Peace, peace,’when there is no peace.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Were they ashamed when they committed abomination?No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19166U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19166U\"></sup>they were not at all ashamed;they did not know how to blush.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19166V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19166V\"></sup>Therefore they shall fall among the fallen;when I punish them, they shall be overthrown,says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When I would gather them, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19167W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19167W\"></sup>no grapes on the vine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19167X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19167X\"></sup>nor figs on the fig tree;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19167Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19167Y\"></sup>even the leaves are withered,and what I gave them has passed away from them.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Why do we sit still?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19168Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19168Z\"></sup>Gather together; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19168AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19168AA\"></sup>let us go into the fortified citiesand perish there,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has doomed us to perishand has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19168AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19168AB\"></sup>given us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19168AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19168AC\"></sup>poisoned water to drink,because we have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19169AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19169AD\"></sup>We looked for peace, but no good came;for a time of healing, but behold, terror.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19170AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19170AE\"></sup>“The snorting of their horses is heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19170AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19170AF\"></sup>from Dan;at the sound of the neighing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19170AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19170AG\"></sup>of their stallions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19170AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19170AH\"></sup>the whole land quakes.They come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19170AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19170AI\"></sup>and devour the land and all that fills it,the city and those who dwell in it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For behold, I am sending among you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19171AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19171AJ\"></sup>serpents,adders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19171AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19171AK\"></sup>that cannot be charmed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19171AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19171AL\"></sup>and they shall bite you,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>My joy is gone; grief is upon me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19172AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19172AM\"></sup>my heart is sick within me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Behold, the cry of the daughter of my peoplefrom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19173AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19173AN\"></sup>the length and breadth of the land:“Is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> not in Zion?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19173AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19173AO\"></sup>Is her King not in her?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19173AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19173AP\"></sup>“Why have they provoked me to anger with their carved imagesand with their foreign idols?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The harvest is past, the summer is ended,and we are not saved.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the wound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19175AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19175AQ\"></sup>the daughter of my people is my heart wounded;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19175AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19175AR\"></sup>I mourn, and dismay has taken hold on me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Is there no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19176AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19176AS\"></sup>balm in Gilead?Is there no physician there?Why then has the health of the daughter of my peoplenot been restored?"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19177A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19177A\"></sup>Oh that my head were waters,and my eyes a fountain of tears,that I might weep day and nightfor the slain of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19177B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19177B\"></sup>the daughter of my people!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup> Oh that I had in the deserta travelers' lodging place,that I might leave my peopleand go away from them!For they are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19178C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19178C\"></sup>adulterers,a company of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19178D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19178D\"></sup>treacherous men.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19179E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19179E\"></sup>They bend their tongue like a bow;falsehood and not truth has grown strong in the land;for they proceed from evil to evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19179F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19179F\"></sup>and they do not know me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19180G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19180G\"></sup>Let everyone beware of his neighbor,and put no trust in any brother,for every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19180H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19180H\"></sup>brother is a deceiver,and every neighbor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19180I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19180I\"></sup>goes about as a slanderer.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Everyone deceives his neighbor,and no one speaks the truth;they have taught their tongue to speak lies;they weary themselves committing iniquity.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Heaping oppression upon oppression, and deceit upon deceit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19182J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19182J\"></sup>they refuse to know me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19183K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19183K\"></sup>I will refine them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19183L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19183L\"></sup>test them,for what else can I do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19183M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19183M\"></sup>because of my people?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19184N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19184N\"></sup>Their tongue is a deadly arrow;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19184O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19184O\"></sup>it speaks deceitfully;with his mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19184P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19184P\"></sup>each speaks peace to his neighbor,but in his heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19184Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19184Q\"></sup>he plans an ambush for him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19185R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19185R\"></sup>Shall I not punish them for these things? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and shall I not avenge myselfon a nation such as this?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I will take up weeping and wailing for the mountains,and a lamentation for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19186S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19186S\"></sup>the pastures of the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19186T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19186T\"></sup>because they are laid waste so that no one passes through,and the lowing of cattle is not heard;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19186U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19186U\"></sup>both the birds of the air and the beastshave fled and are gone.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19187V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19187V\"></sup>I will make Jerusalem a heap of ruins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19187W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19187W\"></sup>a lair of jackals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19187X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19187X\"></sup>and I will make the cities of Judah a desolation,without inhabitant.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19188Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19188Y\"></sup>Who is the man so wise that he can understand this? To whom has the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken, that he may declare it? Why is the land ruined <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19188Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19188Z\"></sup>and laid waste like a wilderness, so that no one passes through?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19189AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19189AA\"></sup>“Because they have forsaken my law that I set before them, and have not obeyed my voice or walked in accord with it,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19190AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19190AB\"></sup>have stubbornly followed their own hearts and have gone after the Baals, as their fathers taught them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19191AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19191AC\"></sup>Behold, I will feed this people with bitter food, and give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19191AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19191AD\"></sup>poisonous water to drink.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19192AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19192AE\"></sup>I will scatter them among the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19192AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19192AF\"></sup>whom neither they nor their fathers have known, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19192AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19192AG\"></sup>send the sword after them, until I have consumed them.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19193AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19193AH\"></sup>“Consider, and call for the mourning women to come;send for the skillful women to come;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>let them make haste <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19194AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19194AI\"></sup>and raise a wailing over us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19194AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19194AJ\"></sup>that our eyes may run down with tearsand our eyelids flow with water.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For a sound of wailing is heard from Zion:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19195AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19195AK\"></sup>‘How we are ruined!We are utterly shamed,because we have left the land,because they have cast down our dwellings.’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Hear, O women, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and let your ear receive the word of his mouth;teach to your daughters a lament,and each to her neighbor a dirge.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For death has come up into our windows;it has entered our palaces,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19197AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19197AL\"></sup>cutting off the children from the streetsand the young men from the squares.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Speak: “Thus declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19198AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19198AM\"></sup>‘The dead bodies of men shall falllike dung upon the open field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19198AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19198AN\"></sup>like sheaves after the reaper,and none shall gather them.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19199AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19199AO\"></sup>“Let not the wise man boast in his wisdom, let not the mighty man boast in his might, let not the rich man boast in his riches,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19200AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19200AP\"></sup>let him who boasts boast in this, that he understands and knows me, that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who practices steadfast love, justice, and righteousness in the earth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19200AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19200AQ\"></sup>For in these things I delight, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19201AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19201AR\"></sup>I will punish all those who are circumcised merely in the flesh—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19202AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19202AS\"></sup>Egypt, Judah, Edom, the sons of Ammon, Moab, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19202AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19202AT\"></sup>all who dwell in the desert who cut the corners of their hair, for all these nations are uncircumcised, and all the house of Israel are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19202AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19202AU\"></sup>uncircumcised in heart.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Hear the word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> speaks to you, O house of Israel.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Learn not the way of the nations,nor be dismayed at the signs of the heavensbecause the nations are dismayed at them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19205A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19205A\"></sup>for the customs of the peoples are vanity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19205B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19205B\"></sup>A tree from the forest is cut downand worked with an axe by the hands of a craftsman.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19206C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19206C\"></sup>They decorate it with silver and gold;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19206D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19206D\"></sup>they fasten it with hammer and nailsso that it cannot move.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Their idols are like scarecrows in a cucumber field,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19207E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19207E\"></sup>they cannot speak;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19207F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19207F\"></sup>they have to be carried,for they cannot walk.Do not be afraid of them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19207G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19207G\"></sup>for they cannot do evil,neither is it in them to do good.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19208H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19208H\"></sup>There is none like you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;you are great, and your name is great in might.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19209I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19209I\"></sup>Who would not fear you, O King of the nations?For this is your due;for among all the wise ones of the nationsand in all their kingdomsthere is none like you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19210J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19210J\"></sup>They are both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19210K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19210K\"></sup>stupid and foolish;the instruction of idols is but wood!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19211L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19211L\"></sup>Beaten silver is brought from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19211M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19211M\"></sup>Tarshish,and gold from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19211N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19211N\"></sup>Uphaz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19211O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19211O\"></sup>They are the work of the craftsman and of the hands of the goldsmith;their clothing is violet and purple;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19211P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19211P\"></sup>they are all the work of skilled men.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19212Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19212Q\"></sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the true God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19212R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19212R\"></sup>he is the living God and the everlasting King.At his wrath the earth quakes,and the nations cannot endure his indignation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus shall you say to them: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19213S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19213S\"></sup>“The gods who did not make the heavens and the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19213T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19213T\"></sup>shall perish from the earth and from under the heavens.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19214U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19214U\"></sup>It is he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19214V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19214V\"></sup>made the earth by his power,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19214W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19214W\"></sup>who established the world by his wisdom,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19214X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19214X\"></sup>by his understanding stretched out the heavens.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19215Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19215Y\"></sup>When he utters his voice, there is a tumult of waters in the heavens,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19215Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19215Z\"></sup>and he makes the mist rise from the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19215AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19215AA\"></sup>He makes lightning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19215AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19215AB\"></sup>for the rain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19215AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19215AC\"></sup>and he brings forth the wind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19215AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19215AD\"></sup>from his storehouses.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19216AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19216AE\"></sup>Every man is stupid and without knowledge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19216AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19216AF\"></sup>every goldsmith is put to shame by his idols,for his images are false,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19216AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19216AG\"></sup>and there is no breath in them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They are worthless, a work of delusion;at the time of their punishment they shall perish.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Not like these is he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19218AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19218AH\"></sup>the portion of Jacob,for he is the one who formed all things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19218AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19218AI\"></sup>and Israel is the tribe of his inheritance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19218AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19218AJ\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19219AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19219AK\"></sup>Gather up your bundle from the ground,O you who dwell under siege!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19220AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19220AL\"></sup>“Behold, I am slinging out the inhabitants of the landat this time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19220AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19220AM\"></sup>and I will bring distress on them,that they may feel it.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Woe is me because of my hurt!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19221AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19221AN\"></sup>My wound is grievous.But I said, “Truly this is an affliction,and I must bear it.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19222AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19222AO\"></sup>My tent is destroyed,and all my cords are broken;my children have gone from me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19222AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19222AP\"></sup>and they are not;there is no one to spread my tent againand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19222AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19222AQ\"></sup>to set up my curtains.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19223AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19223AR\"></sup>For the shepherds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19223AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19223AS\"></sup>are stupidand do not inquire of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;therefore they have not prospered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19223AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19223AT\"></sup>and all their flock is scattered.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>A voice, a rumor! Behold, it comes!—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19224AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19224AU\"></sup>a great commotion out of the north countryto make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19224AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19224AV\"></sup>the cities of Judah a desolation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19224AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19224AW\"></sup>a lair of jackals.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19225AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19225AX\"></sup>I know, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that the way of man is not in himself,that it is not in man who walks to direct his steps.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19226AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19226AY\"></sup>Correct me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, but in justice;not in your anger, lest you bring me to nothing.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19227AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19227AZ\"></sup>Pour out your wrath on the nations that know you not,and on the peoples that call not on your name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19227BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19227BA\"></sup>for they have devoured Jacob;they have devoured him and consumed him,and have laid waste his habitation."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19229A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19229A\"></sup>“Hear the words of this covenant, and speak to the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You shall say to them, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19230B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19230B\"></sup>Cursed be the man who does not hear the words of this covenant",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that I commanded your fathers when I brought them out of the land of Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19231C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19231C\"></sup>from the iron furnace, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19231D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19231D\"></sup>Listen to my voice, and do all that I command you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19231E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19231E\"></sup>So shall you be my people, and I will be your God,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19232F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19232F\"></sup>that I may confirm the oath that I swore to your fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19232G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19232G\"></sup>to give them a land flowing with milk and honey, as at this day.” Then I answered, “So be it, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19233H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19233H\"></sup>“Proclaim all these words in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19233I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19233I\"></sup>Hear the words of this covenant and do them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For I solemnly warned your fathers when I brought them up out of the land of Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19234J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19234J\"></sup>warning them persistently, even to this day, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19234K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19234K\"></sup>Obey my voice.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19235L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19235L\"></sup>Yet they did not obey or incline their ear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19235M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19235M\"></sup>but everyone walked in the stubbornness of his evil heart. Therefore I brought upon them all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19235N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19235N\"></sup>the words of this covenant, which I commanded them to do, but they did not.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Again the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19236O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19236O\"></sup>“A conspiracy exists among the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They have turned back to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19237P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19237P\"></sup>the iniquities of their forefathers, who refused to hear my words. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19237Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19237Q\"></sup>They have gone after other gods to serve them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19237R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19237R\"></sup>The house of Israel and the house of Judah have broken my covenant that I made with their fathers.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Behold, I am bringing disaster upon them that they cannot escape. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19238S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19238S\"></sup>Though they cry to me, I will not listen to them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the cities of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19239T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19239T\"></sup>will go and cry to the gods to whom they make offerings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19239U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19239U\"></sup>but they cannot save them in the time of their trouble.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19240V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19240V\"></sup>For your gods have become as many as your cities, O Judah, and as many as the streets of Jerusalem are the altars you have set up to shame, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19240W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19240W\"></sup>altars to make offerings to Baal.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19241X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19241X\"></sup>do not pray for this people, or lift up a cry or prayer on their behalf, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19241Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19241Y\"></sup>for I will not listen when they call to me in the time of their trouble.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19242Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19242Z\"></sup>What right has my beloved in my house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19242AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19242AA\"></sup>when she has done many vile deeds? Can even sacrificial flesh avert your doom? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19242AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19242AB\"></sup>Can you then exult?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> once called you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19243AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19243AC\"></sup>‘a green olive tree, beautiful with good fruit.’ But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19243AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19243AD\"></sup>with the roar of a great tempest he will set fire to it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19243AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19243AE\"></sup>its branches will be consumed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19244AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19244AF\"></sup>who planted you, has decreed disaster against you, because of the evil that the house of Israel and the house of Judah have done, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19244AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19244AG\"></sup>provoking me to anger by making offerings to Baal.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> made it known to me and I knew;then you showed me their deeds.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19246AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19246AH\"></sup>like a gentle lambled to the slaughter.I did not know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19246AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19246AI\"></sup>it was against methey devised schemes, saying,“Let us destroy the tree with its fruit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19246AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19246AJ\"></sup>let us cut him off from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19246AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19246AK\"></sup>the land of the living,that his name be remembered no more.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, who judges righteously,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19247AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19247AL\"></sup>tests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19247AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19247AM\"></sup>the heart and the mind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19247AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19247AN\"></sup>let me see your vengeance upon them,for to you have I committed my cause.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19248AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19248AO\"></sup>Anathoth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19248AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19248AP\"></sup>who seek your life, and say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19248AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19248AQ\"></sup>“Do not prophesy in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, or you will die by our hand”—",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: “Behold, I will punish them. The young men shall die by the sword, their sons and their daughters shall die by famine,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and none of them shall be left. For I will bring disaster upon the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19250AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19250AR\"></sup>Anathoth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19250AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19250AS\"></sup>the year of their punishment.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19251A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19251A\"></sup>Righteous are you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,when I complain to you;yet I would plead my case before you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19251B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19251B\"></sup>Why does the way of the wicked prosper?Why do all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19251C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19251C\"></sup>who are treacherous thrive?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You plant them, and they take root;they grow and produce fruit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19252D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19252D\"></sup>you are near in their mouthand far from their heart.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19253E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19253E\"></sup>But you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, know me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19253F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19253F\"></sup>you see me, and test my heart toward you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19253G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19253G\"></sup>Pull them out like sheep for the slaughter,and set them apart for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19253H\"></sup>the day of slaughter.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19254I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19254I\"></sup>How long will the land mournand the grass of every field wither?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19254J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19254J\"></sup>For the evil of those who dwell in it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19254K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19254K\"></sup>the beasts and the birds are swept away,because they said, “He will not see our latter end.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If you have raced with men on foot, and they have wearied you,how will you compete with horses?And if in a safe land you are so trusting,what will you do in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19255L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19255L\"></sup>the thicket of the Jordan?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19256M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19256M\"></sup>even your brothers and the house of your father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19256N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19256N\"></sup>even they have dealt treacherously with you;they are in full cry after you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19256O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19256O\"></sup>do not believe them,though they speak friendly words to you.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I have forsaken my house;I have abandoned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19257P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19257P\"></sup>my heritage;I have given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19257Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19257Q\"></sup>the beloved of my soulinto the hands of her enemies.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19258R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19258R\"></sup>My heritage has become to melike a lion in the forest;she has lifted up her voice against me;therefore I hate her.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19259S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19259S\"></sup>my heritage to me like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19259T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19259T\"></sup>a hyena's lair?Are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19259U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19259U\"></sup>birds of prey against her all around?Go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19259V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19259V\"></sup>assemble all the wild beasts;bring them to devour.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Many shepherds have destroyed my vineyard;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19260W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19260W\"></sup>they have trampled down my portion;they have made my pleasant portiona desolate wilderness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They have made it a desolation;desolate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19261X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19261X\"></sup>it mourns to me.The whole land is made desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19261Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19261Y\"></sup>but no man lays it to heart.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Upon all the bare heights in the desertdestroyers have come,for the sword of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> devoursfrom one end of the land to the other;no flesh has peace.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19263Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19263Z\"></sup>They have sown wheat and have reaped thorns;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19263AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19263AA\"></sup>they have tired themselves out but profit nothing.They shall be ashamed of their harvests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19263AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19263AB\"></sup>because of the fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19264AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19264AC\"></sup>my evil neighbors <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19264AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19264AD\"></sup>who touch the heritage that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19264AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19264AE\"></sup>I have given my people Israel to inherit: “Behold, I will pluck them up from their land, and I will pluck up the house of Judah from among them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And after I have plucked them up, I will again have compassion on them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19265AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19265AF\"></sup>and I will bring them again each to his heritage and each to his land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And it shall come to pass, if they will diligently learn the ways of my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19266AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19266AG\"></sup>to swear by my name, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’ even as they taught my people to swear by Baal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19266AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19266AH\"></sup>then they shall be built up in the midst of my people.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19267AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19267AI\"></sup>But if any nation will not listen, then I will utterly pluck it up and destroy it, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to me, “Go and buy a linen loincloth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19268A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19268A\"></sup>put it around your waist, and do not dip it in water.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I bought a loincloth according to the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and put it around my waist.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me a second time,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Take the loincloth that you have bought, which is around your waist, and arise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19271B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19271B\"></sup>go to the Euphrates and hide it there in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19271C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19271C\"></sup>a cleft of the rock.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So I went and hid it by the Euphrates, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> commanded me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And after many days the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Arise, go to the Euphrates, and take from there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19273D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19273D\"></sup>the loincloth that I commanded you to hide there.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then I went to the Euphrates, and dug, and I took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19274E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19274E\"></sup>the loincloth from the place where I had hidden it. And behold, the loincloth was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19274F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19274F\"></sup>spoiled; it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19274G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19274G\"></sup>good for nothing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19276H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19276H\"></sup>Even so will I spoil the pride of Judah and the great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19276I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19276I\"></sup>pride of Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This evil people, who refuse to hear my words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19277J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19277J\"></sup>who stubbornly follow their own heart and have gone after other gods to serve them and worship them, shall be like this loincloth, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19277K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19277K\"></sup>good for nothing.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For as the loincloth clings to the waist of a man, so I made the whole house of Israel and the whole house of Judah cling to me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19278L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19278L\"></sup>that they might be for me a people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19278M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19278M\"></sup>a name, a praise, and a glory, but they would not listen.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“You shall speak to them this word: ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, “Every jar shall be filled with wine.”’ And they will say to you, ‘Do we not indeed know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19279N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19279N\"></sup>every jar will be filled with wine?’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19280O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19280O\"></sup>Behold, I will fill with drunkenness all the inhabitants of this land: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19280P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19280P\"></sup>the kings who sit on David's throne, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19280Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19280Q\"></sup>the priests, the prophets, and all the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19281R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19281R\"></sup>dash them one against another, fathers and sons together, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. I will not pity or spare or have compassion, that I should not destroy them.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Hear and give ear; be not proud,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19283S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19283S\"></sup>Give glory to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19283T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19283T\"></sup>before he brings darkness,before your feet stumbleon the twilight mountains,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19283U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19283U\"></sup>while you look for lighthe turns it into gloomand makes it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19283V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19283V\"></sup>deep darkness.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if you will not listen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19284W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19284W\"></sup>my soul will weep in secret for your pride;my eyes will weep bitterly and run down with tears,because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s flock has been taken captive.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19285X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19285X\"></sup>the king and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19285Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19285Y\"></sup>the queen mother:“Take a lowly seat,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19285Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19285Z\"></sup>your beautiful crownhas come down from your head.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19286AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19286AA\"></sup>The cities of the Negeb are shut up,with none to open them;all Judah is taken into exile,wholly taken into exile.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Lift up your eyes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19287AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19287AB\"></sup>and seethose who come from the north.Where is the flock that was given you,your beautiful flock?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>What will you say when they set as head over youthose whom you yourself have taught to be friends to you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19288AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19288AC\"></sup>Will not pangs take hold of youlike those of a woman in labor?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And if you say in your heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19289AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19289AD\"></sup>‘Why have these things come upon me?’it is for the greatness of your iniquitythat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19289AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19289AE\"></sup>your skirts are lifted upand you suffer violence.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19290AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19290AF\"></sup>Can the Ethiopian change his skinor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19290AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19290AG\"></sup>the leopard his spots?Then also you can do goodwho are accustomed to do evil.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I will scatter you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19291AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19291AH\"></sup>like chaffdriven by the wind from the desert.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19292AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19292AI\"></sup>This is your lot,the portion I have measured out to you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19292AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19292AJ\"></sup>you have forgotten meand trusted in lies.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19293AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19293AK\"></sup>I myself will lift up your skirts over your face,and your shame will be seen.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>I have seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19294AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19294AL\"></sup>your abominations,your adulteries and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19294AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19294AM\"></sup>neighings, your lewd whorings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19294AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19294AN\"></sup>on the hills in the field.Woe to you, O Jerusalem!How long will it be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19294AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19294AO\"></sup>before you are made clean?”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19295A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19295A\"></sup>the drought:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19296B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19296B\"></sup>“Judah mourns,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19296C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19296C\"></sup>her gates languish;her people lament on the ground,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19296D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19296D\"></sup>the cry of Jerusalem goes up.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Her nobles send their servants for water;they come to the cisterns;they find no water;they return with their vessels empty;they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19297E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19297E\"></sup>ashamed and confoundedand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19297F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19297F\"></sup>cover their heads.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Because of the ground that is dismayed,since there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19298G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19298G\"></sup>no rain on the land,the farmers are ashamed;they cover their heads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19299H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19299H\"></sup>the doe in the field forsakes her newborn fawnbecause there is no grass.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19300I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19300I\"></sup>The wild donkeys stand on the bare heights;they pant for air like jackals;their eyes failbecause there is no vegetation.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Though our iniquities testify against us,act, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19301J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19301J\"></sup>for your name's sake;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19301K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19301K\"></sup>for our backslidings are many;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19301L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19301L\"></sup>we have sinned against you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19302M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19302M\"></sup>O you hope of Israel,its savior in time of trouble,why should you be like a stranger in the land,like a traveler who turns aside to tarry for a night?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Why should you be like a man confused,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19303N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19303N\"></sup>like a mighty warrior who cannot save?Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19303O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19303O\"></sup>you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are in the midst of us,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19303P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19303P\"></sup>we are called by your name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19303Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19303Q\"></sup>do not leave us.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning this people:“They have loved to wander thus;they have not restrained their feet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19304R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19304R\"></sup>therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not accept them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19304S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19304S\"></sup>now he will remember their iniquityand punish their sins.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19305T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19305T\"></sup>“Do not pray for the welfare of this people.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Though they fast, I will not hear their cry, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19306U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19306U\"></sup>and though they offer burnt offering and grain offering, I will not accept them. But I will consume them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19306V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19306V\"></sup>by the sword, by famine, and by pestilence.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I said: “Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, behold, the prophets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19307W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19307W\"></sup>say to them, ‘You shall not see the sword, nor shall you have famine, but I will give you assured peace in this place.’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19308X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19308X\"></sup>prophets are prophesying lies in my name. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19308Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19308Y\"></sup>I did not send them, nor did I command them or speak to them. They are prophesying to you a lying vision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19308Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19308Z\"></sup>worthless divination, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19308AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19308AA\"></sup>the deceit of their own minds.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the prophets who prophesy in my name although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19309AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19309AB\"></sup>I did not send them, and who say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19309AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19309AC\"></sup>‘Sword and famine shall not come upon this land’: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19309AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19309AD\"></sup>By sword and famine those prophets shall be consumed.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the people to whom they prophesy shall be cast out in the streets of Jerusalem, victims of famine and sword, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19310AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19310AE\"></sup>with none to bury them—them, their wives, their sons, and their daughters. For I will pour out their evil upon them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“You shall say to them this word:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19311AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19311AF\"></sup>‘Let my eyes run down with tears night and day,and let them not cease,for the virgin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19311AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19311AG\"></sup>daughter of my people is shattered with a great wound,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19311AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19311AH\"></sup>with a very grievous blow.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19312AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19312AI\"></sup>If I go out into the field,behold, those pierced by the sword!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19312AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19312AJ\"></sup>And if I enter the city,behold, the diseases of famine!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19312AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19312AK\"></sup>For both prophet and priest ply their trade through the landand have no knowledge.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19313AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19313AL\"></sup>Have you utterly rejected Judah?Does your soul loathe Zion?Why have you struck us down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19313AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19313AM\"></sup>so that there is no healing for us?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19313AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19313AN\"></sup>We looked for peace, but no good came;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19313AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19313AO\"></sup>for a time of healing, but behold, terror.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19314AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19314AP\"></sup>We acknowledge our wickedness, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and the iniquity of our fathers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19314AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19314AQ\"></sup>for we have sinned against you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Do not spurn us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19315AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19315AR\"></sup>for your name's sake;do not dishonor your glorious throne;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19315AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19315AS\"></sup>remember and do not break your covenant with us.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Are there any among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19316AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19316AT\"></sup>the false gods of the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19316AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19316AU\"></sup>that can bring rain?Or can the heavens give showers?Are you not he, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God?We set our hope on you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19316AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19316AV\"></sup>for you do all these things."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19317A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19317A\"></sup>“Though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19317B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19317B\"></sup>Moses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19317C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19317C\"></sup>and Samuel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19317D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19317D\"></sup>stood before me, yet my heart would not turn toward this people. Send them out of my sight, and let them go!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when they ask you, ‘Where shall we go?’ you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19318E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19318E\"></sup>“‘Those who are for pestilence, to pestilence,and those who are for the sword, to the sword;those who are for famine, to famine,and those who are for captivity, to captivity.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19319F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19319F\"></sup>I will appoint over them four kinds of destroyers, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: the sword to kill, the dogs to tear, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19319G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19319G\"></sup>the birds of the air <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19319H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19319H\"></sup>and the beasts of the earth to devour and destroy.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19320I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19320I\"></sup>And I will make them a horror to all the kingdoms of the earth because of what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19320J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19320J\"></sup>Manasseh the son of Hezekiah, king of Judah, did in Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19321K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19321K\"></sup>“Who will have pity on you, O Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19321L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19321L\"></sup>or who will grieve for you?Who will turn asideto ask about your welfare?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19322M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19322M\"></sup>You have rejected me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19322N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19322N\"></sup>you keep going backward,so I have stretched out my hand against you and destroyed you—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19322O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19322O\"></sup>I am weary of relenting.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19323P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19323P\"></sup>I have winnowed them with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19323Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19323Q\"></sup>a winnowing forkin the gates of the land;I have bereaved them; I have destroyed my people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19323R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19323R\"></sup>they did not turn from their ways.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I have made their widows more in numberthan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19324S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19324S\"></sup>the sand of the seas;I have brought against the mothers of young mena destroyer at noonday;I have made anguish and terrorfall upon them suddenly.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19325T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19325T\"></sup>She who bore seven has grown feeble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19325U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19325U\"></sup>she has fainted away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19325V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19325V\"></sup>her sun went down while it was yet day;she has been shamed and disgraced.And the rest of them I will give to the swordbefore their enemies,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19326W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19326W\"></sup>Woe is me, my mother, that you bore me, a man of strife and contention to the whole land! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19326X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19326X\"></sup>I have not lent, nor have I borrowed, yet all of them curse me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Have I not set you free for their good? Have I not pleaded for you before the enemy in the time of trouble and in the time of distress?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Can one break iron, iron <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19328Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19328Y\"></sup>from the north, and bronze?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19329Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19329Z\"></sup>“Your wealth and your treasures I will give as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19329AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19329AA\"></sup>spoil, without price, for all your sins, throughout all your territory.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will make you serve your enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19330AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19330AB\"></sup>in a land that you do not know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19330AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19330AC\"></sup>for in my anger a fire is kindled that shall burn forever.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19331AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19331AD\"></sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you know;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19331AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19331AE\"></sup>remember me and visit me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19331AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19331AF\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19331AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19331AG\"></sup>and take vengeance for me on my persecutors.In your forbearance take me not away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19331AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19331AH\"></sup>know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19331AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19331AI\"></sup>for your sake I bear reproach.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Your words were found, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19332AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19332AJ\"></sup>and I ate them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19332AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19332AK\"></sup>your words became to me a joyand the delight of my heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19332AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19332AL\"></sup>for I am called by your name,O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, God of hosts.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19333AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19333AM\"></sup>I did not sit in the company of revelers,nor did I rejoice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19333AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19333AN\"></sup>I sat alone, because your hand was upon me,for you had filled me with indignation.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Why is my pain unceasing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19334AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19334AO\"></sup>my wound incurable,refusing to be healed?Will you be to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19334AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19334AP\"></sup>like a deceitful brook,like waters that fail?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19335AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19335AQ\"></sup>“If you return, I will restore you,and you shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19335AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19335AR\"></sup>stand before me.If you utter what is precious, and not what is worthless,you shall be as my mouth.They shall turn to you,but you shall not turn to them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19336AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19336AS\"></sup>And I will make you to this peoplea fortified wall of bronze;they will fight against you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19336AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19336AT\"></sup>but they shall not prevail over you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19336AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19336AU\"></sup>for I am with youto save you and deliver you,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19337AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19337AV\"></sup>I will deliver you out of the hand of the wicked,and redeem you from the grasp of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19337AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19337AW\"></sup>the ruthless.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“You shall not take a wife, nor shall you have sons or daughters in this place.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the sons and daughters who are born in this place, and concerning the mothers who bore them and the fathers who fathered them in this land:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19341A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19341A\"></sup>They shall die of deadly diseases. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19341B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19341B\"></sup>They shall not be lamented, nor shall they be buried. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19341C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19341C\"></sup>They shall be as dung on the surface of the ground. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19341D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19341D\"></sup>They shall perish by the sword and by famine, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19341E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19341E\"></sup>and their dead bodies shall be food for the birds of the air and for the beasts of the earth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19342F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19342F\"></sup>Do not enter the house of mourning, or go to lament or grieve for them, for I have taken away my peace from this people, my steadfast love and mercy, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Both great and small shall die in this land. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19343G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19343G\"></sup>They shall not be buried, and no one shall lament for them or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19343H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19343H\"></sup>cut himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19343I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19343I\"></sup>or make himself bald for them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>No one shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19344J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19344J\"></sup>break bread for the mourner, to comfort him for the dead, nor shall anyone give him the cup of consolation to drink for his father or his mother.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You shall not go into the house of feasting to sit with them, to eat and drink.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19346K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19346K\"></sup>Behold, I will silence in this place, before your eyes and in your days, the voice of mirth and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“And when you tell this people all these words, and they say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19347L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19347L\"></sup>‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> pronounced all this great evil against us? What is our iniquity? What is the sin that we have committed against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God?’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>then you shall say to them: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19348M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19348M\"></sup>‘Because your fathers have forsaken me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19348N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19348N\"></sup>have gone after other gods and have served and worshiped them, and have forsaken me and have not kept my law,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19349O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19349O\"></sup>you have done worse than your fathers, for behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19349P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19349P\"></sup>every one of you follows his stubborn, evil will, refusing to listen to me.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19350Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19350Q\"></sup>I will hurl you out of this land into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19350R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19350R\"></sup>a land that neither you nor your fathers have known, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19350S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19350S\"></sup>and there you shall serve other gods day and night, for I will show you no favor.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19351T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19351T\"></sup>“Therefore, behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when it shall no longer be said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19351U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19351U\"></sup>‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives who brought up the people of Israel out of the land of Egypt,’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19352V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19352V\"></sup>‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives who brought up the people of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19352W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19352W\"></sup>out of the north country and out of all the countries where he had driven them.’ For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19352X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19352X\"></sup>I will bring them back to their own land that I gave to their fathers.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19353Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19353Y\"></sup>I am sending for many fishers, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and they shall catch them. And afterward I will send for many hunters, and they shall hunt them from every mountain and every hill, and out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19353Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19353Z\"></sup>of the clefts of the rocks.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19354AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19354AA\"></sup>my eyes are on all their ways. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19354AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19354AB\"></sup>They are not hidden from me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19354AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19354AC\"></sup>nor is their iniquity concealed from my eyes.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19355AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19355AD\"></sup>I will doubly repay their iniquity and their sin, because they have polluted my land with the carcasses of their detestable idols, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19355AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19355AE\"></sup>have filled my inheritance with their abominations.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19356AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19356AF\"></sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, my strength and my stronghold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19356AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19356AG\"></sup>my refuge in the day of trouble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19356AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19356AH\"></sup>to you shall the nations comefrom the ends of the earth and say:“Our fathers have inherited nothing but lies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19356AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19356AI\"></sup>worthless things in which there is no profit.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Can man make for himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19357AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19357AJ\"></sup>gods?Such are not gods!”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Therefore, behold, I will make them know, this once I will make them know my power and my might, and they shall know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19358AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19358AK\"></sup>my name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>“The sin of Judah is written with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19359A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19359A\"></sup>a pen of iron; with a point of diamond it is engraved on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19359B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19359B\"></sup>the tablet of their heart, and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19359C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19359C\"></sup>the horns of their altars,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19360D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19360D\"></sup>their children remember their altars and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19360E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19360E\"></sup>Asherim, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19360F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19360F\"></sup>beside every green tree and on the high hills,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19361G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19361G\"></sup>on the mountains in the open country. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19361H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19361H\"></sup>Your wealth and all your treasures I will give for spoil as the price of your high places for sin throughout all your territory.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You shall loosen your hand from your heritage that I gave to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19362I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19362I\"></sup>and I will make you serve your enemies in a land that you do not know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19362J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19362J\"></sup>for in my anger a fire is kindled that shall burn forever.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Cursed is the man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19363K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19363K\"></sup>who trusts in manand makes flesh his strength,whose heart turns away from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19364L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19364L\"></sup>He is like a shrub in the desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19364M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19364M\"></sup>and shall not see any good come.He shall dwell in the parched places of the wilderness,in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19364N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19364N\"></sup>an uninhabited salt land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19365O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19365O\"></sup>“Blessed is the man who trusts in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19365P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19365P\"></sup>whose trust is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19366Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19366Q\"></sup>He is like a tree planted by water,that sends out its roots by the stream,and does not fear when heat comes,for its leaves remain green,and is not anxious in the year of drought,for it does not cease to bear fruit.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The heart is deceitful above all things,and desperately sick;who can understand it?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19368R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19368R\"></sup>“I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> search the heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19368S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19368S\"></sup>and test the mind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19368T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19368T\"></sup>to give every man according to his ways,according to the fruit of his deeds.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19369U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19369U\"></sup>partridge that gathers a brood that she did not hatch,so is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19369V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19369V\"></sup>he who gets riches but not by justice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19369W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19369W\"></sup>in the midst of his days they will leave him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19369X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19369X\"></sup>and at his end he will be a fool.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A glorious throne set on high from the beginningis the place of our sanctuary.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19371Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19371Y\"></sup>the hope of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19371Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19371Z\"></sup>all who forsake you shall be put to shame;those who turn away from you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19371AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19371AA\"></sup>shall be written in the earth,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19371AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19371AB\"></sup>they have forsaken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19371AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19371AC\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the fountain of living water.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19372AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19372AD\"></sup>Heal me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I shall be healed;save me, and I shall be saved,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19372AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19372AE\"></sup>you are my praise.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19373AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19373AF\"></sup>Behold, they say to me,“Where is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?Let it come!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have not run away from being your shepherd,nor have I desired the day of sickness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19374AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19374AG\"></sup>You know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19374AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19374AH\"></sup>what came out of my lips;it was before your face.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Be not a terror to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19375AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19375AI\"></sup>you are my refuge in the day of disaster.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19376AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19376AJ\"></sup>Let those be put to shame who persecute me,but let me not be put to shame;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19376AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19376AK\"></sup>let them be dismayed,but let me not be dismayed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19376AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19376AL\"></sup>bring upon them the day of disaster;destroy them with double destruction!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Thus said the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to me: “Go and stand in the People's Gate, by which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19377AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19377AM\"></sup>the kings of Judah enter and by which they go out, and in all the gates of Jerusalem,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and say: ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19378AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19378AN\"></sup>you kings of Judah, and all Judah, and all the inhabitants of Jerusalem, who enter by these gates.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Take care for the sake of your lives, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19379AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19379AO\"></sup>do not bear a burden on the Sabbath day or bring it in by the gates of Jerusalem.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And do not carry a burden out of your houses on the Sabbath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19380AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19380AP\"></sup>or do any work, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19380AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19380AQ\"></sup>keep the Sabbath day holy, as I commanded your fathers.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19381AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19381AR\"></sup>they did not listen or incline their ear, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19381AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19381AS\"></sup>but stiffened their neck, that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19381AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19381AT\"></sup>might not hear and receive instruction.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“‘But if you listen to me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19382AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19382AU\"></sup>bring in no burden by the gates of this city on the Sabbath day, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19382AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19382AV\"></sup>keep the Sabbath day holy and do no work on it,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19383AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19383AW\"></sup>there shall enter by the gates of this city kings and princes who sit on the throne of David, riding in chariots and on horses, they and their officials, the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem. And this city shall be inhabited forever.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And people shall come from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384AX\"></sup>the cities of Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384AY\"></sup>and the places around Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384AZ\"></sup>from the land of Benjamin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384BA\"></sup>from the Shephelah, from the hill country, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384BB\"></sup>and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384BC\"></sup>the Negeb, bringing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384BD\"></sup>burnt offerings and sacrifices, grain offerings and frankincense, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19384BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19384BE\"></sup>bringing thank offerings to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But if you do not listen to me, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19385BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19385BF\"></sup>keep the Sabbath day holy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19385BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19385BG\"></sup>and not to bear a burden and enter by the gates of Jerusalem on the Sabbath day, then I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19385BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19385BH\"></sup>kindle a fire in its gates, and it shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19385BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19385BI\"></sup>devour the palaces of Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19385BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19385BJ\"></sup>shall not be quenched.’”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Arise, and go down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19387A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19387A\"></sup>the potter's house, and there I will let you hear my words.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So I went down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19388B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19388B\"></sup>the potter's house, and there he was working at his wheel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the vessel he was making of clay was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19389C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19389C\"></sup>spoiled in the potter's hand, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19389D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19389D\"></sup>he reworked it into another vessel, as it seemed good to the potter to do.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“O house of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19391E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19391E\"></sup>can I not do with you as this potter has done? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19391F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19391F\"></sup>Behold, like the clay in the potter's hand, so are you in my hand, O house of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If at any time I declare concerning a nation or a kingdom, that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19392G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19392G\"></sup>pluck up and break down and destroy it,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and if that nation, concerning which I have spoken, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19393H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19393H\"></sup>turns from its evil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19393I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19393I\"></sup>I will relent of the disaster that I intended to do to it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And if at any time I declare concerning a nation or a kingdom that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19394J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19394J\"></sup>build and plant it,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and if it does evil in my sight, not listening to my voice, then I will relent of the good that I had intended to do to it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now, therefore, say to the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem: ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Behold, I am shaping disaster against you and devising a plan against you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19396K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19396K\"></sup>Return, every one from his evil way, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19396L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19396L\"></sup>amend your ways and your deeds.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But they say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19397M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19397M\"></sup>‘That is in vain! We will follow our own plans, and will every one act according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19397N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19397N\"></sup>the stubbornness of his evil heart.’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19398O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19398O\"></sup>Ask among the nations,Who has heard the like of this?The virgin Israelhas done <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19398P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19398P\"></sup>a very horrible thing.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Does the snow of Lebanon leavethe crags of Sirion?Do the mountain waters run dry,the cold flowing streams?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19400Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19400Q\"></sup>But my people have forgotten me;they make offerings to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19400R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19400R\"></sup>false gods;they made them stumble in their ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19400S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19400S\"></sup>in the ancient roads,and to walk into side roads,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19400T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19400T\"></sup>not the highway,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>making their land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19401U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19401U\"></sup>a horror,a thing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19401V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19401V\"></sup>to be hissed at forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19401W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19401W\"></sup>Everyone who passes by it is horrified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19401X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19401X\"></sup>and shakes his head.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19402Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19402Y\"></sup>Like the east wind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19402Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19402Z\"></sup>I will scatter thembefore the enemy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19402AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19402AA\"></sup>I will show them my back, not my face,in the day of their calamity.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19403AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19403AB\"></sup>“Come, let us make plots against Jeremiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19403AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19403AC\"></sup>for the law shall not perish from the priest, nor counsel from the wise, nor the word from the prophet. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19403AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19403AD\"></sup>Come, let us strike him with the tongue, and let us not pay attention to any of his words.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Hear me, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19404AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19404AE\"></sup>listen to the voice of my adversaries.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19405AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19405AF\"></sup>Should good be repaid with evil?Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19405AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19405AG\"></sup>they have dug a pit for my life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19405AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19405AH\"></sup>Remember how I stood before youto speak good for them,to turn away your wrath from them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19406AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19406AI\"></sup>deliver up their children to famine;give them over to the power of the sword;let their wives become childless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19406AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19406AJ\"></sup>and widowed.May their men meet death by pestilence,their youths be struck down by the sword in battle.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19407AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19407AK\"></sup>May a cry be heard from their houses,when you bring the plunderer suddenly upon them!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19407AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19407AL\"></sup>they have dug a pit to take me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19407AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19407AM\"></sup>and laid snares for my feet.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19408AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19408AN\"></sup>you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, knowall their plotting to kill me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19408AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19408AO\"></sup>Forgive not their iniquity,nor blot out their sin from your sight.Let them be overthrown before you;deal with them in the time of your anger."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Go, buy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19409A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19409A\"></sup>a potter's earthenware <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19409B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19409B\"></sup>flask, and take some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19409C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19409C\"></sup>the elders of the people and some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19409D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19409D\"></sup>the elders of the priests,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and go out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19410E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19410E\"></sup>to the Valley of the Son of Hinnom at the entry of the Potsherd Gate, and proclaim there the words that I tell you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You shall say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19411F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19411F\"></sup>‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19411G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19411G\"></sup>O kings of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem. Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Behold, I am bringing such disaster upon this place that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19411H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19411H\"></sup>the ears of everyone who hears of it will tingle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19412I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19412I\"></sup>Because the people have forsaken me and have profaned this place by making offerings in it to other gods whom neither they nor their fathers nor the kings of Judah have known; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19412J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19412J\"></sup>and because they have filled this place with the blood of innocents,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19413K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19413K\"></sup>and have built the high places of Baal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19413L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19413L\"></sup>to burn their sons in the fire as burnt offerings to Baal, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19413M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19413M\"></sup>which I did not command or decree, nor did it come into my mind—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19414N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19414N\"></sup>behold, days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when this place shall no more be called Topheth, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19414O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19414O\"></sup>the Valley of the Son of Hinnom, but the Valley of Slaughter.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And in this place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19415P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19415P\"></sup>I will make void the plans of Judah and Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19415Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19415Q\"></sup>and will cause their people to fall by the sword before their enemies, and by the hand of those who seek their life. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19415R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19415R\"></sup>I will give their dead bodies for food to the birds of the air and to the beasts of the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I will make this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19416S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19416S\"></sup>a horror, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19416T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19416T\"></sup>a thing to be hissed at. Everyone who passes by it will be horrified and will hiss because of all its wounds.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19417U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19417U\"></sup>And I will make them eat the flesh of their sons and their daughters, and everyone shall eat the flesh of his neighbor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19417V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19417V\"></sup>in the siege and in the distress, with which their enemies and those who seek their life afflict them.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19418W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19418W\"></sup>you shall break <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19418X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19418X\"></sup>the flask in the sight of the men who go with you,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: So will I break this people and this city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19419Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19419Y\"></sup>as one breaks a potter's vessel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19419Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19419Z\"></sup>so that it can never be mended. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19419AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19419AA\"></sup>Men shall bury in Topheth because there will be no place else to bury.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Thus will I do to this place, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and to its inhabitants, making this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19420AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19420AB\"></sup>like Topheth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The houses of Jerusalem and the houses of the kings of Judah—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19421AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19421AC\"></sup>all the houses on whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19421AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19421AD\"></sup>roofs offerings have been offered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19421AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19421AE\"></sup>to all the host of heaven, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19421AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19421AF\"></sup>drink offerings have been poured out to other gods—shall be defiled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19421AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19421AG\"></sup>like the place of Topheth.’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then Jeremiah came from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19422AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19422AH\"></sup>Topheth, where the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had sent him to prophesy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19422AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19422AI\"></sup>and he stood in the court of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house and said to all the people:",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, behold, I am bringing upon this city and upon all its towns all the disaster that I have pronounced against it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19423AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19423AJ\"></sup>because they have stiffened their neck, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19423AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19423AK\"></sup>refusing to hear my words.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19424A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19424A\"></sup>Pashhur the priest, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19424B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19424B\"></sup>Immer, who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19424C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19424C\"></sup>chief officer in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, heard Jeremiah prophesying these things.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19425D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19425D\"></sup>Pashhur beat Jeremiah the prophet, and put him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19425E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19425E\"></sup>in the stocks that were in the upper <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19425F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19425F\"></sup>Benjamin Gate of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The next day, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19426G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19426G\"></sup>Pashhur released Jeremiah from the stocks, Jeremiah said to him, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not call your name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19426H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19426H\"></sup>Pashhur, but Terror on Every Side.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Behold, I will make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19427I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19427I\"></sup>a terror to yourself and to all your friends. They shall fall by the sword of their enemies while you look on. And I will give all Judah into the hand of the king of Babylon. He shall carry them captive to Babylon, and shall strike them down with the sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Moreover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19428J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19428J\"></sup>I will give all the wealth of the city, all its gains, all its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19428K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19428K\"></sup>prized belongings, and all the treasures of the kings of Judah into the hand of their enemies, who shall plunder them and seize them and carry them to Babylon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19429L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19429L\"></sup>Pashhur, and all who dwell in your house, shall go into captivity. To Babylon you shall go, and there you shall die, and there you shall be buried, you and all your friends, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19429M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19429M\"></sup>to whom you have prophesied falsely.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19430N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19430N\"></sup>you have deceived me,and I was deceived;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19430O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19430O\"></sup>you are stronger than I,and you have prevailed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19430P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19430P\"></sup>I have become a laughingstock all the day;everyone mocks me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For whenever I speak, I cry out,I shout, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19431Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19431Q\"></sup>“Violence and destruction!”For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19431R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19431R\"></sup>the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has become for me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19431S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19431S\"></sup>a reproach and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19431T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19431T\"></sup>derision all day long.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If I say, “I will not mention him,or speak any more in his name,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19432U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19432U\"></sup>there is in my heart as it were a burning fireshut up in my bones,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19432V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19432V\"></sup>I am weary with holding it in,and I cannot.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433W\"></sup>For I hear many whispering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433X\"></sup>Terror is on every side!“Denounce him! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433Y\"></sup>Let us denounce him!”say all my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433Z\"></sup>close friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433AA\"></sup>watching for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433AB\"></sup>my fall.“Perhaps he will be deceived;then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19433AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19433AC\"></sup>we can overcome himand take our revenge on him.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19434AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19434AD\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with me as a dread warrior;therefore my persecutors will stumble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19434AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19434AE\"></sup>they will not overcome me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19434AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19434AF\"></sup>They will be greatly shamed,for they will not succeed.Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19434AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19434AG\"></sup>eternal dishonorwill never be forgotten.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, who tests the righteous,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19435AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19435AH\"></sup>who sees the heart and the mind,let me see your vengeance upon them,for to you have I committed my cause.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19436AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19436AI\"></sup>Sing to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!For he has delivered the life of the needyfrom the hand of evildoers.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19437AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19437AJ\"></sup>Cursed be the dayon which I was born!The day when my mother bore me,let it not be blessed!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Cursed be the man who brought the news to my father,“A son is born to you,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19438AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19438AK\"></sup>making him very glad.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let that man be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19439AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19439AL\"></sup>the citiesthat the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> overthrew without pity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19439AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19439AM\"></sup>let him hear a cry in the morningand an alarm at noon,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19440AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19440AN\"></sup>because he did not kill me in the womb;so my mother would have been my grave,and her womb forever great.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19441AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19441AO\"></sup>Why did I come out from the womb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19441AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19441AP\"></sup>to see toil and sorrow,and spend my days in shame?"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when King Zedekiah sent to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19442A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19442A\"></sup>Pashhur the son of Malchiah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19442B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19442B\"></sup>Zephaniah the priest, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19442C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19442C\"></sup>Maaseiah, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19443D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19443D\"></sup>“Inquire of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19443E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19443E\"></sup>for Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon is making war against us. Perhaps the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deal with us according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19443F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19443F\"></sup>all his wonderful deeds and will make him withdraw from us.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to them: “Thus you shall say to Zedekiah,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19445G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19445G\"></sup>Behold, I will turn back the weapons of war that are in your hands and with which you are fighting against the king of Babylon and against the Chaldeans who are besieging you outside the walls. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19445H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19445H\"></sup>And I will bring them together into the midst of this city.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I myself will fight against you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19446I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19446I\"></sup>with outstretched hand and strong arm, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19446J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19446J\"></sup>in anger and in fury and in great wrath.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I will strike down the inhabitants of this city, both man and beast. They shall die of a great pestilence.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Afterward, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19448K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19448K\"></sup>I will give Zedekiah king of Judah and his servants and the people in this city who survive the pestilence, sword, and famine into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and into the hand of their enemies, into the hand of those who seek their lives. He shall strike them down with the edge of the sword. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19448L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19448L\"></sup>He shall not pity them or spare them or have compassion.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And to this people you shall say: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19449M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19449M\"></sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19449N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19449N\"></sup>I set before you the way of life and the way of death.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He who stays in this city shall die <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19450O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19450O\"></sup>by the sword, by famine, and by pestilence, but he who goes out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19450P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19450P\"></sup>surrenders to the Chaldeans who are besieging you shall live <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19450Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19450Q\"></sup>and shall have his life as a prize of war.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19451R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19451R\"></sup>I have set my face against this city for harm and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19451S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19451S\"></sup>not for good, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19451T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19451T\"></sup>it shall be given into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he shall burn it with fire.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“And to the house of the king of Judah say, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>O house of David! Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19453U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19453U\"></sup>“‘Execute justice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19453V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19453V\"></sup>in the morning,and deliver from the hand of the oppressorhim who has been robbed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19453W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19453W\"></sup>lest my wrath go forth like fire,and burn with none to quench it,because of your evil deeds.’”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19454X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19454X\"></sup>“Behold, I am against you, O inhabitant of the valley,O rock of the plain,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;you who say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19454Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19454Y\"></sup>‘Who shall come down against us,or who shall enter our habitations?’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19455Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19455Z\"></sup>I will punish you according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19455AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19455AA\"></sup>the fruit of your deeds,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19455AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19455AB\"></sup>I will kindle a fire in her forest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19455AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19455AC\"></sup>and it shall devour all that is around her.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: “Go down to the house of the king of Judah and speak there this word,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19457A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19457A\"></sup>‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O king of Judah, who sits on the throne of David, you, and your servants, and your people who enter these gates.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19458B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19458B\"></sup>Do justice and righteousness, and deliver from the hand of the oppressor him who has been robbed. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19458C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19458C\"></sup>do no wrong or violence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19458D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19458D\"></sup>to the resident alien, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19458E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19458E\"></sup>the fatherless, and the widow, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19458F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19458F\"></sup>shed innocent blood in this place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For if you will indeed obey this word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19459G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19459G\"></sup>then there shall enter the gates of this house kings who sit on the throne of David, riding in chariots and on horses, they and their servants and their people.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But if you will not obey these words, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19460H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19460H\"></sup>swear by myself, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19460I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19460I\"></sup>this house shall become a desolation.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the house of the king of Judah:“‘You are like Gilead to me,like the summit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19461J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19461J\"></sup>Lebanon,yet surely I will make you a desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19461K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19461K\"></sup>an uninhabited city.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19462L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19462L\"></sup>I will prepare destroyers against you,each with his weapons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19462M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19462M\"></sup>and they shall cut down your choicest cedarsand cast them into the fire.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘And many nations will pass by this city, and every man will say to his neighbor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19463N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19463N\"></sup>“Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> dealt thus with this great city?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19464O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19464O\"></sup>And they will answer, “Because they have forsaken the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and worshiped other gods and served them.”’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19465P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19465P\"></sup>Weep not for him who is dead,nor grieve for him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19465Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19465Q\"></sup>but weep bitterly for him who goes away,for he shall return no moreto see his native land.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Shallum the son of Josiah, king of Judah, who reigned instead of Josiah his father, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19466R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19466R\"></sup>who went away from this place: “He shall return here no more,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19467S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19467S\"></sup>in the place where they have carried him captive, there shall he die, and he shall never see this land again.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19468T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19468T\"></sup>“Woe to him who builds his house by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19468U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19468U\"></sup>unrighteousness,and his upper rooms by injustice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19468V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19468V\"></sup>who makes his neighbor serve him for nothingand does not give him his wages,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>who says, ‘I will build myself a great housewith spacious upper rooms,’who cuts out windows for it,paneling it with cedarand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19469W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19469W\"></sup>painting it with vermilion.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do you think you are a kingbecause you compete in cedar?Did not your father eat and drinkand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19470X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19470X\"></sup>do justice and righteousness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19470Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19470Y\"></sup>Then it was well with him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19471Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19471Z\"></sup>He judged the cause of the poor and needy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19471AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19471AA\"></sup>then it was well.Is not this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19471AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19471AB\"></sup>to know me?declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But you have eyes and heartonly for your dishonest gain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19472AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19472AC\"></sup>for shedding innocent blood,and for practicing oppression and violence.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19473AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19473AD\"></sup>“They shall not lament for him, saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19473AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19473AE\"></sup>‘Ah, my brother!’ or ‘Ah, sister!’They shall not lament for him, saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19473AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19473AF\"></sup>‘Ah, lord!’ or ‘Ah, his majesty!’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>With the burial of a donkey <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19474AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19474AG\"></sup>he shall be buried,dragged and dumped beyond the gates of Jerusalem.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Go up to Lebanon, and cry out,and lift up your voice in Bashan;cry out from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19475AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19475AH\"></sup>Abarim,for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19475AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19475AI\"></sup>your lovers are destroyed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I spoke to you in your prosperity,but you said, ‘I will not listen.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19476AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19476AJ\"></sup>This has been your way from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19476AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19476AK\"></sup>your youth,that you have not obeyed my voice.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19477AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19477AL\"></sup>The wind shall shepherd all your shepherds,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19477AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19477AM\"></sup>your lovers shall go into captivity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19477AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19477AN\"></sup>then you will be ashamed and confoundedbecause of all your evil.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>O inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19478AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19478AO\"></sup>Lebanon,nested among the cedars,how you will be pitied when pangs come upon you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19478AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19478AP\"></sup>pain as of a woman in labor!”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19479AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19479AQ\"></sup>“As I live, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, though Coniah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19479AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19479AR\"></sup>the signet ring on my right hand, yet I would tear you off",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19480AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19480AS\"></sup>give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19480AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19480AT\"></sup>into the hand of those who seek your life, into the hand of those of whom you are afraid, even into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and into the hand of the Chaldeans.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19481AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19481AU\"></sup>I will hurl you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19481AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19481AV\"></sup>the mother who bore you into another country, where you were not born, and there you shall die.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But to the land to which they will long to return, there they shall not return.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Is this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19483AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19483AW\"></sup>Coniah a despised, broken pot,a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19483AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19483AX\"></sup>vessel no one cares for?Why are he and his children hurled and castinto a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19483AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19483AY\"></sup>land that they do not know?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19484AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19484AZ\"></sup>O land, land, land,hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Write this man down as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19485BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19485BA\"></sup>childless,a man who shall not succeed in his days,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19485BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19485BB\"></sup>for none of his offspring shall succeed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19485BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19485BC\"></sup>in sitting on the throne of Davidand ruling again in Judah.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19486A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19486A\"></sup>“Woe to the shepherds who destroy and scatter the sheep of my pasture!” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19487B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19487B\"></sup>the shepherds who care for my people: “You have scattered my flock and have driven them away, and you have not attended to them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19487C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19487C\"></sup>Behold, I will attend to you for your evil deeds, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19488D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19488D\"></sup>Then I will gather the remnant of my flock <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19488E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19488E\"></sup>out of all the countries where I have driven them, and I will bring them back to their fold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19488F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19488F\"></sup>and they shall be fruitful and multiply.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19489G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19489G\"></sup>I will set shepherds over them who will care for them, and they shall fear no more, nor be dismayed, neither shall any be missing, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19490H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19490H\"></sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I will raise up for David a righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19490I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19490I\"></sup>Branch, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19490J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19490J\"></sup>he shall reign as king and deal wisely, and shall execute justice and righteousness in the land.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In his days Judah will be saved, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19491K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19491K\"></sup>Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19491L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19491L\"></sup>dwell securely. And this is the name by which he will be called: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19491M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19491M\"></sup>‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our righteousness.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19492N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19492N\"></sup>“Therefore, behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when they shall no longer say, ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives who brought up the people of Israel out of the land of Egypt,’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>but ‘As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives who brought up and led the offspring of the house of Israel out of the north country and out of all the countries where he had driven them.’ Then they shall dwell in their own land.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Concerning the prophets:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19494O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19494O\"></sup>My heart is broken within me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19494P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19494P\"></sup>all my bones shake;I am like a drunken man,like a man overcome by wine,because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and because of his holy words.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19495Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19495Q\"></sup>For the land is full of adulterers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19495R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19495R\"></sup>because of the curse <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19495S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19495S\"></sup>the land mourns,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19495T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19495T\"></sup>the pastures of the wilderness are dried up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19495U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19495U\"></sup>Their course is evil,and their might is not right.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19496V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19496V\"></sup>“Both prophet and priest are ungodly;even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19496W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19496W\"></sup>in my house I have found their evil,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19497X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19497X\"></sup>Therefore their way shall be to themlike slippery paths <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19497Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19497Y\"></sup>in the darkness,into which they shall be driven and fall,for I will bring disaster upon them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19497Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19497Z\"></sup>in the year of their punishment,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In the prophets of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19498AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19498AA\"></sup>Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19498AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19498AB\"></sup>I saw an unsavory thing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19498AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19498AC\"></sup>they prophesied by Baal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19498AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19498AD\"></sup>and led my people Israel astray.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But in the prophets of JerusalemI have seen a horrible thing:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19499AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19499AE\"></sup>they commit adultery and walk in lies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19499AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19499AF\"></sup>they strengthen the hands of evildoers,so that no one turns from his evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19499AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19499AG\"></sup>all of them have become like Sodom to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19499AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19499AH\"></sup>and its inhabitants like Gomorrah.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts concerning the prophets:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19500AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19500AI\"></sup>“Behold, I will feed them with bitter food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19500AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19500AJ\"></sup>and give them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19500AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19500AK\"></sup>poisoned water to drink,for from the prophets of Jerusalemungodliness has gone out into all the land.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: “Do not listen to the words of the prophets who prophesy to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19501AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19501AL\"></sup>filling you with vain hopes. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19501AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19501AM\"></sup>They speak visions of their own minds, not from the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They say continually to those who despise the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19502AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19502AN\"></sup>‘It shall be well with you’; and to everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19502AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19502AO\"></sup>stubbornly follows his own heart, they say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19502AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19502AP\"></sup>‘No disaster shall come upon you.’”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19503AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19503AQ\"></sup>who among them has stood in the council of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>to see and to hear his word,or who has paid attention to his word and listened?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19504AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19504AR\"></sup>Behold, the storm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!Wrath has gone forth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19504AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19504AS\"></sup>a whirling tempest;it will burst upon the head of the wicked.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19505AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19505AT\"></sup>The anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not turn backuntil he has executed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19505AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19505AU\"></sup>accomplishedthe intents of his heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19505AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19505AV\"></sup>In the latter days you will understand it clearly.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19506AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19506AW\"></sup>“I did not send the prophets,yet they ran;I did not speak to them,yet they prophesied.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19507AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19507AX\"></sup>But if they had stood in my council,then they would have proclaimed my words to my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19507AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19507AY\"></sup>and they would have turned them from their evil way,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19507AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19507AZ\"></sup>from the evil of their deeds.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19508BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19508BA\"></sup>“Am I a God at hand, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and not a God far away?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19509BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19509BB\"></sup>Can a man hide himself in secret places so that I cannot see him? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19509BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19509BC\"></sup>Do I not fill heaven and earth? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I have heard what the prophets have said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19510BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19510BD\"></sup>who prophesy lies in my name, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19510BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19510BE\"></sup>‘I have dreamed, I have dreamed!’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>How long shall there be lies in the heart of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19511BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19511BF\"></sup>the prophets who prophesy lies, and who prophesy the deceit of their own heart,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>who think to make my people forget my name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19512BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19512BG\"></sup>by their dreams that they tell one another, even as their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19512BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19512BH\"></sup>fathers forgot my name for Baal?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19513BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19513BI\"></sup>Let the prophet who has a dream <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19513BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19513BJ\"></sup>tell the dream, but let him who has my word speak my word faithfully. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19513BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19513BK\"></sup>What has straw in common with wheat? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19514BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19514BL\"></sup>Is not my word like fire, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19514BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19514BM\"></sup>like a hammer that breaks the rock in pieces?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19515BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19515BN\"></sup>Therefore, behold, I am against the prophets, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who steal my words from one another.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Behold, I am against the prophets, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who use their tongues and declare, ‘declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Behold, I am against those who prophesy lying dreams, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and who tell them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19517BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19517BO\"></sup>lead my people astray by their lies and their recklessness, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19517BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19517BP\"></sup>I did not send them or charge them. So they do not profit this people at all, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19518BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19518BQ\"></sup>“When one of this people, or a prophet or a priest asks you, ‘What is the burden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’ you shall say to them, ‘You are the burden, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19518BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19518BR\"></sup>I will cast you off, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And as for the prophet, priest, or one of the people who says, ‘The burden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19519BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19519BS\"></sup>I will punish that man and his household.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Thus shall you say, every one to his neighbor and every one to his brother, ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered?’ or ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken?’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But ‘the burden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’ you shall mention no more, for the burden is every man's own word, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19521BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19521BT\"></sup>you pervert the words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19521BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19521BU\"></sup>the living God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, our God.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Thus you shall say to the prophet, ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answered you?’ or ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken?’",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But if you say, ‘The burden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘Because you have said these words, “The burden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,” when I sent to you, saying, “You shall not say, ‘The burden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>therefore, behold, I will surely lift you up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19524BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19524BV\"></sup>cast you away from my presence, you and the city that I gave to you and your fathers.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19525BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19525BW\"></sup>And I will bring upon you everlasting reproach and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19525BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19525BX\"></sup>perpetual shame, which shall not be forgotten.’”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19526A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19526A\"></sup>After Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon had taken into exile from Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19526B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19526B\"></sup>Jeconiah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19526C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19526C\"></sup>the officials of Judah, the craftsmen, and the metal workers, and had brought them to Babylon, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me this vision: behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19526D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19526D\"></sup>two baskets of figs placed before the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>One basket had very good figs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19527E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19527E\"></sup>like first-ripe figs, but the other basket had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19527F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19527F\"></sup>very bad figs, so bad that they could not be eaten.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “What do you see, Jeremiah?” I said, “Figs, the good figs very good, and the bad figs very bad, so bad that they cannot be eaten.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: Like these good figs, so I will regard as good the exiles from Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19530G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19530G\"></sup>whom I have sent away from this place to the land of the Chaldeans.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19531H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19531H\"></sup>I will set my eyes on them for good, and I will bring them back to this land. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19531I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19531I\"></sup>I will build them up, and not tear them down; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19531J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19531J\"></sup>I will plant them, and not pluck them up.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19532K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19532K\"></sup>I will give them a heart to know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19532L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19532L\"></sup>and they shall be my people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19532M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19532M\"></sup>and I will be their God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19532N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19532N\"></sup>for they shall return to me with their whole heart.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19533O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19533O\"></sup>the bad figs that are so bad they cannot be eaten, so will I treat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19533P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19533P\"></sup>Zedekiah the king of Judah, his officials, the remnant of Jerusalem who remain in this land, and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19533Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19533Q\"></sup>dwell in the land of Egypt.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19534R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19534R\"></sup>a horror to all the kingdoms of the earth, to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19534S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19534S\"></sup>a reproach, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19534T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19534T\"></sup>a byword, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19534U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19534U\"></sup>a taunt, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19534V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19534V\"></sup>a curse in all the places where I shall drive them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I will send <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19535W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19535W\"></sup>sword, famine, and pestilence upon them, until they shall be utterly destroyed from the land that I gave to them and their fathers.”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19536A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19536A\"></sup>The word that came to Jeremiah concerning all the people of Judah, in the fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah (that was the first year of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon),",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>which Jeremiah the prophet spoke to all the people of Judah and all the inhabitants of Jerusalem:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For twenty-three years, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19538B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19538B\"></sup>from the thirteenth year of Josiah the son of Amon, king of Judah, to this day, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has come to me, and I have spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19538C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19538C\"></sup>persistently to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19538D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19538D\"></sup>but you have not listened.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19539E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19539E\"></sup>You have neither listened nor inclined your ears to hear, although the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19539F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19539F\"></sup>persistently sent to you all his servants the prophets,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19540G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19540G\"></sup>‘Turn now, every one of you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19540H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19540H\"></sup>from his evil way and evil deeds, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19540I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19540I\"></sup>dwell upon the land that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given to you and your fathers from of old and forever.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19541J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19541J\"></sup>Do not go after other gods to serve and worship them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19541K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19541K\"></sup>or provoke me to anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19541L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19541L\"></sup>with the work of your hands. Then I will do you no harm.’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19542M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19542M\"></sup>Yet you have not listened to me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19542N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19542N\"></sup>that you might provoke me to anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19542O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19542O\"></sup>with the work of your hands to your own harm.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: Because you have not obeyed my words,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19544P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19544P\"></sup>behold, I will send for all the tribes of the north, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and for Nebuchadnezzar the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19544Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19544Q\"></sup>my servant, and I will bring them against this land and its inhabitants, and against all these surrounding nations. I will devote them to destruction, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19544R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19544R\"></sup>and make them a horror, a hissing, and an everlasting desolation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Moreover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19545S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19545S\"></sup>I will banish from them the voice of mirth and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19545T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19545T\"></sup>the grinding of the millstones and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19545U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19545U\"></sup>the light of the lamp.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19546V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19546V\"></sup>This whole land shall become a ruin and a waste, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19546W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19546W\"></sup>these nations shall serve the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19546X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19546X\"></sup>seventy years.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19547Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19547Y\"></sup>seventy years are completed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19547Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19547Z\"></sup>I will punish the king of Babylon and that nation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19547AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19547AA\"></sup>the land of the Chaldeans, for their iniquity, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19547AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19547AB\"></sup>making the land an everlasting waste.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will bring upon that land all the words that I have uttered against it, everything written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19548AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19548AC\"></sup>in this book, which Jeremiah prophesied against all the nations.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19549AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19549AD\"></sup>For many nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19549AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19549AE\"></sup>and great kings shall make slaves even of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19549AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19549AF\"></sup>and I will recompense them according to their deeds and the work of their hands.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, said to me: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19550AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19550AG\"></sup>“Take from my hand this cup of the wine of wrath, and make all the nations to whom I send you drink it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They shall drink and stagger and be crazed because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19551AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19551AH\"></sup>the sword that I am sending among them.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So I took the cup from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s hand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19552AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19552AI\"></sup>and made all the nations to whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent me drink it:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19553AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19553AJ\"></sup>Jerusalem and the cities of Judah, its kings and officials, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19553AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19553AK\"></sup>to make them a desolation and a waste, a hissing and a curse, as at this day;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19554AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19554AL\"></sup>Pharaoh king of Egypt, his servants, his officials, all his people,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19555AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19555AM\"></sup>all the mixed tribes among them; all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19555AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19555AN\"></sup>the land of Uz and all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19555AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19555AO\"></sup>the land of the Philistines (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19555AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19555AP\"></sup>Ashkelon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19555AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19555AQ\"></sup>Gaza, Ekron, and the remnant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19555AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19555AR\"></sup>Ashdod);",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19556AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19556AS\"></sup>Edom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19556AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19556AT\"></sup>Moab, and the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19556AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19556AU\"></sup>Ammon;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19557AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19557AV\"></sup>Tyre, all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19557AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19557AW\"></sup>Sidon, and the kings of the coastland across <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19557AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19557AX\"></sup>the sea;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19558AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19558AY\"></sup>Dedan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19558AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19558AZ\"></sup>Tema, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19558BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19558BA\"></sup>Buz, and all who cut <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19558BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19558BB\"></sup>the corners of their hair;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19559BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19559BC\"></sup>kings of Arabia and all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19559BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19559BD\"></sup>the mixed tribes who dwell in the desert;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>all the kings of Zimri, all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19560BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19560BE\"></sup>Elam, and all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19560BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19560BF\"></sup>Media;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>all the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19561BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19561BG\"></sup>the north, far and near, one after another, and all the kingdoms of the world that are on the face of the earth. And after them the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19561BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19561BH\"></sup>Babylon shall drink.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Then you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19562BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19562BI\"></sup>Drink, be drunk and vomit, fall and rise no more, because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19562BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19562BJ\"></sup>the sword that I am sending among you.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“And if they refuse to accept the cup from your hand to drink, then you shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19563BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19563BK\"></sup>You must drink!",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19564BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19564BL\"></sup>I begin to work disaster at the city that is called by my name, and shall you go unpunished? You shall not go unpunished, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19564BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19564BM\"></sup>for I am summoning a sword against all the inhabitants of the earth, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“You, therefore, shall prophesy against them all these words, and say to them:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19565BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19565BN\"></sup>“‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will roar from on high,and from his holy habitation utter his voice;he will roar mightily against his fold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19565BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19565BO\"></sup>and shout, like those who tread grapes,against all the inhabitants of the earth.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The clamor will resound to the ends of the earth,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19566BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19566BP\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has an indictment against the nations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19566BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19566BQ\"></sup>he is entering into judgment with all flesh,and the wicked he will put to the sword,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:Behold, disaster is going forthfrom nation to nation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19567BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19567BR\"></sup>and a great tempest is stirring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19567BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19567BS\"></sup>from the farthest parts of the earth!",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19568BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19568BT\"></sup>“And those pierced by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on that day shall extend from one end of the earth to the other. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19568BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19568BU\"></sup>They shall not be lamented, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19568BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19568BV\"></sup>or gathered, or buried; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19568BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19568BW\"></sup>they shall be dung on the surface of the ground.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19569BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19569BX\"></sup>“Wail, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19569BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19569BY\"></sup>you shepherds, and cry out,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19569BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19569BZ\"></sup>and roll in ashes, you lords of the flock,for the days of your slaughter and dispersion have come,and you shall fall like a choice vessel.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>No refuge will remain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19570CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19570CA\"></sup>for the shepherds,nor escape for the lords of the flock.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>A voice—the cry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19571CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19571CB\"></sup>of the shepherds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19571CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19571CC\"></sup>and the wail of the lords of the flock!For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is laying waste their pasture,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19572CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19572CD\"></sup>and the peaceful folds are devastated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19572CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19572CE\"></sup>because of the fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Like a lion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19573CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19573CF\"></sup>he has left his lair,for their land has become a wastebecause of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19573CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19573CG\"></sup>the sword of the oppressor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19573CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19573CH\"></sup>and because of his fierce anger.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19574A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19574A\"></sup>In the beginning of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19574B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19574B\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, this word came from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19575C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19575C\"></sup>Stand in the court of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house, and speak to all the cities of Judah that come to worship in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19575D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19575D\"></sup>all the words that I command you to speak to them; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19575E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19575E\"></sup>do not hold back a word.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19576F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19576F\"></sup>It may be they will listen, and every one turn from his evil way, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19576G\"></sup>that I may relent of the disaster that I intend to do to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19576H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19576H\"></sup>because of their evil deeds.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You shall say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19577I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19577I\"></sup>If you will not listen to me, to walk in my law that I have set before you,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19578J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19578J\"></sup>and to listen to the words of my servants the prophets whom I send to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19578K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19578K\"></sup>urgently, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19578L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19578L\"></sup>though you have not listened,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>then I will make this house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19579M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19579M\"></sup>like Shiloh, and I will make this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19579N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19579N\"></sup>a curse for all the nations of the earth.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19580O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19580O\"></sup>The priests and the prophets and all the people heard Jeremiah speaking these words in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And when Jeremiah had finished speaking all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded him to speak to all the people, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19581P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19581P\"></sup>the priests and the prophets and all the people laid hold of him, saying, “You shall die!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Why have you prophesied in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying, ‘This house shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19582Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19582Q\"></sup>like Shiloh, and this city shall be desolate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19582R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19582R\"></sup>without inhabitant’?” And all the people gathered around Jeremiah in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19583S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19583S\"></sup>the officials of Judah heard these things, they came up from the king's house to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and took their seat in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19583T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19583T\"></sup>entry of the New Gate of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19584U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19584U\"></sup>the priests and the prophets said to the officials and to all the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19584V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19584V\"></sup>“This man deserves the sentence of death, because he has prophesied against this city, as you have heard with your own ears.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Jeremiah spoke to all the officials and all the people, saying, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent me to prophesy against this house and this city all the words you have heard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19586W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19586W\"></sup>mend your ways and your deeds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19586X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19586X\"></sup>and obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19586Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19586Y\"></sup>and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will relent of the disaster that he has pronounced against you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19587Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19587Z\"></sup>But as for me, behold, I am in your hands. Do with me as seems good and right to you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Only know for certain that if you put me to death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19588AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19588AA\"></sup>you will bring innocent blood upon yourselves and upon this city and its inhabitants, for in truth the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent me to you to speak all these words in your ears.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19589AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19589AB\"></sup>Then the officials and all the people said to the priests and the prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19589AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19589AC\"></sup>“This man does not deserve the sentence of death, for he has spoken to us in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19590AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19590AD\"></sup>And certain of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19590AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19590AE\"></sup>the elders of the land arose and spoke to all the assembled people, saying,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Micah of Moresheth prophesied in the days of Hezekiah king of Judah, and said to all the people of Judah: ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19591AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19591AF\"></sup>“‘Zion shall be plowed as a field;Jerusalem shall become a heap of ruins,and the mountain of the house a wooded height.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Did Hezekiah king of Judah and all Judah put him to death? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19592AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19592AG\"></sup>Did he not fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and entreat the favor of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19592AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19592AH\"></sup>and did not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> relent of the disaster that he had pronounced against them? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19592AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19592AI\"></sup>But we are about to bring great disaster upon ourselves.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>There was another man who prophesied in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Uriah the son of Shemaiah from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19593AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19593AJ\"></sup>Kiriath-jearim. He prophesied against this city and against this land in words like those of Jeremiah.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19594AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19594AK\"></sup>King Jehoiakim, with all his warriors and all the officials, heard his words, the king sought to put him to death. But when Uriah heard of it, he was afraid and fled and escaped to Egypt.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19595AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19595AL\"></sup>King Jehoiakim sent to Egypt certain men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19595AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19595AM\"></sup>Elnathan the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19595AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19595AN\"></sup>Achbor and others with him,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and they took Uriah from Egypt and brought him to King Jehoiakim, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19596AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19596AO\"></sup>who struck him down with the sword and dumped his dead body into the burial place of the common people.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19597AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19597AP\"></sup>Ahikam the son of Shaphan was with Jeremiah so that he was not given over to the people to be put to death."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>In the beginning of the reign of Zedekiah the son of Josiah, king of Judah, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19599A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19599A\"></sup>“Make yourself straps and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19599B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19599B\"></sup>yoke-bars, and put them on your neck.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Send word to the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19600C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19600C\"></sup>Edom, the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19600D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19600D\"></sup>Moab, the king of the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19600E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19600E\"></sup>Ammon, the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19600F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19600F\"></sup>Tyre, and the king of Sidon by the hand of the envoys who have come to Jerusalem to Zedekiah king of Judah.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Give them this charge for their masters: ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: This is what you shall say to your masters:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“It is I who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19602G\"></sup>by my great power and my outstretched arm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19602H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19602H\"></sup>have made the earth, with the men and animals that are on the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19602I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19602I\"></sup>and I give it to whomever it seems right to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19603J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19603J\"></sup>Now I have given all these lands into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar, the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19603K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19603K\"></sup>my servant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19603L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19603L\"></sup>and I have given him also the beasts of the field to serve him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19604M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19604M\"></sup>All the nations shall serve him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19604N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19604N\"></sup>his son and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19604O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19604O\"></sup>his grandson, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19604P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19604P\"></sup>until the time of his own land comes. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19604Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19604Q\"></sup>Then many nations and great kings shall make him their slave.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘“But if any nation or kingdom will not serve this Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19605R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19605R\"></sup>and put its neck under the yoke of the king of Babylon, I will punish that nation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19605S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19605S\"></sup>with the sword, with famine, and with pestilence, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, until I have consumed it by his hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19606T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19606T\"></sup>do not listen to your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19606U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19606U\"></sup>prophets, your diviners, your dreamers, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19606V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19606V\"></sup>fortune-tellers, or your sorcerers, who are saying to you, ‘You shall not serve the king of Babylon.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19607W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19607W\"></sup>For it is a lie that they are prophesying to you, with the result that you will be removed far from your land, and I will drive you out, and you will perish.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19608X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19608X\"></sup>But any nation that will bring its neck under the yoke of the king of Babylon and serve him, I will leave on its own land, to work it and dwell there, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19609Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19609Y\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah I spoke in like manner: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19609Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19609Z\"></sup>“Bring your necks under the yoke of the king of Babylon, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19609AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19609AA\"></sup>serve him and his people and live.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19610AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19610AB\"></sup>Why will you and your people die <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19610AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19610AC\"></sup>by the sword, by famine, and by pestilence, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19610AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19610AD\"></sup>as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken concerning any nation that will not serve the king of Babylon?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19611AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19611AE\"></sup>Do not listen to the words of the prophets who are saying to you, ‘You shall not serve the king of Babylon,’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19611AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19611AF\"></sup>for it is a lie that they are prophesying to you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I have not sent them, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19612AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19612AG\"></sup>they are prophesying falsely in my name, with the result that I will drive you out and you will perish, you and the prophets who are prophesying to you.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then I spoke to the priests and to all this people, saying, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19613AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19613AH\"></sup>Do not listen to the words of your prophets who are prophesying to you, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19613AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19613AI\"></sup>‘Behold, the vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house will now shortly be brought back from Babylon,’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19613AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19613AJ\"></sup>for it is a lie that they are prophesying to you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19614AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19614AK\"></sup>Do not listen to them; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19614AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19614AL\"></sup>serve the king of Babylon and live. Why should this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19614AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19614AM\"></sup>become a desolation?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If they are prophets, and if the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is with them, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19615AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19615AN\"></sup>let them intercede with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19615AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19615AO\"></sup>that the vessels that are left in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, in the house of the king of Judah, and in Jerusalem may not go to Babylon.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19616AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19616AP\"></sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts concerning the pillars, the sea, the stands, and the rest of the vessels that are left in this city,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon did not take away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19617AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19617AQ\"></sup>when he took into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon Jeconiah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, and all the nobles of Judah and Jerusalem—",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19618AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19618AR\"></sup>concerning the vessels that are left in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, in the house of the king of Judah, and in Jerusalem:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19619AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19619AS\"></sup>They shall be carried to Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19619AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19619AT\"></sup>and remain there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19619AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19619AU\"></sup>until the day when I visit them, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19619AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19619AV\"></sup>Then I will bring them back <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19619AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19619AW\"></sup>and restore them to this place.”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>In that same year, at the beginning of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19620A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19620A\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah, in the fifth month of the fourth year, Hananiah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19620B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19620B\"></sup>Azzur, the prophet from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19620C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19620C\"></sup>Gibeon, spoke to me in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, in the presence of the priests and all the people, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19621D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19621D\"></sup>I have broken the yoke of the king of Babylon.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19622E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19622E\"></sup>Within <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19622F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19622F\"></sup>two years I will bring back to this place all the vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house, which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon took away from this place and carried to Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will also bring back to this place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19623G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19623G\"></sup>Jeconiah the son of Jehoiakim, king of Judah, and all the exiles from Judah who went to Babylon, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19623H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19623H\"></sup>for I will break the yoke of the king of Babylon.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the prophet Jeremiah spoke to Hananiah the prophet in the presence of the priests and all the people who were standing in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and the prophet Jeremiah said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19625I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19625I\"></sup>“Amen! May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> do so; may the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> make the words that you have prophesied come true, and bring back to this place from Babylon the vessels of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and all the exiles.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet hear now this word that I speak in your hearing and in the hearing of all the people.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19627J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19627J\"></sup>The prophets who preceded you and me from ancient times prophesied war, famine, and pestilence against many countries and great kingdoms.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19628K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19628K\"></sup>As for the prophet who prophesies peace, when the word of that prophet comes to pass, then it will be known that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has truly sent the prophet.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the prophet Hananiah took the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19629L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19629L\"></sup>yoke-bars from the neck of Jeremiah the prophet and broke them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And Hananiah spoke in the presence of all the people, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19630M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19630M\"></sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19630N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19630N\"></sup>Even so will I break the yoke of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon from the neck of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19630O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19630O\"></sup>all the nations within two years.” But Jeremiah the prophet went his way.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Sometime after the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19631P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19631P\"></sup>Hananiah had broken the yoke-bars from off the neck of Jeremiah the prophet, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Go, tell Hananiah, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: You have broken wooden bars, but you have made in their place bars of iron.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: I have put upon the neck of all these nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19633Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19633Q\"></sup>an iron yoke to serve Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19633R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19633R\"></sup>and they shall serve him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19633S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19633S\"></sup>for I have given to him even the beasts of the field.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And Jeremiah the prophet said to the prophet Hananiah, “Listen, Hananiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19634T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19634T\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not sent you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19634U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19634U\"></sup>and you have made this people trust in a lie.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: ‘Behold, I will remove you from the face of the earth. This year you shall die, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19635V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19635V\"></sup>because you have uttered rebellion against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In that same year, in the seventh month, the prophet Hananiah died."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>These are the words of the letter that Jeremiah the prophet sent from Jerusalem to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19637A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19637A\"></sup>the surviving elders of the exiles, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19637B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19637B\"></sup>the priests, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19637C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19637C\"></sup>the prophets, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19637D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19637D\"></sup>all the people, whom Nebuchadnezzar had taken into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This was after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19638E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19638E\"></sup>King Jeconiah and the queen mother, the eunuchs, the officials of Judah and Jerusalem, the craftsmen, and the metal workers had departed from Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The letter was sent by the hand of Elasah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19639F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19639F\"></sup>Shaphan and Gemariah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19639G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19639G\"></sup>Hilkiah, whom Zedekiah king of Judah sent to Babylon to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon. It said:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, to all the exiles whom I have sent into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19641H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19641H\"></sup>Build houses and live in them; plant gardens and eat their produce.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Take wives and have sons and daughters; take wives for your sons, and give your daughters in marriage, that they may bear sons and daughters; multiply there, and do not decrease.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But seek the welfare of the city where I have sent you into exile, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19643I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19643I\"></sup>pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on its behalf, for in its welfare you will find your welfare.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19644J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19644J\"></sup>Do not let your prophets and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19644K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19644K\"></sup>your diviners who are among you deceive you, and do not listen to the dreams that they dream,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19645L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19645L\"></sup>it is a lie that they are prophesying to you in my name; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19645M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19645M\"></sup>I did not send them, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19646N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19646N\"></sup>When seventy years are completed for Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19646O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19646O\"></sup>I will visit you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19646P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19646P\"></sup>and I will fulfill to you my promise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19646Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19646Q\"></sup>and bring you back to this place.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19647R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19647R\"></sup>For I know the plans I have for you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, plans for welfare and not for evil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19647S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19647S\"></sup>to give you a future and a hope.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19648T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19648T\"></sup>Then you will call upon me and come and pray to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19648U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19648U\"></sup>and I will hear you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19649V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19649V\"></sup>You will seek me and find me, when you seek me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19649W\"></sup>with all your heart.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will be found by you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19650X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19650X\"></sup>and I will restore your fortunes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19650Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19650Y\"></sup>gather you from all the nations and all the places <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19650Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19650Z\"></sup>where I have driven you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I will bring you back to the place from which I sent you into exile.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Because you have said, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has raised up prophets for us in Babylon,’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19652AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19652AA\"></sup>the king who sits on the throne of David, and concerning all the people who dwell in this city, your kinsmen who did not go out with you into exile:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, behold, I am sending on them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19653AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19653AB\"></sup>sword, famine, and pestilence, and I will make them like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19653AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19653AC\"></sup>vile figs that are so rotten they cannot be eaten.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will pursue them with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19654AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19654AD\"></sup>sword, famine, and pestilence, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19654AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19654AE\"></sup>and will make them a horror to all the kingdoms of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19654AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19654AF\"></sup>to be a curse, a terror, a hissing, and a reproach among all the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19654AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19654AG\"></sup>where I have driven them,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>because they did not pay attention to my words, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19655AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19655AH\"></sup>that I persistently sent to you by my servants the prophets, but you would not listen, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you exiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19656AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19656AI\"></sup>whom I sent away from Jerusalem to Babylon:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, concerning Ahab the son of Kolaiah and Zedekiah the son of Maaseiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19657AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19657AJ\"></sup>who are prophesying a lie to you in my name: Behold, I will deliver them into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and he shall strike them down before your eyes.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19658AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19658AK\"></sup>Because of them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19658AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19658AL\"></sup>this curse shall be used by all the exiles from Judah in Babylon: “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> make you like Zedekiah and Ahab, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19658AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19658AM\"></sup>whom the king of Babylon roasted in the fire,”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>because they have done an outrageous thing in Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19659AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19659AN\"></sup>they have committed adultery with their neighbors' wives, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19659AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19659AO\"></sup>they have spoken in my name lying words that I did not command them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19659AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19659AP\"></sup>I am the one who knows, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19659AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19659AQ\"></sup>and I am witness, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19660AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19660AR\"></sup>Shemaiah of Nehelam you shall say:",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: You have sent letters in your name to all the people who are in Jerusalem, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19661AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19661AS\"></sup>Zephaniah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19661AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19661AT\"></sup>Maaseiah the priest, and to all the priests, saying,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made you priest instead of Jehoiada the priest, to have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19662AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19662AU\"></sup>charge in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19662AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19662AV\"></sup>over every madman who prophesies, to put him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19662AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19662AW\"></sup>the stocks and neck irons.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now why have you not rebuked Jeremiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19663AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19663AX\"></sup>of Anathoth who is prophesying to you?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For he has sent to us in Babylon, saying, “Your exile will be long; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19664AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19664AY\"></sup>build houses and live in them, and plant gardens and eat their produce.”’”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19665AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19665AZ\"></sup>Zephaniah the priest read this letter in the hearing of Jeremiah the prophet.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19666BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19666BA\"></sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Send to all the exiles, saying, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19667BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19667BB\"></sup>Shemaiah of Nehelam: Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19667BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19667BC\"></sup>Shemaiah had prophesied to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19667BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19667BD\"></sup>when I did not send him, and has made you trust in a lie,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: Behold, I will punish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19668BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19668BE\"></sup>Shemaiah of Nehelam and his descendants. He shall not have anyone living among this people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19668BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19668BF\"></sup>and he shall not see the good that I will do to my people, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19668BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19668BG\"></sup>for he has spoken rebellion against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19670A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19670A\"></sup>Write in a book all the words that I have spoken to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19671B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19671B\"></sup>For behold, days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19671C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19671C\"></sup>when I will restore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19671D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19671D\"></sup>the fortunes of my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19671E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19671E\"></sup>Israel and Judah, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19671F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19671F\"></sup>and I will bring them back to the land that I gave to their fathers, and they shall take possession of it.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>These are the words that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19672G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19672G\"></sup>Israel and Judah:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:We have heard a cry of panic,of terror, and no peace.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Ask now, and see,can a man bear a child?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19674H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19674H\"></sup>Why then do I see every manwith his hands on his stomach <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19674I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19674I\"></sup>like a woman in labor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19674J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19674J\"></sup>Why has every face turned pale?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Alas! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19675K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19675K\"></sup>That day is so great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19675L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19675L\"></sup>there is none like it;it is a time of distress for Jacob;yet he shall be saved out of it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And it shall come to pass in that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19676M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19676M\"></sup>break his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19676N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19676N\"></sup>yoke from off your neck, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19676O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19676O\"></sup>burst your bonds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19676P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19676P\"></sup>and foreigners shall no more make a servant of him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But they shall serve the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19677Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19677Q\"></sup>David their king, whom I will raise up for them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19678R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19678R\"></sup>“Then fear not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19678S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19678S\"></sup>O Jacob my servant, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,nor be dismayed, O Israel;for behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19678T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19678T\"></sup>I will save you from far away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19678U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19678U\"></sup>and your offspring from the land of their captivity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19678V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19678V\"></sup>Jacob shall return and have quiet and ease,and none shall make him afraid.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19679W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19679W\"></sup>For I am with you to save you,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19679X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19679X\"></sup>I will make a full end of all the nationsamong whom I scattered you,but of you I will not make a full end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19679Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19679Y\"></sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19679Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19679Z\"></sup>discipline you in just measure,and I will by no means leave you unpunished.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19680AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19680AA\"></sup>Your hurt is incurable,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19680AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19680AB\"></sup>and your wound is grievous.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There is none to uphold your cause,no medicine for your wound,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19681AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19681AC\"></sup>no healing for you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19682AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19682AD\"></sup>All your lovers have forgotten you;they care nothing for you;for I have dealt you the blow of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19682AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19682AE\"></sup>an enemy,the punishment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19682AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19682AF\"></sup>of a merciless foe,because your guilt is great,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19682AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19682AG\"></sup>because your sins are flagrant.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19683AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19683AH\"></sup>Why do you cry out over your hurt?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19683AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19683AI\"></sup>Your pain is incurable.Because your guilt is great,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19683AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19683AJ\"></sup>because your sins are flagrant,I have done these things to you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19684AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19684AK\"></sup>Therefore all who devour you shall be devoured,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19684AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19684AL\"></sup>all your foes, every one of them, shall go into captivity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19684AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19684AM\"></sup>those who plunder you shall be plundered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19684AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19684AN\"></sup>and all who prey on you I will make a prey.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19685AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19685AO\"></sup>For I will restore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19685AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19685AP\"></sup>health to you,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19685AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19685AQ\"></sup>your wounds I will heal,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19685AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19685AR\"></sup>they have called you an outcast:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19685AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19685AS\"></sup>‘It is Zion, for whom no one cares!’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19686AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19686AT\"></sup>I will restore the fortunes of the tents of Jacoband have compassion on his dwellings;the city shall be rebuilt on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19686AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19686AU\"></sup>its mound,and the palace shall stand where it used to be.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19687AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19687AV\"></sup>Out of them shall come songs of thanksgiving,and the voices of those who celebrate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19687AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19687AW\"></sup>I will multiply them, and they shall not be few;I will make them honored, and they shall not be small.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19688AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19688AX\"></sup>Their children shall be as they were of old,and their congregation shall be established before me,and I will punish all who oppress them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19689AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19689AY\"></sup>Their prince shall be one of themselves;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19689AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19689AZ\"></sup>their ruler shall come out from their midst;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19689BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19689BA\"></sup>I will make him draw near, and he shall approach me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19689BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19689BB\"></sup>for who would dare of himself to approach me?declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19690BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19690BC\"></sup>And you shall be my people,and I will be your God.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19691BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19691BD\"></sup>Behold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19691BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19691BE\"></sup>the storm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!Wrath has gone forth,a whirling tempest;it will burst upon the head of the wicked.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19692BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19692BF\"></sup>The fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not turn backuntil he has executed and accomplishedthe intentions of his mind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19692BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19692BG\"></sup>In the latter days you will understand this."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19693A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19693A\"></sup>“At that time, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19693B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19693B\"></sup>I will be the God of all the clans of Israel, and they shall be my people.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“The people who survived the swordfound grace in the wilderness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19694C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19694C\"></sup>when Israel sought for rest,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> appeared to him from far away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19695D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19695D\"></sup>I have loved you with an everlasting love;therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19695E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19695E\"></sup>I have continued <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19695F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19695F\"></sup>my faithfulness to you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19696G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19696G\"></sup>Again I will build you, and you shall be built,O virgin Israel!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19696H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19696H\"></sup>Again you shall adorn yourself with tambourinesand shall go forth in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19696I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19696I\"></sup>the dance of the merrymakers.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19697J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19697J\"></sup>Again you shall plant vineyardson the mountains of Samaria;the planters shall plantand shall enjoy the fruit.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For there shall be a day when watchmen will callin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19698K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19698K\"></sup>the hill country of Ephraim:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19698L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19698L\"></sup>‘Arise, and let us go up to Zion,to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19699M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19699M\"></sup>“Sing aloud with gladness for Jacob,and raise shouts for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19699N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19699N\"></sup>the chief of the nations;proclaim, give praise, and say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19699O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19699O\"></sup>‘O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, save your people,the remnant of Israel.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behold, I will bring them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19700P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19700P\"></sup>from the north countryand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19700Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19700Q\"></sup>gather them from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19700R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19700R\"></sup>the farthest parts of the earth,among them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19700S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19700S\"></sup>the blind and the lame,the pregnant woman and she who is in labor, together;a great company, they shall return here.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19701T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19701T\"></sup>With weeping they shall come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19701U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19701U\"></sup>and with pleas for mercy I will lead them back,I will make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19701V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19701V\"></sup>walk by brooks of water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19701W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19701W\"></sup>in a straight path in which they shall not stumble,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19701X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19701X\"></sup>I am a father to Israel,and Ephraim is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19701Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19701Y\"></sup>my firstborn.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O nations,and declare it in the coastlands far away;say, ‘He who scattered Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19702Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19702Z\"></sup>gather him,and will keep him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19702AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19702AA\"></sup>as a shepherd keeps his flock.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19703AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19703AB\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has ransomed Jacoband has redeemed him from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19703AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19703AC\"></sup>hands too strong for him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They shall come and sing aloud on the height of Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19704AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19704AD\"></sup>and they shall be radiant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19704AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19704AE\"></sup>over the goodness of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19704AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19704AF\"></sup>over the grain, the wine, and the oil,and over the young of the flock and the herd;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19704AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19704AG\"></sup>their life shall be like a watered garden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19704AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19704AH\"></sup>and they shall languish no more.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19705AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19705AI\"></sup>Then shall the young women rejoice in the dance,and the young men and the old shall be merry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19705AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19705AJ\"></sup>I will turn their mourning into joy;I will comfort them, and give them gladness for sorrow.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19706AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19706AK\"></sup>I will feast the soul of the priests with abundance,and my people shall be satisfied with my goodness,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19707AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19707AL\"></sup>“A voice is heard in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19707AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19707AM\"></sup>Ramah,lamentation and bitter weeping.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19707AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19707AN\"></sup>Rachel is weeping for her children;she refuses to be comforted for her children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19707AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19707AO\"></sup>because they are no more.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Keep your voice from weeping,and your eyes from tears,for there is a reward for your work,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19708AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19708AP\"></sup>they shall come back from the land of the enemy.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19709AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19709AQ\"></sup>There is hope for your future,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and your children shall come back to their own country.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I have heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19710AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19710AR\"></sup>Ephraim grieving,‘You have disciplined me, and I was disciplined,like an untrained calf;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19710AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19710AS\"></sup>bring me back that I may be restored,for you are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19711AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19711AT\"></sup>I had turned away, I relented,and after I was instructed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19711AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19711AU\"></sup>I struck my thigh;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19711AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19711AV\"></sup>I was ashamed, and I was confounded,because I bore the disgrace of my youth.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19712AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19712AW\"></sup>Is Ephraim my dear son?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19712AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19712AX\"></sup>Is he my darling child?For as often as I speak against him,I do remember him still.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19712AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19712AY\"></sup>Therefore my heart yearns for him;I will surely have mercy on him,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19713AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19713AZ\"></sup>“Set up road markers for yourself;make yourself guideposts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19713BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19713BA\"></sup>consider well the highway,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19713BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19713BB\"></sup>the road by which you went.Return, O virgin Israel,return to these your cities.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19714BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19714BC\"></sup>How long will you waver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19714BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19714BD\"></sup>O faithless daughter?For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has created a new thing on the earth:a woman encircles a man.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: “Once more they shall use these words in the land of Judah and in its cities, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19715BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19715BE\"></sup>when I restore their fortunes:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19715BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19715BF\"></sup>“‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> bless you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19715BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19715BG\"></sup>O habitation of righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19715BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19715BH\"></sup>O holy hill!’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19716BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19716BI\"></sup>And Judah and all its cities shall dwell there together, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19716BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19716BJ\"></sup>the farmers and those who wander with their flocks.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19717BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19717BK\"></sup>satisfy the weary soul, and every languishing soul I will replenish.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At this I awoke and looked, and my sleep was pleasant to me.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19719BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19719BL\"></sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19719BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19719BM\"></sup>I will sow the house of Israel and the house of Judah with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19719BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19719BN\"></sup>the seed of man and the seed of beast.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And it shall come to pass that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19720BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19720BO\"></sup>as I have watched over them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19720BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19720BP\"></sup>to pluck up and break down, to overthrow, destroy, and bring harm, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19720BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19720BQ\"></sup>so I will watch over them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19720BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19720BR\"></sup>to build and to plant, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>In those days they shall no longer say:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19721BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19721BS\"></sup>“‘The fathers have eaten sour grapes,and the children's teeth are set on edge.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19722BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19722BT\"></sup>But everyone shall die for his own iniquity. Each man who eats sour grapes, his teeth shall be set on edge.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19723BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19723BU\"></sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19723BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19723BV\"></sup>a new covenant with the house of Israel and the house of Judah,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>not like the covenant that I made with their fathers on the day when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19724BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19724BW\"></sup>I took them by the hand to bring them out of the land of Egypt, my covenant that they broke, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19724BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19724BX\"></sup>though I was their husband, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19725BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19725BY\"></sup>For this is the covenant that I will make with the house of Israel after those days, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19725BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19725BZ\"></sup>I will put my law within them, and I will write it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19725CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19725CA\"></sup>on their hearts. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19725CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19725CB\"></sup>And I will be their God, and they shall be my people.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And no longer shall each one teach his neighbor and each his brother, saying, ‘Know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19726CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19726CC\"></sup>for they shall all know me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19726CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19726CD\"></sup>from the least of them to the greatest, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19726CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19726CE\"></sup>I will forgive their iniquity, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19726CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19726CF\"></sup>I will remember their sin no more.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19727CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19727CG\"></sup>gives the sun for light by dayand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19727CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19727CH\"></sup>the fixed order of the moon and the stars for light by night,who stirs up the sea so that its waves roar—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19727CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19727CI\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name:",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19728CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19728CJ\"></sup>“If this fixed order departsfrom before me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,then shall the offspring of Israel ceasefrom being a nation before me forever.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“If the heavens above can be measured,and the foundations of the earth below can be explored,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19729CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19729CK\"></sup>then I will cast off all the offspring of Israelfor all that they have done,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19730CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19730CL\"></sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when the city shall be rebuilt for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19730CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19730CM\"></sup>from the Tower of Hananel to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19730CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19730CN\"></sup>the Corner Gate.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19731CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19731CO\"></sup>And the measuring line shall go out farther, straight to the hill Gareb, and shall then turn to Goah.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19732CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19732CP\"></sup>The whole valley of the dead bodies and the ashes, and all the fields as far as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19732CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19732CQ\"></sup>brook Kidron, to the corner of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19732CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19732CR\"></sup>the Horse Gate toward the east, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19732CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19732CS\"></sup>shall be sacred to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19732CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19732CT\"></sup>It shall not be plucked up or overthrown anymore forever.”"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19733A\"></sup>in the tenth year of Zedekiah king of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19733B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19733B\"></sup>which was the eighteenth year of Nebuchadnezzar.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>At that time the army of the king of Babylon was besieging Jerusalem, and Jeremiah the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19734C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19734C\"></sup>was shut up in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19734D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19734D\"></sup>the court of the guard that was in the palace of the king of Judah.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For Zedekiah king of Judah had imprisoned him, saying, “Why do you prophesy and say, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19735E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19735E\"></sup>Behold, I am giving this city into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he shall capture it;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19736F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19736F\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah shall not escape out of the hand of the Chaldeans, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19736G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19736G\"></sup>but shall surely be given into the hand of the king of Babylon, and shall speak with him face to face and see him eye to eye.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19737H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19737H\"></sup>he shall take Zedekiah to Babylon, and there he shall remain until I visit him, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19737I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19737I\"></sup>Though you fight against the Chaldeans, you shall not succeed’?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jeremiah said, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, Hanamel the son of Shallum your uncle will come to you and say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19739J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19739J\"></sup>‘Buy my field that is at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19739K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19739K\"></sup>Anathoth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19739L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19739L\"></sup>for the right of redemption by purchase is yours.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Hanamel my cousin came to me in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19740M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19740M\"></sup>the court of the guard, in accordance with the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and said to me, ‘Buy my field that is at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19740N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19740N\"></sup>Anathoth in the land of Benjamin, for the right of possession and redemption is yours; buy it for yourself.’ Then I knew that this was the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And I bought the field at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19741O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19741O\"></sup>Anathoth from Hanamel my cousin, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19741P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19741P\"></sup>weighed out the money to him, seventeen shekels of silver.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19742Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19742Q\"></sup>I signed the deed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19742R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19742R\"></sup>sealed it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19742S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19742S\"></sup>got witnesses, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19742T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19742T\"></sup>weighed the money on scales.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I took the sealed deed of purchase, containing the terms and conditions and the open copy.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I gave the deed of purchase to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19744U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19744U\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah son of Mahseiah, in the presence of Hanamel my cousin, in the presence of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19744V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19744V\"></sup>the witnesses who signed the deed of purchase, and in the presence of all the Judeans who were sitting in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19744W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19744W\"></sup>the court of the guard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I charged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19745X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19745X\"></sup>Baruch in their presence, saying,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Take these deeds, both this sealed deed of purchase and this open deed, and put them in an earthenware vessel, that they may last for a long time.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Houses and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19747Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19747Y\"></sup>fields and vineyards shall again be bought in this land.’",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“After I had given the deed of purchase to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19748Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19748Z\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah, I prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Ah, Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>! It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19749AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19749AA\"></sup>you who have made the heavens and the earth by your great power and by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19749AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19749AB\"></sup>your outstretched arm! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19749AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19749AC\"></sup>Nothing is too hard for you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19750AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19750AD\"></sup>You show steadfast love to thousands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19750AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19750AE\"></sup>but you repay the guilt of fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19750AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19750AF\"></sup>to their children after them, O great and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19750AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19750AG\"></sup>mighty God, whose name is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19750AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19750AH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19751AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19751AI\"></sup>great in counsel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19751AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19751AJ\"></sup>mighty in deed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19751AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19751AK\"></sup>whose eyes are open to all the ways of the children of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19751AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19751AL\"></sup>rewarding each one according to his ways and according to the fruit of his deeds.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You have shown <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19752AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19752AM\"></sup>signs and wonders in the land of Egypt, and to this day in Israel and among all mankind, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19752AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19752AN\"></sup>and have made a name for yourself, as at this day.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19753AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19753AO\"></sup>You brought your people Israel out of the land of Egypt with signs and wonders, with a strong hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19753AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19753AP\"></sup>outstretched arm, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19753AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19753AQ\"></sup>and with great terror.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And you gave them this land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19754AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19754AR\"></sup>which you swore to their fathers to give them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19754AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19754AS\"></sup>a land flowing with milk and honey.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And they entered and took possession of it. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19755AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19755AT\"></sup>But they did not obey your voice or walk in your law. They did nothing of all you commanded them to do. Therefore you have made all this disaster come upon them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19756AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19756AU\"></sup>the siege mounds have come up to the city to take it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19756AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19756AV\"></sup>because of sword and famine and pestilence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19756AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19756AW\"></sup>the city is given into the hands of the Chaldeans who are fighting against it. What you spoke has come to pass, and behold, you see it.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Yet you, O Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, have said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19757AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19757AX\"></sup>“Buy the field for money <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19757AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19757AY\"></sup>and get witnesses”—though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19757AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19757AZ\"></sup>the city is given into the hands of the Chaldeans.’”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Behold, I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19759BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19759BA\"></sup>the God of all flesh. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19759BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19759BB\"></sup>Is anything too hard for me?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19760BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19760BC\"></sup>Behold, I am giving this city into the hands of the Chaldeans and into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and he shall capture it.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The Chaldeans who are fighting against this city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19761BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19761BD\"></sup>shall come and set this city on fire and burn it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19761BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19761BE\"></sup>with the houses on whose roofs offerings have been made to Baal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19761BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19761BF\"></sup>and drink offerings have been poured out to other gods, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19761BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19761BG\"></sup>to provoke me to anger.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For the children of Israel and the children of Judah have done nothing but evil in my sight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19762BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19762BH\"></sup>from their youth. The children of Israel have done nothing but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19762BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19762BI\"></sup>provoke me to anger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19762BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19762BJ\"></sup>by the work of their hands, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>This city has aroused my anger and wrath, from the day it was built to this day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19763BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19763BK\"></sup>so that I will remove it from my sight",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>because of all the evil of the children of Israel and the children of Judah that they did to provoke me to anger—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19764BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19764BL\"></sup>their kings and their officials, their priests and their prophets, the men of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19765BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19765BM\"></sup>They have turned to me their back and not their face. And though I have taught them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19765BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19765BN\"></sup>persistently, they have not listened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19765BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19765BO\"></sup>to receive instruction.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>They set up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19766BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19766BP\"></sup>their abominations in the house that is called by my name, to defile it.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They built the high places of Baal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19767BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19767BQ\"></sup>in the Valley of the Son of Hinnom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19767BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19767BR\"></sup>to offer up their sons and daughters to Molech, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19767BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19767BS\"></sup>though I did not command them, nor did it enter into my mind, that they should do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19767BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19767BT\"></sup>this abomination, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19767BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19767BU\"></sup>to cause Judah to sin.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Now therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, concerning this city of which you say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19768BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19768BV\"></sup>‘It is given into the hand of the king of Babylon by sword, by famine, and by pestilence’:",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19769BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19769BW\"></sup>Behold, I will gather them from all the countries <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19769BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19769BX\"></sup>to which I drove them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19769BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19769BY\"></sup>my anger and my wrath and in great indignation. I will bring them back to this place, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19769BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19769BZ\"></sup>and I will make them dwell in safety.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19770CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19770CA\"></sup>And they shall be my people, and I will be their God.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19771CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19771CB\"></sup>I will give them one heart and one way, that they may fear me forever, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19771CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19771CC\"></sup>for their own good and the good of their children after them.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19772CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19772CD\"></sup>I will make with them an everlasting covenant, that I will not turn away from doing good to them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19772CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19772CE\"></sup>And I will put the fear of me in their hearts, that they may not turn from me.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19773CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19773CF\"></sup>I will rejoice in doing them good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19773CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19773CG\"></sup>and I will plant them in this land in faithfulness, with all my heart and all my soul.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19774CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19774CH\"></sup>Just as I have brought all this great disaster upon this people, so I will bring upon them all the good that I promise them.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19775CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19775CI\"></sup>Fields shall be bought in this land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19775CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19775CJ\"></sup>of which you are saying, ‘It is a desolation, without man or beast; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19775CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19775CK\"></sup>it is given into the hand of the Chaldeans.’",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Fields shall be bought for money, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CL\"></sup>deeds shall be signed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CM\"></sup>sealed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CN\"></sup>witnessed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CO\"></sup>in the land of Benjamin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CP\"></sup>in the places about Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CQ\"></sup>and in the cities of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CR\"></sup>in the cities of the hill country, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CS\"></sup>in the cities of the Shephelah, and in the cities of the Negeb; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19776CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19776CT\"></sup>I will restore their fortunes, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah a second time, while he was still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19777A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19777A\"></sup>shut up in the court of the guard:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19778B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19778B\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who made the earth, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who formed it to establish it—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19778C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19778C\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19779D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19779D\"></sup>Call to me and I will answer you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19779E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19779E\"></sup>and will tell you great and hidden things that you have not known.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, concerning the houses of this city and the houses of the kings of Judah that were torn down to make a defense against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19780F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19780F\"></sup>the siege mounds and against the sword:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They are coming in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19781G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19781G\"></sup>to fight against the Chaldeans and to fill them with the dead bodies of men whom I shall strike down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19781H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19781H\"></sup>in my anger and my wrath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19781I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19781I\"></sup>for I have hidden my face from this city because of all their evil.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19782J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19782J\"></sup>Behold, I will bring to it health and healing, and I will heal them and reveal to them abundance of prosperity and security.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19783K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19783K\"></sup>I will restore the fortunes of Judah and the fortunes of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19783L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19783L\"></sup>and rebuild them as they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19783M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19783M\"></sup>at first.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19784N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19784N\"></sup>I will cleanse them from all the guilt of their sin against me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19784O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19784O\"></sup>and I will forgive all the guilt of their sin and rebellion against me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19785P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19785P\"></sup>And this city shall be to me a name of joy, a praise and a glory before all the nations of the earth who shall hear of all the good that I do for them. They shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19785Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19785Q\"></sup>fear and tremble because of all the good and all the prosperity I provide for it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: In this place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19786R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19786R\"></sup>of which you say, ‘It is a waste without man or beast,’ in the cities of Judah and the streets of Jerusalem that are desolate, without man or inhabitant or beast, there shall be heard again",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19787S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19787S\"></sup>the voice of mirth and the voice of gladness, the voice of the bridegroom and the voice of the bride, the voices of those who sing, as they bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19787T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19787T\"></sup>thank offerings to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19787U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19787U\"></sup>“‘Give thanks to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is good,for his steadfast love endures forever!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19787V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19787V\"></sup>For I will restore the fortunes of the land as at first, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19788W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19788W\"></sup>In this place that is waste, without man or beast, and in all of its cities, there shall again be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19788X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19788X\"></sup>habitations of shepherds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19788Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19788Y\"></sup>resting their flocks.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789Z\"></sup>In the cities of the hill country, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789AA\"></sup>in the cities of the Shephelah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789AB\"></sup>and in the cities of the Negeb, in the land of Benjamin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789AC\"></sup>the places about Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789AD\"></sup>and in the cities of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789AE\"></sup>flocks shall again pass under the hands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19789AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19789AF\"></sup>of the one who counts them, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19790AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19790AG\"></sup>“Behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19790AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19790AH\"></sup>I will fulfill the promise I made to the house of Israel and the house of Judah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In those days and at that time I will cause a righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19791AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19791AI\"></sup>Branch to spring up for David, and he shall execute justice and righteousness in the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In those days Judah will be saved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19792AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19792AJ\"></sup>and Jerusalem will dwell securely. And this is the name by which it will be called: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19792AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19792AK\"></sup>‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our righteousness.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19793AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19793AL\"></sup>David shall never lack a man to sit on the throne of the house of Israel,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19794AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19794AM\"></sup>and the Levitical priests shall never lack a man in my presence to offer burnt offerings, to burn grain offerings, and to make sacrifices forever.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19796AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19796AN\"></sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19796AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19796AO\"></sup>If you can break my covenant with the day and my covenant with the night, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19796AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19796AP\"></sup>so that day and night will not come at their appointed time,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19797AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19797AQ\"></sup>then also my covenant with David my servant may be broken, so that he shall not have a son to reign on his throne, and my covenant with the Levitical priests my ministers.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19798AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19798AR\"></sup>the host of heaven cannot be numbered and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19798AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19798AS\"></sup>the sands of the sea cannot be measured, so I will multiply the offspring of David my servant, and the Levitical priests who minister to me.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Have you not observed that these people are saying, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected the two clans that he chose’? Thus they have despised my people so that they are no longer a nation in their sight.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19801AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19801AT\"></sup>If I have not established my covenant with day and night and the fixed order of heaven and earth,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then I will reject the offspring of Jacob and David my servant and will not choose one of his offspring to rule over the offspring of Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19802AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19802AU\"></sup>For I will restore their fortunes and will have mercy on them.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19803A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19803A\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and all his army <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19803B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19803B\"></sup>and all the kingdoms of the earth under his dominion and all the peoples were fighting against Jerusalem and all of its cities:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: Go and speak to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19804C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19804C\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah and say to him, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19804D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19804D\"></sup>Behold, I am giving this city into the hand of the king of Babylon, and he shall burn it with fire.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19805E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19805E\"></sup>You shall not escape from his hand but shall surely be captured and delivered into his hand. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19805F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19805F\"></sup>You shall see the king of Babylon eye to eye and speak with him face to face. And you shall go to Babylon.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O Zedekiah king of Judah! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19806G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19806G\"></sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning you: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19806H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19806H\"></sup>‘You shall not die by the sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You shall die in peace. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19807I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19807I\"></sup>And as spices were burned for your fathers, the former kings who were before you, so people shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19807J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19807J\"></sup>burn spices for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19807K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19807K\"></sup>and lament for you, saying, “Alas, lord!”’ For I have spoken the word, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Jeremiah the prophet spoke all these words to Zedekiah king of Judah, in Jerusalem,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>when the army of the king of Babylon was fighting against Jerusalem and against all the cities of Judah that were left, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19809L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19809L\"></sup>Lachish and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19809M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19809M\"></sup>Azekah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19809N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19809N\"></sup>for these were the only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19809O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19809O\"></sup>fortified cities of Judah that remained.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, after King Zedekiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19810P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19810P\"></sup>had made a covenant with all the people in Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19810Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19810Q\"></sup>to make a proclamation of liberty to them,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19811R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19811R\"></sup>that everyone should set free his Hebrew slaves, male and female, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19811S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19811S\"></sup>so that no one should enslave a Jew, his brother.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And they obeyed, all the officials and all the people who had entered into the covenant that everyone would set free his slave, male or female, so that they would not be enslaved again. They obeyed and set them free.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But afterward they turned around and took back the male and female slaves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19813T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19813T\"></sup>they had set free, and brought them into subjection as slaves.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel: I myself made a covenant with your fathers when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19815U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19815U\"></sup>I brought them out of the land of Egypt, out of the house of slavery, saying,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19816V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19816V\"></sup>‘At the end of seven years each of you must set free the fellow Hebrew who has been sold to you and has served you six years; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19816W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19816W\"></sup>you must set him free from your service.’ But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19816X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19816X\"></sup>your fathers did not listen to me or incline their ears to me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You recently repented and did what was right in my eyes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19817Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19817Y\"></sup>by proclaiming liberty, each to his neighbor, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19817Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19817Z\"></sup>you made a covenant before me in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19817AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19817AA\"></sup>house that is called by my name,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>but then you turned around <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19818AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19818AB\"></sup>and profaned my name when each of you took back his male and female slaves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19818AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19818AC\"></sup>whom you had set free according to their desire, and you brought them into subjection to be your slaves.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: You have not obeyed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19819AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19819AD\"></sup>by proclaiming liberty, every one to his brother and to his neighbor; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19819AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19819AE\"></sup>behold, I proclaim to you liberty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19819AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19819AF\"></sup>to the sword, to pestilence, and to famine, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19819AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19819AG\"></sup>I will make you a horror to all the kingdoms of the earth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the men who transgressed my covenant and did not keep the terms of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19820AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19820AH\"></sup>the covenant that they made before me, I will make them like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19820AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19820AI\"></sup>the calf that they cut in two and passed between its parts—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>the officials of Judah, the officials of Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19821AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19821AJ\"></sup>the eunuchs, the priests, and all the people of the land who passed between the parts of the calf.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And I will give them into the hand of their enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19822AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19822AK\"></sup>and into the hand of those who seek their lives. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19822AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19822AL\"></sup>Their dead bodies shall be food for the birds of the air and the beasts of the earth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19823AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19823AM\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah and his officials I will give into the hand of their enemies and into the hand of those who seek their lives, into the hand of the army of the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19823AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19823AN\"></sup>which has withdrawn from you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19824AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19824AO\"></sup>I will command, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19824AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19824AP\"></sup>bring them back to this city. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19824AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19824AQ\"></sup>And they will fight against it and take it and burn it with fire. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19824AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19824AR\"></sup>I will make the cities of Judah a desolation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19824AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19824AS\"></sup>without inhabitant.”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19825A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19825A\"></sup>Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go to the house of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19826B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19826B\"></sup>Rechabites and speak with them and bring them to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, into one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19826C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19826C\"></sup>the chambers; then offer them wine to drink.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So I took Jaazaniah the son of Jeremiah, son of Habazziniah and his brothers and all his sons and the whole house of the Rechabites.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I brought them to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19828D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19828D\"></sup>the chamber of the sons of Hanan the son of Igdaliah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19828E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19828E\"></sup>the man of God, which was near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19828F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19828F\"></sup>the chamber of the officials, above <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19828G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19828G\"></sup>the chamber of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19828H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19828H\"></sup>Maaseiah the son of Shallum, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19828I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19828I\"></sup>keeper of the threshold.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I set before the Rechabites pitchers full of wine, and cups, and I said to them, “Drink wine.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But they answered, “We will drink no wine, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19830J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19830J\"></sup>Jonadab the son of Rechab, our father, commanded us, ‘You shall not drink wine, neither you nor your sons forever.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You shall not build a house; you shall not sow seed; you shall not plant or have a vineyard; but you shall live in tents all your days, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19831K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19831K\"></sup>that you may live many days in the land where you sojourn.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We have obeyed the voice of Jonadab the son of Rechab, our father, in all that he commanded us, to drink no wine all our days, ourselves, our wives, our sons, or our daughters,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and not to build houses to dwell in. We have no vineyard or field or seed,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but we have lived in tents and have obeyed and done all that Jonadab our father commanded us.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19835L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19835L\"></sup>when Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon came up against the land, we said, ‘Come, and let us go to Jerusalem for fear of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19835M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19835M\"></sup>the army of the Chaldeans and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19835N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19835N\"></sup>the army of the Syrians.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19835O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19835O\"></sup>So we are living in Jerusalem.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Go and say to the people of Judah and the inhabitants of Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19837P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19837P\"></sup>Will you not receive instruction and listen to my words? declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The command that Jonadab the son of Rechab gave to his sons, to drink no wine, has been kept, and they drink none to this day, for they have obeyed their father's command. I have spoken to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19838Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19838Q\"></sup>persistently, but you have not listened to me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I have sent to you all my servants the prophets, sending them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19839R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19839R\"></sup>persistently, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19839S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19839S\"></sup>‘Turn now every one of you from his evil way, and amend your deeds, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19839T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19839T\"></sup>do not go after other gods to serve them, and then you shall dwell in the land that I gave to you and your fathers.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19839U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19839U\"></sup>But you did not incline your ear or listen to me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The sons of Jonadab the son of Rechab have kept the command that their father gave them, but this people has not obeyed me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts, the God of Israel: Behold, I am bringing upon Judah and all the inhabitants of Jerusalem all the disaster that I have pronounced against them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19841V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19841V\"></sup>because I have spoken to them and they have not listened, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19841W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19841W\"></sup>I have called to them and they have not answered.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But to the house of the Rechabites Jeremiah said, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Because you have obeyed the command of Jonadab your father and kept all his precepts and done all that he commanded you,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Jonadab the son of Rechab shall never lack a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19843X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19843X\"></sup>to stand before me.”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19844A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19844A\"></sup>fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19845B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19845B\"></sup>a scroll and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19845C\"></sup>write on it all the words that I have spoken to you against Israel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19845D\"></sup>Judah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19845E\"></sup>and all the nations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19845F\"></sup>from the day I spoke to you, from the days of Josiah until today.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19846G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19846G\"></sup>It may be that the house of Judah will hear all the disaster that I intend to do to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19846H\"></sup>so that every one may turn from his evil way, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19846I\"></sup>that I may forgive their iniquity and their sin.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then Jeremiah called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19847J\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19847K\"></sup>Baruch wrote on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19847L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19847L\"></sup>a scroll at the dictation of Jeremiah all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that he had spoken to him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Jeremiah ordered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19848M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19848M\"></sup>Baruch, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19848N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19848N\"></sup>“I am banned from going to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>so you are to go, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19849O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19849O\"></sup>on a day of fasting in the hearing of all the people in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house you shall read the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the scroll that you have written at my dictation. You shall read them also in the hearing of all the men of Judah who come out of their cities.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19850P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19850P\"></sup>It may be that their plea for mercy will come before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19850Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19850Q\"></sup>and that every one will turn from his evil way, for great is the anger and wrath that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has pronounced against this people.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Baruch the son of Neriah did all that Jeremiah the prophet ordered him about reading from the scroll the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19852R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19852R\"></sup>In the fifth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19852S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19852S\"></sup>in the ninth month, all the people in Jerusalem and all the people who came from the cities of Judah to Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19852T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19852T\"></sup>proclaimed a fast before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then, in the hearing of all the people, Baruch read the words of Jeremiah from the scroll, in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19853U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19853U\"></sup>the chamber of Gemariah the son of Shaphan the secretary, which was in the upper court, at the entry of the New Gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Micaiah the son of Gemariah, son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19854V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19854V\"></sup>Shaphan, heard all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the scroll,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>he went down to the king's house, into the secretary's chamber, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855W\"></sup>all the officials were sitting there: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855X\"></sup>Elishama the secretary, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855Y\"></sup>Delaiah the son of Shemaiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855Z\"></sup>Elnathan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855AA\"></sup>the son of Achbor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855AB\"></sup>Gemariah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19855AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19855AC\"></sup>Shaphan, Zedekiah the son of Hananiah, and all the officials.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And Micaiah told them all the words that he had heard, when Baruch read the scroll in the hearing of the people.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then all the officials sent Jehudi the son of Nethaniah, son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19857AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19857AD\"></sup>Shelemiah, son of Cushi, to say to Baruch, “Take in your hand the scroll that you read in the hearing of the people, and come.” So Baruch the son of Neriah took the scroll in his hand and came to them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And they said to him, “Sit down and read it.” So Baruch read it to them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When they heard all the words, they turned one to another in fear. And they said to Baruch, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19859AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19859AE\"></sup>“We must report all these words to the king.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then they asked Baruch, “Tell us, please, how did you write all these words? Was it at his dictation?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Baruch answered them, “He dictated all these words to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19861AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19861AF\"></sup>while I wrote them with ink on the scroll.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the officials said to Baruch, “Go and hide, you and Jeremiah, and let no one know where you are.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So they went into the court to the king, having put the scroll in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19863AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19863AG\"></sup>the chamber of Elishama the secretary, and they reported all the words to the king.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then the king sent Jehudi to get the scroll, and he took it from the chamber of Elishama the secretary. And Jehudi read it to the king and all the officials who stood beside the king.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19865AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19865AH\"></sup>the ninth month, and the king was sitting in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19865AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19865AI\"></sup>the winter house, and there was a fire burning in the fire pot before him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>As Jehudi read three or four columns, the king would cut them off with a knife and throw them into the fire in the fire pot, until the entire scroll was consumed in the fire that was in the fire pot.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19867AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19867AJ\"></sup>neither the king nor any of his servants who heard all these words was afraid, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19867AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19867AK\"></sup>nor did they tear their garments.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Even when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19868AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19868AL\"></sup>Elnathan and Delaiah and Gemariah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19868AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19868AM\"></sup>urged the king not to burn the scroll, he would not listen to them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And the king commanded Jerahmeel the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19869AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19869AN\"></sup>king's son and Seraiah the son of Azriel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19869AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19869AO\"></sup>Shelemiah the son of Abdeel to seize <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19869AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19869AP\"></sup>Baruch the secretary and Jeremiah the prophet, but the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> hid them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now after the king had burned the scroll with the words that Baruch wrote at Jeremiah's dictation, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Take another scroll and write on it all the former words that were in the first scroll, which Jehoiakim the king of Judah has burned.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And concerning Jehoiakim king of Judah you shall say, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, You have burned this scroll, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19872AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19872AQ\"></sup>“Why have you written in it that the king of Babylon will certainly come and destroy this land, and will cut off from it man and beast?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning Jehoiakim king of Judah: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19873AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19873AR\"></sup>He shall have none <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19873AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19873AS\"></sup>to sit on the throne of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19873AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19873AT\"></sup>and his dead body shall be cast out to the heat by day and the frost by night.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19874AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19874AU\"></sup>And I will punish him and his offspring and his servants for their iniquity. I will bring upon them and upon the inhabitants of Jerusalem and upon the people of Judah all the disaster that I have pronounced against them, but they would not hear.’”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then Jeremiah took another scroll and gave it to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19875AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19875AV\"></sup>Baruch the scribe, the son of Neriah, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19875AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19875AW\"></sup>wrote on it at the dictation of Jeremiah all the words of the scroll that Jehoiakim king of Judah had burned in the fire. And many similar words were added to them."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19876A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19876A\"></sup>Zedekiah the son of Josiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19876B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19876B\"></sup>whom Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon made king in the land of Judah, reigned instead of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19876C\"></sup>Coniah the son of Jehoiakim.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19877D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19877D\"></sup>But neither he nor his servants nor the people of the land listened to the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that he spoke through Jeremiah the prophet.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>King Zedekiah sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19878E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19878E\"></sup>Jehucal the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19878F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19878F\"></sup>Shelemiah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19878G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19878G\"></sup>Zephaniah the priest, the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19878H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19878H\"></sup>Maaseiah, to Jeremiah the prophet, saying, “Please <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19878I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19878I\"></sup>pray for us to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19879J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19879J\"></sup>Now Jeremiah was still going in and out among the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19879K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19879K\"></sup>for he had not yet been put in prison.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19880L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19880L\"></sup>The army of Pharaoh had come out of Egypt. And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19880M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19880M\"></sup>the Chaldeans who were besieging Jerusalem heard news about them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19880N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19880N\"></sup>they withdrew from Jerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah the prophet:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, God of Israel: Thus shall you say to the king of Judah who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19882O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19882O\"></sup>sent you to me to inquire of me, ‘Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19882P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19882P\"></sup>Pharaoh's army that came to help you is about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19882Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19882Q\"></sup>return to Egypt, to its own land.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19883R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19883R\"></sup>the Chaldeans shall come back and fight against this city. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19883S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19883S\"></sup>They shall capture it and burn it with fire.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Do not deceive yourselves, saying, “The Chaldeans will surely go away from us,” for they will not go away.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19885T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19885T\"></sup>For even if you should defeat the whole army of Chaldeans who are fighting against you, and there remained of them only wounded men, every man in his tent, they would rise up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19885U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19885U\"></sup>burn this city with fire.’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19886V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19886V\"></sup>the Chaldean army had withdrawn from Jerusalem at the approach of Pharaoh's army,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Jeremiah set out from Jerusalem to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19887W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19887W\"></sup>the land of Benjamin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19887X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19887X\"></sup>to receive his portion there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19887Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19887Y\"></sup>among the people.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When he was at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19888Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19888Z\"></sup>the Benjamin Gate, a sentry there named Irijah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19888AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19888AA\"></sup>Shelemiah, son of Hananiah, seized Jeremiah the prophet, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19888AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19888AB\"></sup>“You are deserting to the Chaldeans.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And Jeremiah said, “It is a lie; I am not deserting to the Chaldeans.” But Irijah would not listen to him, and seized Jeremiah and brought him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19889AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19889AC\"></sup>the officials.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the officials were enraged at Jeremiah, and they beat him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19890AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19890AD\"></sup>and imprisoned him in the house of Jonathan the secretary, for it had been made a prison.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19891AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19891AE\"></sup>When Jeremiah had come to the dungeon cells and remained there many days,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>King Zedekiah sent for him and received him. The king questioned him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19892AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19892AF\"></sup>secretly in his house and said, “Is there any word from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?” Jeremiah said, “There is.” Then he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19892AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19892AG\"></sup>“You shall be delivered into the hand of the king of Babylon.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Jeremiah also said to King Zedekiah, “What wrong have I done to you or your servants or this people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19893AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19893AH\"></sup>that you have put me in prison?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19894AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19894AI\"></sup>Where are your prophets who prophesied to you, saying, ‘The king of Babylon will not come against you and against this land’?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now hear, please, O my lord the king: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19895AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19895AJ\"></sup>let my humble plea come before you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19895AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19895AK\"></sup>do not send me back to the house of Jonathan the secretary, lest I die there.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So King Zedekiah gave orders, and they committed Jeremiah to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19896AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19896AL\"></sup>the court of the guard. And a loaf of bread was given him daily from the bakers' street, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19896AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19896AM\"></sup>until all the bread of the city was gone. So Jeremiah remained in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19896AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19896AN\"></sup>the court of the guard."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>Now Shephatiah the son of Mattan, Gedaliah the son of Pashhur, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19897A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19897A\"></sup>Jucal the son of Shelemiah, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19897B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19897B\"></sup>Pashhur the son of Malchiah heard the words that Jeremiah was saying to all the people:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19898C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19898C\"></sup>He who stays in this city shall die by the sword, by famine, and by pestilence, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19898D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19898D\"></sup>but he who goes out to the Chaldeans shall live. He shall have his life as a prize of war, and live.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19899E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19899E\"></sup>This city shall surely be given into the hand of the army of the king of Babylon and be taken.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the officials said to the king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19900F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19900F\"></sup>“Let this man be put to death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19900G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19900G\"></sup>for he is weakening the hands of the soldiers who are left in this city, and the hands of all the people, by speaking such words to them. For this man is not seeking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19900H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19900H\"></sup>the welfare of this people, but their harm.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>King Zedekiah said, “Behold, he is in your hands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19901I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19901I\"></sup>for the king can do nothing against you.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So they took Jeremiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19902J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19902J\"></sup>and cast him into the cistern of Malchiah, the king's son, which was in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19902K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19902K\"></sup>the court of the guard, letting Jeremiah down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19902L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19902L\"></sup>by ropes. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19902M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19902M\"></sup>And there was no water in the cistern, but only mud, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19902N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19902N\"></sup>Jeremiah sank in the mud.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19903O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19903O\"></sup>Ebed-melech <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19903P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19903P\"></sup>the Ethiopian, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19903Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19903Q\"></sup>a eunuch who was in the king's house, heard that they had put Jeremiah into the cistern—the king was sitting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19903R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19903R\"></sup>in the Benjamin Gate—",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19904S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19904S\"></sup>Ebed-melech went from the king's house and said to the king,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“My lord the king, these men have done evil in all that they did to Jeremiah the prophet by casting him into the cistern, and he will die there of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19905T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19905T\"></sup>hunger, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19905U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19905U\"></sup>for there is no bread left in the city.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the king commanded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19906V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19906V\"></sup>Ebed-melech the Ethiopian, “Take thirty men with you from here, and lift Jeremiah the prophet out of the cistern before he dies.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19907W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19907W\"></sup>Ebed-melech took the men with him and went to the house of the king, to a wardrobe in the storehouse, and took from there old rags and worn-out clothes, which he let down to Jeremiah in the cistern <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19907X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19907X\"></sup>by ropes.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19908Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19908Y\"></sup>Ebed-melech the Ethiopian said to Jeremiah, “Put the rags and clothes between your armpits and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19908Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19908Z\"></sup>the ropes.” Jeremiah did so.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then they drew Jeremiah up with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19909AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19909AA\"></sup>ropes and lifted him out of the cistern. And Jeremiah remained in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19909AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19909AB\"></sup>court of the guard.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>King Zedekiah sent for Jeremiah the prophet and received him at the third entrance of the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. The king said to Jeremiah, “I will ask you a question; hide nothing from me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Jeremiah said to Zedekiah, “If I tell you, will you not surely put me to death? And if I give you counsel, you will not listen to me.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then King Zedekiah swore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19912AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19912AC\"></sup>secretly to Jeremiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19912AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19912AD\"></sup>“As the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19912AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19912AE\"></sup>who made our souls, I will not put you to death or deliver you into the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19912AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19912AF\"></sup>these men who seek your life.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to Zedekiah, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19913AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19913AG\"></sup>If you will surrender to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19913AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19913AH\"></sup>the officials of the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19913AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19913AI\"></sup>then your life shall be spared, and this city shall not be burned with fire, and you and your house shall live.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if you do not surrender to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19914AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19914AJ\"></sup>the officials of the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19914AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19914AK\"></sup>then this city shall be given into the hand of the Chaldeans, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19914AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19914AL\"></sup>and they shall burn it with fire, and you shall not escape from their hand.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>King Zedekiah said to Jeremiah, “I am afraid of the Judeans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19915AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19915AM\"></sup>who have deserted to the Chaldeans, lest I be handed over to them and they deal cruelly with me.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Jeremiah said, “You shall not be given to them. Obey now the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in what I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19916AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19916AN\"></sup>and it shall be well with you, and your life shall be spared.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But if you refuse to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19917AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19917AO\"></sup>surrender, this is the vision which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has shown to me:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, all the women left in the house of the king of Judah were being led out to the officials of the king of Babylon and were saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19918AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19918AP\"></sup>“‘Your trusted friends have deceived youand prevailed against you;now that your feet are sunk in the mud,they turn away from you.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>All your wives and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19919AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19919AQ\"></sup>your sons shall be led out to the Chaldeans, and you yourself shall not escape from their hand, but shall be seized by the king of Babylon, and this city shall be burned with fire.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Zedekiah said to Jeremiah, “Let no one know of these words, and you shall not die.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19921AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19921AR\"></sup>the officials hear that I have spoken with you and come to you and say to you, ‘Tell us what you said to the king and what the king said to you; hide nothing from us and we will not put you to death,’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then you shall say to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19922AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19922AS\"></sup>‘I made a humble plea to the king that he would not send me back to the house of Jonathan to die there.’”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then all the officials came to Jeremiah and asked him, and he answered them as the king had instructed him. So they stopped speaking with him, for the conversation had not been overheard.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And Jeremiah remained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19924AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19924AT\"></sup>in the court of the guard until the day that Jerusalem was taken."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19925A\"></sup>In the ninth year of Zedekiah king of Judah, in the tenth month, Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and all his army came against Jerusalem and besieged it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In the eleventh year of Zedekiah, in the fourth month, on the ninth day of the month, a breach was made in the city.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19927B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19927B\"></sup>the officials of the king of Babylon came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19927C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19927C\"></sup>and sat in the middle gate: Nergal-sar-ezer of Samgar, Nebu-sar-sekim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19927D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19927D\"></sup>the Rab-saris, Nergal-sar-ezer the Rab-mag, with all the rest of the officers of the king of Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When Zedekiah king of Judah and all the soldiers saw them, they fled, going out of the city at night by way of the king's garden through the gate between the two walls; and they went toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19928E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19928E\"></sup>the Arabah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the army of the Chaldeans pursued them and overtook Zedekiah in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19929F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19929F\"></sup>the plains of Jericho. And when they had taken him, they brought him up to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19929G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19929G\"></sup>Riblah, in the land of Hamath; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19929H\"></sup>and he passed sentence on him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19930I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19930I\"></sup>slaughtered the sons of Zedekiah at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19930J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19930J\"></sup>Riblah before his eyes, and the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19930K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19930K\"></sup>slaughtered all the nobles of Judah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19931L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19931L\"></sup>He put out the eyes of Zedekiah and bound him in chains to take him to Babylon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19932M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19932M\"></sup>The Chaldeans burned the king's house and the house of the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19932N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19932N\"></sup>and broke down the walls of Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19933O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19933O\"></sup>Nebuzaradan, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19933P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19933P\"></sup>captain of the guard, carried into exile to Babylon the rest of the people who were left in the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19933Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19933Q\"></sup>those who had deserted to him, and the people who remained.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Nebuzaradan, the captain of the guard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19934R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19934R\"></sup>left in the land of Judah some of the poor people who owned nothing, and gave them vineyards and fields at the same time.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon gave command concerning Jeremiah through Nebuzaradan, the captain of the guard, saying,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19936S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19936S\"></sup>“Take him, look after him well, and do him no harm, but deal with him as he tells you.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19937T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19937T\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard, Nebushazban the Rab-saris, Nergal-sar-ezer the Rab-mag, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19937U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19937U\"></sup>and all the chief officers of the king of Babylon",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>sent and took Jeremiah from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19938V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19938V\"></sup>the court of the guard. They entrusted him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19938W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19938W\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19938X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19938X\"></sup>Ahikam, son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19938Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19938Y\"></sup>Shaphan, that he should take him home. So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19938Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19938Z\"></sup>he lived among the people.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19939AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19939AA\"></sup>while he was shut up in the court of the guard:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Go, and say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19940AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19940AB\"></sup>Ebed-melech the Ethiopian, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19940AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19940AC\"></sup>Behold, I will fulfill my words against this city for harm and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19940AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19940AD\"></sup>not for good, and they shall be accomplished before you on that day.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But I will deliver you on that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and you shall not be given into the hand of the men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19941AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19941AE\"></sup>of whom you are afraid.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For I will surely save you, and you shall not fall by the sword, but you shall have your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19942AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19942AF\"></sup>life as a prize of war, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19942AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19942AG\"></sup>because you have put your trust in me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19943A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19943A\"></sup>after Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard had let him go from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19943B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19943B\"></sup>Ramah, when he took him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19943C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19943C\"></sup>bound in chains along with all the captives of Jerusalem and Judah who were being exiled to Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The captain of the guard took Jeremiah and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19944D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19944D\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God pronounced this disaster against this place.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought it about, and has done as he said. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19945E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19945E\"></sup>Because you sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and did not obey his voice, this thing has come upon you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now, behold, I release you today from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19946F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19946F\"></sup>the chains on your hands. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19946G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19946G\"></sup>If it seems good to you to come with me to Babylon, come, and I will look after you well, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19946H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19946H\"></sup>but if it seems wrong to you to come with me to Babylon, do not come. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19946I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19946I\"></sup>See, the whole land is before you; go wherever you think it good and right to go.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If you remain, then return to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19947J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19947J\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, son of Shaphan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19947K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19947K\"></sup>whom the king of Babylon appointed governor of the cities of Judah, and dwell with him among the people. Or go wherever you think it right to go.” So the captain of the guard gave him an allowance of food and a present, and let him go.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Jeremiah went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19948L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19948L\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19948M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19948M\"></sup>Mizpah, and lived with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19948N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19948N\"></sup>among the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19948O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19948O\"></sup>who were left in the land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19949P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19949P\"></sup>When all the captains of the forces in the open country and their men heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19949Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19949Q\"></sup>the king of Babylon had appointed Gedaliah the son of Ahikam governor in the land and had committed to him men, women, and children, those of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19949R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19949R\"></sup>the poorest of the land who had not been taken into exile to Babylon,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>they went to Gedaliah at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19950S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19950S\"></sup>Mizpah—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19950T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19950T\"></sup>Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19950U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19950U\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah, Seraiah the son of Tanhumeth, the sons of Ephai the Netophathite, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19950V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19950V\"></sup>Jezaniah the son of the Maacathite, they and their men.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, son of Shaphan, swore to them and their men, saying, “Do not be afraid to serve the Chaldeans. Dwell in the land and serve the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19951W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19951W\"></sup>and it shall be well with you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>As for me, I will dwell at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19952X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19952X\"></sup>Mizpah, to represent you before the Chaldeans who will come to us. But as for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19952Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19952Y\"></sup>gather wine and summer fruits and oil, and store them in your vessels, and dwell in your cities that you have taken.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Likewise, when all the Judeans who were in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19953Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19953Z\"></sup>Moab and among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19953AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19953AA\"></sup>the Ammonites and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19953AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19953AB\"></sup>Edom and in other lands heard that the king of Babylon had left a remnant in Judah and had appointed Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, son of Shaphan, as governor over them,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19954AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19954AC\"></sup>then all the Judeans returned from all the places to which they had been driven and came to the land of Judah, to Gedaliah at Mizpah. And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19954AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19954AD\"></sup>gathered wine and summer fruits in great abundance.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19955AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19955AE\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19955AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19955AF\"></sup>all the leaders of the forces in the open country came to Gedaliah at Mizpah",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and said to him, “Do you know that Baalis the king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19956AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19956AG\"></sup>the Ammonites has sent Ishmael the son of Nethaniah to take your life?” But Gedaliah the son of Ahikam would not believe them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then Johanan the son of Kareah spoke secretly to Gedaliah at Mizpah, “Please let me go and strike down Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, and no one will know it. Why should he take your life, so that all the Judeans who are gathered about you would be scattered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19957AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19957AH\"></sup>and the remnant of Judah would perish?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Gedaliah the son of Ahikam said to Johanan the son of Kareah, “You shall not do this thing, for you are speaking falsely of Ishmael.”"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19959A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19959A\"></sup>In the seventh month, Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, son of Elishama, of the royal family, one of the chief officers of the king, came with ten men to Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19959B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19959B\"></sup>Mizpah. As they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19959C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19959C\"></sup>ate bread together there at Mizpah,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19960D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19960D\"></sup>Ishmael the son of Nethaniah and the ten men with him rose up and struck down Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, son of Shaphan, with the sword, and killed him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19960E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19960E\"></sup>whom the king of Babylon had appointed governor in the land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Ishmael also struck down all the Judeans who were with Gedaliah at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19961F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19961F\"></sup>Mizpah, and the Chaldean soldiers who happened to be there.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>On the day after the murder of Gedaliah, before anyone knew of it,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>eighty men arrived from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963G\"></sup>Shechem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963H\"></sup>Shiloh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963I\"></sup>Samaria, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963J\"></sup>their beards shaved and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963K\"></sup>their clothes torn, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963L\"></sup>their bodies gashed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19963M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19963M\"></sup>bringing grain offerings and incense to present at the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And Ishmael the son of Nethaniah came out from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19964N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19964N\"></sup>Mizpah to meet them, weeping as he came. As he met them, he said to them, “Come in to Gedaliah the son of Ahikam.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When they came into the city, Ishmael the son of Nethaniah and the men with him slaughtered them and cast them into a cistern.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But there were ten men among them who said to Ishmael, “Do not put us to death, for we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19966O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19966O\"></sup>stores of wheat, barley, oil, and honey hidden in the fields.” So he refrained and did not put them to death with their companions.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now the cistern into which Ishmael had thrown all the bodies of the men whom he had struck down along with Gedaliah was the large cistern that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19967P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19967P\"></sup>King Asa had made for defense against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19967Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19967Q\"></sup>Baasha king of Israel; Ishmael the son of Nethaniah filled it with the slain.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Ishmael took captive all the rest of the people who were in Mizpah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19968R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19968R\"></sup>the king's daughters and all the people who were left at Mizpah, whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19968S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19968S\"></sup>Nebuzaradan, the captain of the guard, had committed to Gedaliah the son of Ahikam. Ishmael the son of Nethaniah took them captive and set out to cross over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19968T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19968T\"></sup>the Ammonites.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19969U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19969U\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19969V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19969V\"></sup>all the leaders of the forces with him heard of all the evil that Ishmael the son of Nethaniah had done,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>they took all their men and went to fight against Ishmael the son of Nethaniah. They came upon him at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19970W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19970W\"></sup>the great pool that is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19970X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19970X\"></sup>Gibeon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when all the people who were with Ishmael saw Johanan the son of Kareah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19971Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19971Y\"></sup>all the leaders of the forces with him, they rejoiced.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19972Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19972Z\"></sup>So all the people whom Ishmael had carried away captive from Mizpah turned around and came back, and went to Johanan the son of Kareah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Ishmael the son of Nethaniah escaped from Johanan with eight men, and went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19973AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19973AA\"></sup>the Ammonites.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then Johanan the son of Kareah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19974AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19974AB\"></sup>all the leaders of the forces with him took from Mizpah all the rest of the people whom he had recovered from Ishmael the son of Nethaniah, after he had struck down Gedaliah the son of Ahikam—soldiers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19974AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19974AC\"></sup>women, children, and eunuchs, whom Johanan brought back from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19974AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19974AD\"></sup>Gibeon.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they went and stayed at Geruth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19975AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19975AE\"></sup>Chimham near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19975AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19975AF\"></sup>Bethlehem, intending to go to Egypt",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>because of the Chaldeans. For they were afraid of them, because Ishmael the son of Nethaniah had struck down Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19976AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19976AG\"></sup>whom the king of Babylon had made governor over the land."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19977A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19977A\"></sup>all the commanders of the forces, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19977B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19977B\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and Jezaniah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19977C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19977C\"></sup>Hoshaiah, and all the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19977D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19977D\"></sup>from the least to the greatest, came near",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and said to Jeremiah the prophet, “Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19978E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19978E\"></sup>our plea for mercy come before you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19978F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19978F\"></sup>pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God for us, for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19978G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19978G\"></sup>this remnant—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19978H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19978H\"></sup>because we are left with but a few, as your eyes see us—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19979I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19979I\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God may show us the way we should go, and the thing that we should do.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Jeremiah the prophet said to them, “I have heard you. Behold, I will pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God according to your request, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19980J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19980J\"></sup>whatever the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> answers you I will tell you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19980K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19980K\"></sup>I will keep nothing back from you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then they said to Jeremiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19981L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19981L\"></sup>“May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be a true and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19981M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19981M\"></sup>faithful witness against us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19981N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19981N\"></sup>if we do not act according to all the word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19981O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19981O\"></sup>with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God sends you to us.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whether it is good or bad, we will obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God to whom we are sending you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19982P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19982P\"></sup>that it may be well with us when we obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19983Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19983Q\"></sup>At the end of ten days the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he summoned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19984R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19984R\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19984S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19984S\"></sup>all the commanders of the forces who were with him, and all the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19984T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19984T\"></sup>from the least to the greatest,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and said to them, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19985U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19985U\"></sup>to whom you sent me to present your plea for mercy before him:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If you will remain in this land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19986V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19986V\"></sup>then I will build you up and not pull you down; I will plant you, and not pluck you up; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19986W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19986W\"></sup>for I relent of the disaster that I did to you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19987X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19987X\"></sup>Do not fear the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19987Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19987Y\"></sup>of whom you are afraid. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19987Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19987Z\"></sup>Do not fear him, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19987AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19987AA\"></sup>for I am with you, to save you and to deliver you from his hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19988AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19988AB\"></sup>I will grant you mercy, that he may have mercy on you and let you remain in your own land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19989AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19989AC\"></sup>But if you say, ‘We will not remain in this land,’ disobeying the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and saying, ‘No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19990AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19990AD\"></sup>we will go to the land of Egypt, where we shall not see war or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19990AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19990AE\"></sup>hear the sound of the trumpet or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19990AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19990AF\"></sup>be hungry for bread, and we will dwell there,’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>then hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O remnant of Judah. Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19991AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19991AG\"></sup>If you set your faces to enter Egypt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19991AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19991AH\"></sup>and go to live there,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>then the sword <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19992AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19992AI\"></sup>that you fear shall overtake you there in the land of Egypt, and the famine of which you are afraid shall follow close after you to Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19992AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19992AJ\"></sup>and there you shall die.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>All the men who set their faces to go to Egypt to live there shall die by the sword, by famine, and by pestilence. They shall have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19993AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19993AK\"></sup>no remnant or survivor from the disaster that I will bring upon them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19994AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19994AL\"></sup>As my anger and my wrath were poured out on the inhabitants of Jerusalem, so my wrath will be poured out on you when you go to Egypt. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19994AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19994AM\"></sup>You shall become an execration, a horror, a curse, and a taunt. You shall see this place no more.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has said to you, O remnant of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19995AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19995AN\"></sup>‘Do not go to Egypt.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19995AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19995AO\"></sup>Know for a certainty that I have warned you this day",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>that you have gone astray at the cost of your lives. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19996AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19996AP\"></sup>For you sent me to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19996AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19996AQ\"></sup>‘Pray for us to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19996AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19996AR\"></sup>whatever the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God says, declare to us and we will do it.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And I have this day declared it to you, but you have not obeyed the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in anything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19997AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19997AS\"></sup>that he sent me to tell you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-19998AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-19998AT\"></sup>Now therefore know for a certainty that you shall die by the sword, by famine, and by pestilence in the place where you desire to go to live.”"
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>When Jeremiah finished speaking to all the people all these words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God, with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God had sent him to them,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Azariah the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20000A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20000A\"></sup>Hoshaiah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20000B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20000B\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20000C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20000C\"></sup>all the insolent men said to Jeremiah, “You are telling a lie. The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God did not send you to say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20000D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20000D\"></sup>‘Do not go to Egypt to live there,’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20001E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20001E\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20001F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20001F\"></sup>has set you against us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20001G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20001G\"></sup>to deliver us into the hand of the Chaldeans, that they may kill us or take us into exile in Babylon.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20002H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20002H\"></sup>Johanan the son of Kareah and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20002I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20002I\"></sup>the commanders of the forces and all the people did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, to remain in the land of Judah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But Johanan the son of Kareah and all the commanders of the forces took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20003J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20003J\"></sup>all the remnant of Judah who had returned to live in the land of Judah from all the nations to which they had been driven—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20004K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20004K\"></sup>the men, the women, the children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20004L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20004L\"></sup>the princesses, and every person whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20004M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20004M\"></sup>Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard had left with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20004N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20004N\"></sup>Gedaliah the son of Ahikam, son of Shaphan; also Jeremiah the prophet and Baruch the son of Neriah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And they came into the land of Egypt, for they did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. And they arrived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20005O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20005O\"></sup>Tahpanhes.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20006P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20006P\"></sup>Tahpanhes:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Take in your hands large stones and hide them in the mortar in the pavement that is at the entrance to Pharaoh's palace in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20007Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20007Q\"></sup>Tahpanhes, in the sight of the men of Judah,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and say to them, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Behold, I will send and take Nebuchadnezzar the king of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20008R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20008R\"></sup>my servant, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20008S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20008S\"></sup>and I will set his throne above these stones that I have hidden, and he will spread his royal canopy over them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He shall come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20009T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20009T\"></sup>and strike the land of Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20009U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20009U\"></sup>giving over to the pestilence those who are doomed to the pestilence, to captivity those who are doomed to captivity, and to the sword those who are doomed to the sword.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20010V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20010V\"></sup>I shall kindle a fire <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20010W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20010W\"></sup>in the temples of the gods of Egypt, and he shall burn them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20010X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20010X\"></sup>and carry them away captive. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20010Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20010Y\"></sup>And he shall clean the land of Egypt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20010Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20010Z\"></sup>as a shepherd cleans his cloak of vermin, and he shall go away from there in peace.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He shall break the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20011AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20011AA\"></sup>obelisks of Heliopolis, which is in the land of Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20011AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20011AB\"></sup>and the temples of the gods of Egypt he shall burn with fire.’”"
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>The word that came to Jeremiah concerning all the Judeans who lived in the land of Egypt, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20012A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20012A\"></sup>Migdol, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20012B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20012B\"></sup>Tahpanhes, at Memphis, and in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20012C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20012C\"></sup>Pathros,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: You have seen all the disaster that I brought upon Jerusalem and upon all the cities of Judah. Behold, this day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20013D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20013D\"></sup>they are a desolation, and no one dwells in them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>because of the evil that they committed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20014E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20014E\"></sup>provoking me to anger, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20014F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20014F\"></sup>in that they went to make offerings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20014G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20014G\"></sup>and serve other gods that they knew not, neither they, nor you, nor your fathers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20015H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20015H\"></sup>Yet I persistently sent to you all my servants the prophets, saying, ‘Oh, do not do this abomination that I hate!’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20016I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20016I\"></sup>But they did not listen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20016J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20016J\"></sup>or incline their ear, to turn from their evil and make no offerings to other gods.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20017K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20017K\"></sup>Therefore my wrath and my anger were poured out and kindled in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20017L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20017L\"></sup>and they became a waste and a desolation, as at this day.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And now thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of hosts, the God of Israel: Why do you commit this great evil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20018M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20018M\"></sup>against yourselves, to cut off from you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20018N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20018N\"></sup>man and woman, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20018O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20018O\"></sup>infant and child, from the midst of Judah, leaving you no remnant?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20019P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20019P\"></sup>Why do you provoke me to anger with the works of your hands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20019Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20019Q\"></sup>making offerings to other gods in the land of Egypt where you have come to live, so that you may be cut off and become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20019R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20019R\"></sup>a curse and a taunt among all the nations of the earth?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Have you forgotten the evil of your fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20020S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20020S\"></sup>the evil of the kings of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20020T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20020T\"></sup>the evil of their wives, your own evil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20020U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20020U\"></sup>and the evil of your wives, which they committed in the land of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They have not humbled themselves even to this day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20021V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20021V\"></sup>nor have they feared, nor walked in my law and my statutes that I set before you and before your fathers.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20022W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20022W\"></sup>Behold, I will set my face against you for harm, to cut off all Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will take the remnant of Judah who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20023X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20023X\"></sup>set their faces to come to the land of Egypt to live, and they shall all be consumed. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20023Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20023Y\"></sup>In the land of Egypt they shall fall; by the sword and by famine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20023Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20023Z\"></sup>they shall be consumed. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20023AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20023AA\"></sup>From the least to the greatest, they shall die by the sword and by famine, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20023AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20023AB\"></sup>and they shall become an oath, a horror, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20023AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20023AC\"></sup>a curse, and a taunt.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20024AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20024AD\"></sup>I will punish those who dwell in the land of Egypt, as I have punished Jerusalem, with the sword, with famine, and with pestilence,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20025AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20025AE\"></sup>so that none of the remnant of Judah who have come to live in the land of Egypt shall escape or survive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20025AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20025AF\"></sup>or return to the land of Judah, to which they desire to return to dwell there. For they shall not return, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20025AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20025AG\"></sup>except some fugitives.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then all the men who knew that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20026AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20026AH\"></sup>their wives had made offerings to other gods, and all the women who stood by, a great assembly, all the people who lived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20026AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20026AI\"></sup>Pathros in the land of Egypt, answered Jeremiah:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“As for the word that you have spoken to us in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20027AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20027AJ\"></sup>we will not listen to you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20028AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20028AK\"></sup>But we will do everything that we have vowed, make offerings to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20028AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20028AL\"></sup>the queen of heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20028AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20028AM\"></sup>and pour out drink offerings to her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20028AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20028AN\"></sup>as we did, both we and our fathers, our kings and our officials, in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem. For then we had plenty of food, and prospered, and saw no disaster.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But since we left off making offerings to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20029AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20029AO\"></sup>the queen of heaven and pouring out drink offerings to her, we have lacked everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20029AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20029AP\"></sup>and have been consumed by the sword and by famine.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And the women said, “When we made offerings to the queen of heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20030AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20030AQ\"></sup>and poured out drink offerings to her, was it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20030AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20030AR\"></sup>without our husbands' approval that we made cakes for her bearing her image and poured out drink offerings to her?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to all the people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20031AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20031AS\"></sup>men and women, all the people who had given him this answer:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20032AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20032AT\"></sup>“As for the offerings that you offered in the cities of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem, you and your fathers, your kings and your officials, and the people of the land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20032AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20032AU\"></sup>did not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> remember them? Did it not come into his mind?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20033AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20033AV\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> could no longer bear your evil deeds and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20033AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20033AW\"></sup>the abominations that you committed. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20033AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20033AX\"></sup>Therefore your land has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20033AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20033AY\"></sup>a desolation and a waste and a curse, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20033AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20033AZ\"></sup>without inhabitant, as it is this day.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>It is because you made offerings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20034BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20034BA\"></sup>and because you sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and did not obey the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> or walk in his law and in his statutes and in his testimonies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20034BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20034BB\"></sup>that this disaster has happened to you, as at this day.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Jeremiah said to all the people and all the women, “Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20035BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20035BC\"></sup>all you of Judah who are in the land of Egypt.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20036BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20036BD\"></sup>You and your wives have declared with your mouths, and have fulfilled it with your hands, saying, ‘We will surely perform our vows that we have made, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20036BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20036BE\"></sup>to make offerings to the queen of heaven and to pour out drink offerings to her.’ Then confirm your vows and perform your vows!",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Therefore hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20037BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20037BF\"></sup>all you of Judah who dwell in the land of Egypt: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20037BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20037BG\"></sup>Behold, I have sworn by my great name, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20037BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20037BH\"></sup>that my name shall no more be invoked by the mouth of any man of Judah in all the land of Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20037BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20037BI\"></sup>saying, ‘As the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> lives.’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20038BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20038BJ\"></sup>Behold, I am watching over them for disaster and not for good. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20038BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20038BK\"></sup>All the men of Judah who are in the land of Egypt shall be consumed by the sword and by famine, until there is an end of them.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20039BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20039BL\"></sup>And those who escape the sword shall return from the land of Egypt to the land of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20039BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20039BM\"></sup>few in number; and all the remnant of Judah, who came to the land of Egypt to live, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20039BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20039BN\"></sup>shall know whose word will stand, mine or theirs.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>This shall be the sign to you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that I will punish you in this place, in order that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20040BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20040BO\"></sup>my words will surely stand against you for harm:",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Behold, I will give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20041BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20041BP\"></sup>Pharaoh Hophra king of Egypt into the hand of his enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20041BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20041BQ\"></sup>and into the hand of those who seek his life, as I gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20041BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20041BR\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, who was his enemy and sought his life.”"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>The word that Jeremiah the prophet spoke to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20042A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20042A\"></sup>Baruch the son of Neriah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20042B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20042B\"></sup>when he wrote these words in a book at the dictation of Jeremiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20042C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20042C\"></sup>in the fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, to you, O Baruch:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20044D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20044D\"></sup>‘Woe is me! For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has added sorrow to my pain. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20044E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20044E\"></sup>I am weary with my groaning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20044F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20044F\"></sup>and I find no rest.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Thus shall you say to him, Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20045G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20045G\"></sup>Behold, what I have built I am breaking down, and what I have planted I am plucking up—that is, the whole land.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20046H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20046H\"></sup>do you seek great things for yourself? Seek them not, for behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20046I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20046I\"></sup>I am bringing disaster upon all flesh, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. But I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20046J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20046J\"></sup>your life as a prize of war in all places to which you may go.”"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20047A\"></sup>concerning the nations.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>About Egypt. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20048B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20048B\"></sup>Concerning the army of Pharaoh Neco, king of Egypt, which was by the river Euphrates at Carchemish and which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon defeated in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20048C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20048C\"></sup>the fourth year of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah, king of Judah:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20049D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20049D\"></sup>“Prepare buckler and shield,and advance for battle!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20050E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20050E\"></sup>Harness the horses;mount, O horsemen!Take your stations with your helmets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20050F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20050F\"></sup>polish your spears,put on your armor!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Why have I seen it?They are dismayedand have turned backward.Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20051G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20051G\"></sup>warriors are beaten downand have fled in haste;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20051H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20051H\"></sup>they look not back—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20051I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20051I\"></sup>terror on every side!declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“The swift cannot flee away,nor the warrior escape;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20052J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20052J\"></sup>in the north by the river Euphrates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20052K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20052K\"></sup>they have stumbled and fallen.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Who is this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20053L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20053L\"></sup>rising like the Nile,like rivers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20053M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20053M\"></sup>whose waters surge?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Egypt rises like the Nile,like rivers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20054N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20054N\"></sup>whose waters surge.He said, ‘I will rise, I will cover the earth,I will destroy cities and their inhabitants.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20055O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20055O\"></sup>Advance, O horses,and rage, O chariots!Let the warriors go out:men of Cush and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20055P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20055P\"></sup>Put who handle the shield,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20055Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20055Q\"></sup>men of Lud, skilled in handling the bow.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056R\"></sup>That day is the day of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056S\"></sup>a day of vengeance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056T\"></sup>to avenge himself on his foes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056U\"></sup>The sword shall devour and be satedand drink its fill of their blood.For the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts holds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056V\"></sup>a sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056W\"></sup>in the north country <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20056X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20056X\"></sup>by the river Euphrates.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20057Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20057Y\"></sup>Go up to Gilead, and take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20057Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20057Z\"></sup>balm,O virgin daughter of Egypt!In vain you have used many medicines;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20057AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20057AA\"></sup>there is no healing for you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The nations have heard of your shame,and the earth is full of your cry;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20058AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20058AB\"></sup>for warrior has stumbled against warrior;they have both fallen together.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Jeremiah the prophet about the coming of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20059AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20059AC\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon to strike the land of Egypt:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Declare in Egypt, and proclaim in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20060AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20060AD\"></sup>Migdol;proclaim in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20060AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20060AE\"></sup>Memphis and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20060AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20060AF\"></sup>Tahpanhes;say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20060AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20060AG\"></sup>‘Stand ready and be prepared,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20060AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20060AH\"></sup>the sword shall devour around you.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Why are your mighty ones face down?They do not standbecause the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> thrust them down.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He made many stumble, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20062AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20062AI\"></sup>and they fell,and they said one to another,‘Arise, and let us go back to our own peopleand to the land of our birth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20062AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20062AJ\"></sup>because of the sword of the oppressor.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Call the name of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20063AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20063AK\"></sup>Pharaoh, king of Egypt,‘Noisy one who lets the hour go by.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20064AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20064AL\"></sup>“As I live, declares the King,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20064AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20064AM\"></sup>whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20064AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20064AN\"></sup>Tabor among the mountainsand like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20064AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20064AO\"></sup>Carmel by the sea, shall one come.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20065AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20065AP\"></sup>Prepare yourselves baggage for exile,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20065AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20065AQ\"></sup>inhabitants of Egypt!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20065AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20065AR\"></sup>Memphis shall become a waste,a ruin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20065AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20065AS\"></sup>without inhabitant.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“A beautiful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20066AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20066AT\"></sup>heifer is Egypt,but a biting fly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20066AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20066AU\"></sup>from the north has come upon her.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Even her hired soldiers in her midstare like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20067AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20067AV\"></sup>fattened calves;yes, they have turned and fled together;they did not stand,for the day of their calamity has come upon them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20067AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20067AW\"></sup>the time of their punishment.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“She makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20068AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20068AX\"></sup>a sound like a serpent gliding away;for her enemies march in forceand come against her with axes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20068AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20068AY\"></sup>like those who fell trees.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20069AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20069AZ\"></sup>They shall cut down her forest,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,though it is impenetrable,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20069BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20069BA\"></sup>they are more numerous than locusts;they are without number.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The daughter of Egypt shall be put to shame;she shall be delivered into the hand of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20070BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20070BB\"></sup>a people from the north.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, said: “Behold, I am bringing punishment upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20071BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20071BC\"></sup>Amon of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20071BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20071BD\"></sup>Thebes, and Pharaoh and Egypt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20071BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20071BE\"></sup>and her gods and her kings, upon Pharaoh and those who trust in him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20072BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20072BF\"></sup>I will deliver them into the hand of those who seek their life, into the hand of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and his officers. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20072BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20072BG\"></sup>Afterward Egypt shall be inhabited <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20072BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20072BH\"></sup>as in the days of old, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20073BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20073BI\"></sup>“But fear not, O Jacob my servant,nor be dismayed, O Israel,for behold, I will save you from far away,and your offspring from the land of their captivity.Jacob shall return and have quiet and ease,and none shall make him afraid.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20074BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20074BJ\"></sup>Fear not, O Jacob my servant,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,for I am with you.I will make a full end of all the nationsto which I have driven you,but of you I will not make a full end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20074BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20074BK\"></sup>I will discipline you in just measure,and I will by no means leave you unpunished.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah the prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20075A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20075A\"></sup>concerning the Philistines, before Pharaoh struck down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20075B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20075B\"></sup>Gaza.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20076C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20076C\"></sup>Behold, waters are rising <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20076D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20076D\"></sup>out of the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20076E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20076E\"></sup>and shall become an overflowing torrent;they shall overflow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20076F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20076F\"></sup>the land and all that fills it,the city and those who dwell in it.Men shall cry out,and every inhabitant of the land shall wail.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>At the noise of the stamping of the hoofs of his stallions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20077G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20077G\"></sup>at the rushing of his chariots, at the rumbling of their wheels,the fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20077H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20077H\"></sup>look not back to their children,so feeble are their hands,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>because of the day that is coming to destroyall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20078I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20078I\"></sup>the Philistines,to cut off from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20078J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20078J\"></sup>Tyre and Sidonevery helper that remains.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is destroying the Philistines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20078K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20078K\"></sup>the remnant of the coastland of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20078L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20078L\"></sup>Caphtor.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20079M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20079M\"></sup>Baldness has come upon Gaza;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20079N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20079N\"></sup>Ashkelon has perished.O remnant of their valley,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20079O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20079O\"></sup>how long will you gash yourselves?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20080P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20080P\"></sup>Ah, sword of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!How long till you are quiet?Put yourself into your scabbard;rest and be still!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>How can it be quiet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20081Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20081Q\"></sup>when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given it a charge?Against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20081R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20081R\"></sup>Ashkelon and against the seashore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20081S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20081S\"></sup>he has appointed it.”"
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20082A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20082A\"></sup>Concerning Moab.Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel:“Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20082B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20082B\"></sup>Nebo, for it is laid waste!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20082C\"></sup>Kiriathaim is put to shame, it is taken;the fortress is put to shame <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20082D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20082D\"></sup>and broken down;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>the renown of Moab is no more.In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20083E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20083E\"></sup>Heshbon they planned disaster against her:‘Come, let us cut her off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20083F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20083F\"></sup>from being a nation!’You also, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20083G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20083G\"></sup>Madmen, shall be brought to silence;the sword shall pursue you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“A voice! A cry from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20084H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20084H\"></sup>Horonaim,‘Desolation and great destruction!’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Moab is destroyed;her little ones have made a cry.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20086I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20086I\"></sup>For at the ascent of Luhiththey go up weeping;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20086J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20086J\"></sup>at the descent of Horonaimthey have heard the distressed cry of destruction.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Flee! Save yourselves!You will be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20087K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20087K\"></sup>a juniper in the desert!",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20088L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20088L\"></sup>because you trusted in your works and your treasures,you also shall be taken;and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20088M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20088M\"></sup>Chemosh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20088N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20088N\"></sup>shall go into exilewith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20088O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20088O\"></sup>his priests and his officials.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20089P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20089P\"></sup>The destroyer shall come upon every city,and no city shall escape;the valley shall perish,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20089Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20089Q\"></sup>the plain shall be destroyed,as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Give wings to Moab,for she would fly away;her cities shall become a desolation,with no inhabitant in them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20091R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20091R\"></sup>“Cursed is he who does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20091S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20091S\"></sup>the work of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> with slackness, and cursed is he who keeps back his sword from bloodshed.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Moab has been at ease from his youthand has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20092T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20092T\"></sup>settled on his dregs;he has not been emptied from vessel to vessel,nor has he gone into exile;so his taste remains in him,and his scent is not changed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore, behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when I shall send to him pourers who will pour him, and empty his vessels and break his jars in pieces.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20094U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20094U\"></sup>Moab shall be ashamed of Chemosh, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20094V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20094V\"></sup>the house of Israel was ashamed of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20094W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20094W\"></sup>Bethel, their confidence.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“How do you say, ‘We are heroesand mighty men of war’?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The destroyer of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20096X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20096X\"></sup>Moab and his cities has come up,and the choicest of his young men have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20096Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20096Y\"></sup>gone down to slaughter,declares <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20096Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20096Z\"></sup>the King, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20096AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20096AA\"></sup>whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The calamity of Moab is near at hand,and his affliction hastens swiftly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20098AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20098AB\"></sup>Grieve for him, all you who are around him,and all who know his name;say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20098AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20098AC\"></sup>‘How the mighty scepter is broken,the glorious staff.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20099AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20099AD\"></sup>“Come down from your glory,and sit on the parched ground,O inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20099AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20099AE\"></sup>Dibon!For the destroyer of Moab has come up against you;he has destroyed your strongholds.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20100AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20100AF\"></sup>Stand by the way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20100AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20100AG\"></sup>and watch,O inhabitant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20100AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20100AH\"></sup>Aroer!Ask him who flees and her who escapes;say, ‘What has happened?’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Moab is put to shame, for it is broken;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20101AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20101AI\"></sup>wail and cry!Tell it beside <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20101AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20101AJ\"></sup>the Arnon,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20101AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20101AK\"></sup>Moab is laid waste.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Judgment has come upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20102AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20102AL\"></sup>the tableland, upon Holon, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20102AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20102AM\"></sup>Jahzah, and Mephaath,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20103AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20103AN\"></sup>Dibon, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20103AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20103AO\"></sup>Nebo, and Beth-diblathaim,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20104AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20104AP\"></sup>Kiriathaim, and Beth-gamul, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20104AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20104AQ\"></sup>Beth-meon,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20105AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20105AR\"></sup>Kerioth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20105AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20105AS\"></sup>Bozrah, and all the cities of the land of Moab, far and near.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20106AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20106AT\"></sup>The horn of Moab is cut off, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20106AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20106AU\"></sup>his arm is broken, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20107AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20107AV\"></sup>“Make him drunk, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20107AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20107AW\"></sup>because he magnified himself against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, so that Moab shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20107AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20107AX\"></sup>wallow in his vomit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20107AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20107AY\"></sup>and he too shall be held in derision.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20108AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20108AZ\"></sup>Was not Israel a derision to you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20108BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20108BA\"></sup>Was he found among thieves, that whenever you spoke of him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20108BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20108BB\"></sup>you wagged your head?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20109BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20109BC\"></sup>“Leave the cities, and dwell in the rock,O inhabitants of Moab!Be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20109BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20109BD\"></sup>like the dove that nestsin the sides of the mouth of a gorge.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20110BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20110BE\"></sup>We have heard of the pride of Moab—he is very proud—of his loftiness, his pride, and his arrogance,and the haughtiness of his heart.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I know his insolence, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20111BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20111BF\"></sup>his boasts are false,his deeds are false.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20112BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20112BG\"></sup>Therefore I wail for Moab;I cry out for all Moab;for the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20112BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20112BH\"></sup>Kir-hareseth I mourn.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>More than for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20113BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20113BI\"></sup>Jazer I weep for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20113BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20113BJ\"></sup>O vine of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20113BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20113BK\"></sup>Sibmah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20113BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20113BL\"></sup>Your branches passed over the sea,reached to the Sea of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20113BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20113BM\"></sup>Jazer;on your summer fruits and your grapesthe destroyer has fallen.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20114BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20114BN\"></sup>Gladness and joy have been taken awayfrom the fruitful land of Moab;I have made the wine cease from the winepresses;no one treads them with shouts of joy;the shouting is not the shout of joy.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20115BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20115BO\"></sup>“From the outcry at Heshbon even to Elealeh, as far as Jahaz they utter their voice, from Zoar to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20115BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20115BP\"></sup>Horonaim and Eglath-shelishiyah. For the waters of Nimrim also have become desolate.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And I will bring to an end in Moab, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, him who offers sacrifice in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20116BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20116BQ\"></sup>the high place and makes offerings to his god.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Therefore my heart moans for Moab like a flute, and my heart moans like a flute for the men of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20117BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20117BR\"></sup>Kir-hareseth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20117BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20117BS\"></sup>Therefore the riches they gained have perished.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20118BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20118BT\"></sup>“For every head is shaved and every beard cut off. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20118BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20118BU\"></sup>On all the hands are gashes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20118BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20118BV\"></sup>around the waist is sackcloth.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>On all the housetops of Moab and in the squares there is nothing but lamentation, for I have broken Moab like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20119BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20119BW\"></sup>a vessel for which no one cares, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>How it is broken! How they wail! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20120BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20120BX\"></sup>How Moab has turned his back in shame! So Moab <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20120BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20120BY\"></sup>has become a derision and a horror to all that are around him.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20121BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20121BZ\"></sup>one shall fly swiftly like an eagle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20121CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20121CA\"></sup>and spread his wings against Moab;",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20122CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20122CB\"></sup>the cities shall be takenand the strongholds seized.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20122CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20122CC\"></sup>The heart of the warriors of Moab shall be in that daylike the heart of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20122CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20122CD\"></sup>a woman in her birth pains;",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Moab shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20123CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20123CE\"></sup>destroyed and be no longer a people,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20123CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20123CF\"></sup>he magnified himself against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20124CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20124CG\"></sup>Terror, pit, and snareare before you, O inhabitant of Moab!declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>He who flees from the terrorshall fall into the pit,and he who climbs out of the pitshall be caught in the snare.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20125CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20125CH\"></sup>For I will bring these things upon Moab,the year of their punishment,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“In the shadow of Heshbonfugitives stop without strength,for fire came out from Heshbon,flame from the house of Sihon;it has destroyed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20126CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20126CI\"></sup>the forehead of Moab,the crown of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20126CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20126CJ\"></sup>the sons of tumult.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20127CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20127CK\"></sup>Woe to you, O Moab!The people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20127CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20127CL\"></sup>Chemosh are undone,for your sons have been taken captive,and your daughters into captivity.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20128CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20128CM\"></sup>Yet I will restore the fortunes of Moabin the latter days, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”Thus far is the judgment on Moab."
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">49 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20129A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20129A\"></sup>Concerning the Ammonites.Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Has Israel no sons?Has he no heir?Why then has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20129B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20129B\"></sup>Milcom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20129C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20129C\"></sup>dispossessed Gad,and his people settled in its cities?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Therefore, behold, the days are coming,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,when I will cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20130D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20130D\"></sup>the battle cry to be heardagainst <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20130E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20130E\"></sup>Rabbah of the Ammonites;it shall become a desolate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20130F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20130F\"></sup>mound,and its villages shall be burned with fire;then Israel shall dispossess those who dispossessed him,says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20131G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20131G\"></sup>Heshbon, for Ai is laid waste!Cry out, O daughters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20131H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20131H\"></sup>Rabbah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20131I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20131I\"></sup>Put on sackcloth,lament, and run to and fro among the hedges!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20131J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20131J\"></sup>Milcom shall go into exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20131K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20131K\"></sup>with his priests and his officials.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Why do you boast of your valleys,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20132L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20132L\"></sup>O faithless daughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20132M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20132M\"></sup>who trusted in her treasures, saying,‘Who will come against me?’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20133N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20133N\"></sup>I will bring terror upon you,declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,from all who are around you,and you shall be driven out, every man straight before him,with none to gather the fugitives.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20134O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20134O\"></sup>afterward I will restore the fortunes of the Ammonites, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20135P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20135P\"></sup>Edom.Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20135Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20135Q\"></sup>“Is wisdom no more in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20135R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20135R\"></sup>Teman?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20135S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20135S\"></sup>Has counsel perished from the prudent?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20135T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20135T\"></sup>Has their wisdom vanished?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20136U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20136U\"></sup>Flee, turn back, dwell in the depths,O inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20136V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20136V\"></sup>Dedan!For I will bring the calamity of Esau upon him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20136W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20136W\"></sup>the time when I punish him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20137X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20137X\"></sup>If grape gatherers came to you,would they not leave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20137Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20137Y\"></sup>gleanings?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20137Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20137Z\"></sup>If thieves came by night,would they not destroy only enough for themselves?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20138AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20138AA\"></sup>But I have stripped Esau bare;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20138AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20138AB\"></sup>I have uncovered his hiding places,and he is not able to conceal himself.His children are destroyed, and his brothers,and his neighbors; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20138AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20138AC\"></sup>he is no more.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20139AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20139AD\"></sup>Leave your fatherless children; I will keep them alive;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20139AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20139AE\"></sup>and let your widows trust in me.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20140AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20140AF\"></sup>“If those who did not deserve to drink the cup must drink it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20140AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20140AG\"></sup>will you go unpunished? You shall not go unpunished, but you must drink.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20141AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20141AH\"></sup>For I have sworn by myself, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20141AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20141AI\"></sup>Bozrah shall become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20141AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20141AJ\"></sup>a horror, a taunt, a waste, and a curse, and all her cities shall be perpetual wastes.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20142AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20142AK\"></sup>I have heard a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and an envoy has been sent among the nations:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20142AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20142AL\"></sup>“Gather yourselves together and come against her,and rise up for battle!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For behold, I will make you small among the nations,despised among mankind.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The horror you inspire has deceived you,and the pride of your heart,you who live in the clefts of the rock,who hold the height of the hill.Though you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20144AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20144AM\"></sup>make your nest as high as the eagle's,I will bring you down from there,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20145AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20145AN\"></sup>“Edom shall become a horror. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20145AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20145AO\"></sup>Everyone who passes by it will be horrified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20145AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20145AP\"></sup>and will hiss because of all its disasters.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20146AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20146AQ\"></sup>As when Sodom and Gomorrah and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20146AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20146AR\"></sup>neighboring cities were overthrown, says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20146AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20146AS\"></sup>no man shall dwell there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20146AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20146AT\"></sup>no man shall sojourn in her.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20147AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20147AU\"></sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20147AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20147AV\"></sup>like a lion coming up from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20147AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20147AW\"></sup>the jungle of the Jordan against a perennial pasture, I will suddenly make him run away from her. And I will appoint over her whomever I choose. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20147AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20147AX\"></sup>For who is like me? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20147AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20147AY\"></sup>Who will summon me? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20147AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20147AZ\"></sup>What shepherd can stand before me?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore hear the plan that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20148BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20148BA\"></sup>Edom and the purposes that he has formed against the inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20148BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20148BB\"></sup>Teman: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20148BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20148BC\"></sup>Even the little ones of the flock shall be dragged away. Surely their fold shall be appalled at their fate.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>At the sound of their fall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20149BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20149BD\"></sup>the earth shall tremble; the sound of their cry shall be heard at the Red Sea.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20150BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20150BE\"></sup>one shall mount up and fly swiftly like an eagle and spread his wings against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20150BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20150BF\"></sup>Bozrah, and the heart of the warriors of Edom shall be in that day like the heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20150BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20150BG\"></sup>of a woman in her birth pains.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20151BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20151BH\"></sup>Damascus:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20151BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20151BI\"></sup>“Hamath and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20151BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20151BJ\"></sup>Arpad are confounded,for they have heard bad news;they melt in fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20151BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20151BK\"></sup>they are troubled like the sea that cannot be quiet.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20152BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20152BL\"></sup>Damascus has become feeble, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20152BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20152BM\"></sup>she turned to flee,and panic seized her;anguish and sorrows have taken hold of her,as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20152BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20152BN\"></sup>of a woman in labor.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>How is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20153BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20153BO\"></sup>the famous city not forsaken,the city of my joy?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20154BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20154BP\"></sup>Therefore her young men shall fall in her squares,and all her soldiers shall be destroyed in that day,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20155BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20155BQ\"></sup>I will kindle a fire in the wall of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20155BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20155BR\"></sup>Damascus,and it shall devour the strongholds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20155BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20155BS\"></sup>Ben-hadad.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20156BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20156BT\"></sup>Kedar and the kingdoms of Hazor that Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon struck down.Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20156BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20156BU\"></sup>“Rise up, advance against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20156BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20156BV\"></sup>Kedar!Destroy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20156BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20156BW\"></sup>the people of the east!",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20157BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20157BX\"></sup>Their tents and their flocks shall be taken,their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20157BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20157BY\"></sup>curtains and all their goods;their camels shall be led away from them,and men shall cry to them: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20157BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20157BZ\"></sup>‘Terror on every side!’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20158CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20158CA\"></sup>Flee, wander far away, dwell in the depths,O inhabitants of Hazor!declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.For Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylonhas made a plan against youand formed a purpose against you.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20159CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20159CB\"></sup>“Rise up, advance against a nation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20159CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20159CC\"></sup>at ease,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20159CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20159CD\"></sup>that dwells securely,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20159CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20159CE\"></sup>that has no gates or bars,that dwells alone.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20160CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20160CF\"></sup>Their camels shall become plunder,their herds of livestock a spoil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20160CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20160CG\"></sup>I will scatter to every wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20160CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20160CH\"></sup>those who cut the corners of their hair,and I will bring their calamityfrom every side of them,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Hazor shall become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20161CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20161CI\"></sup>a haunt of jackals,an everlasting waste;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20161CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20161CJ\"></sup>no man shall dwell there;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20161CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20161CK\"></sup>no man shall sojourn in her.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah the prophet concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20162CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20162CL\"></sup>Elam, in the beginning of the reign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20162CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20162CM\"></sup>Zedekiah king of Judah.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: “Behold, I will break <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20163CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20163CN\"></sup>the bow of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20163CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20163CO\"></sup>Elam, the mainstay of their might.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And I will bring upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20164CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20164CP\"></sup>Elam the four winds from the four quarters of heaven. And I will scatter them to all those winds, and there shall be no nation to which those driven out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20164CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20164CQ\"></sup>Elam shall not come.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20165CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20165CR\"></sup>terrify <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20165CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20165CS\"></sup>Elam before their enemies and before those who seek their life. I will bring disaster upon them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20165CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20165CT\"></sup>my fierce anger, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20165CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20165CU\"></sup>I will send the sword after them, until I have consumed them,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>and I will set my throne in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20166CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20166CV\"></sup>Elam and destroy their king and officials, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“But in the latter days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20167CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20167CW\"></sup>I will restore the fortunes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20167CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20167CX\"></sup>Elam, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">50 </span>The word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20168A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20168A\"></sup>Babylon, concerning the land of the Chaldeans, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20168B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20168B\"></sup>by Jeremiah the prophet:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Declare among the nations and proclaim,set up a banner and proclaim,conceal it not, and say:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20169C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20169C\"></sup>‘Babylon is taken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20169D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20169D\"></sup>Bel is put to shame,Merodach is dismayed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20169E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20169E\"></sup>Her images are put to shame,her idols are dismayed.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20170F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20170F\"></sup>out of the north a nation has come up against her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20170G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20170G\"></sup>which shall make her land a desolation, and none shall dwell in it; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20170H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20170H\"></sup>both man and beast shall flee away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20171I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20171I\"></sup>“In those days and in that time, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20171J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20171J\"></sup>the people of Israel and the people of Judah shall come together, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20171K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20171K\"></sup>weeping as they come, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20171L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20171L\"></sup>shall seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20172M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20172M\"></sup>They shall ask the way to Zion, with faces turned toward it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20172N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20172N\"></sup>saying, ‘Come, let us join ourselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20172O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20172O\"></sup>everlasting covenant that will never be forgotten.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20173P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20173P\"></sup>“My people have been lost sheep. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20173Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20173Q\"></sup>Their shepherds have led them astray, turning them away on the mountains. From mountain to hill they have gone. They have forgotten their fold.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All who found them have devoured them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20174R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20174R\"></sup>and their enemies have said, ‘We are not guilty, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20174S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20174S\"></sup>they have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20174T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20174T\"></sup>their habitation of righteousness, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20174U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20174U\"></sup>the hope of their fathers.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20175V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20175V\"></sup>“Flee from the midst of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20175W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20175W\"></sup>and go out of the land of the Chaldeans, and be as male goats before the flock.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For behold, I am stirring up and bringing against Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20176X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20176X\"></sup>a gathering of great nations, from the north country. And they shall array themselves against her. From there she shall be taken. Their arrows are like a skilled warrior who does not return empty-handed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20177Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20177Y\"></sup>Chaldea shall be plundered; all who plunder her shall be sated, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20178Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20178Z\"></sup>“Though you rejoice, though you exult,O plunderers of my heritage,though you frolic like a heifer in the pasture,and neigh like stallions,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>your mother shall be utterly shamed,and she who bore you shall be disgraced.Behold, she shall be the last of the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20179AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20179AA\"></sup>a wilderness, a dry land, and a desert.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20180AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20180AB\"></sup>Because of the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> she shall not be inhabitedbut shall be an utter desolation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20180AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20180AC\"></sup>everyone who passes by Babylon shall be appalled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20180AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20180AD\"></sup>and hiss because of all her wounds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20181AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20181AE\"></sup>Set yourselves in array against Babylon all around,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20181AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20181AF\"></sup>all you who bend the bow;shoot at her, spare no arrows,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20181AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20181AG\"></sup>for she has sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20182AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20182AH\"></sup>Raise a shout against her all around;she has surrendered;her bulwarks have fallen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20182AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20182AI\"></sup>her walls are thrown down.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20182AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20182AJ\"></sup>this is the vengeance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:take vengeance on her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20182AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20182AK\"></sup>do to her as she has done.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Cut off from Babylon the sower,and the one who handles the sickle in time of harvest;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20183AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20183AL\"></sup>because of the sword of the oppressor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20183AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20183AM\"></sup>every one shall turn to his own people,and every one shall flee to his own land.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20184AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20184AN\"></sup>“Israel is a hunted sheep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20184AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20184AO\"></sup>driven away by lions. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20184AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20184AP\"></sup>First the king of Assyria <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20184AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20184AQ\"></sup>devoured him, and now at last <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20184AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20184AR\"></sup>Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20184AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20184AS\"></sup>has gnawed his bones.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel: Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20185AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20185AT\"></sup>I am bringing punishment on the king of Babylon and his land, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20185AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20185AU\"></sup>as I punished the king of Assyria.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20186AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20186AV\"></sup>I will restore Israel to his pasture, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20186AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20186AW\"></sup>he shall feed on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20186AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20186AX\"></sup>Carmel and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20186AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20186AY\"></sup>Bashan, and his desire shall be satisfied on the hills of Ephraim and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20186AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20186AZ\"></sup>Gilead.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In those days and in that time, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20187BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20187BA\"></sup>iniquity shall be sought in Israel, and there shall be none, and sin in Judah, and none shall be found, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20187BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20187BB\"></sup>I will pardon those whom I leave as a remnant.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Go up against the land of Merathaim,and against the inhabitants of Pekod.Kill, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20188BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20188BC\"></sup>and devote them to destruction,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and do all that I have commanded you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20189BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20189BD\"></sup>The noise of battle is in the land,and great destruction!",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20190BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20190BE\"></sup>How the hammer of the whole earthis cut down and broken!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20190BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20190BF\"></sup>How Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20190BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20190BG\"></sup>has becomea horror among the nations!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20191BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20191BH\"></sup>I set a snare for you and you were taken, O Babylon,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20191BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20191BI\"></sup>you did not know it;you were found and caught,because you opposed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has opened his armoryand brought out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20192BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20192BJ\"></sup>the weapons of his wrath,for the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts has a work to doin the land of the Chaldeans.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Come against her from every quarter;open her granaries;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20193BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20193BK\"></sup>pile her up like heaps of grain, and devote her to destruction;let nothing be left of her.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Kill all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20194BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20194BL\"></sup>her bulls;let them go down to the slaughter.Woe to them, for their day has come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20194BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20194BM\"></sup>the time of their punishment.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“A voice! They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20195BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20195BN\"></sup>flee and escape from the land of Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20195BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20195BO\"></sup>to declare in Zion the vengeance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, vengeance for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20195BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20195BP\"></sup>his temple.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20196BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20196BQ\"></sup>“Summon archers against Babylon, all those who bend the bow. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20196BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20196BR\"></sup>Encamp around her; let no one escape. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20196BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20196BS\"></sup>Repay her according to her deeds; do to her according to all that she has done. For she has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20196BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20196BT\"></sup>proudly defied the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Holy One of Israel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20197BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20197BU\"></sup>Therefore her young men shall fall in her squares, and all her soldiers shall be destroyed on that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Behold, I am against you, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20198BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20198BV\"></sup>proud one,declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20198BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20198BW\"></sup>for your day has come,the time when I will punish you.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20199BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20199BX\"></sup>The proud one shall stumble and fall,with none to raise him up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20199BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20199BY\"></sup>and I will kindle a fire in his cities,and it will devour all that is around him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20200BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20200BZ\"></sup>The people of Israel are oppressed, and the people of Judah with them. All who took them captive have held them fast; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20200CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20200CA\"></sup>they refuse to let them go.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20201CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20201CB\"></sup>Their Redeemer is strong; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20201CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20201CC\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20201CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20201CD\"></sup>He will surely plead their cause, that he may give rest to the earth, but unrest to the inhabitants of Babylon.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“A sword against the Chaldeans, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and against the inhabitants of Babylon,and against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20202CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20202CE\"></sup>her officials and her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20202CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20202CF\"></sup>wise men!",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>A sword against the diviners,that they may become fools!A sword against her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20203CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20203CG\"></sup>warriors,that they may be destroyed!",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>A sword against her horses and against her chariots,and against all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20204CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20204CH\"></sup>the foreign troops in her midst,that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20204CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20204CI\"></sup>they may become women!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20204CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20204CJ\"></sup>A sword against all her treasures,that they may be plundered!",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20205CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20205CK\"></sup>A drought against her waters,that they may be dried up!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20205CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20205CL\"></sup>For it is a land of images,and they are mad over idols.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20206CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20206CM\"></sup>“Therefore wild beasts shall dwell with hyenas in Babylon, and ostriches shall dwell in her. She shall never again have people, nor be inhabited for all generations.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20207CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20207CN\"></sup>As when God overthrew Sodom and Gomorrah and their neighboring cities, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20207CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20207CO\"></sup>so no man shall dwell there, and no son of man shall sojourn in her.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20208CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20208CP\"></sup>“Behold, a people comes from the north;a mighty nation and many kingsare stirring from the farthest parts of the earth.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They lay hold of bow and spear;they are cruel and have no mercy.The sound of them is like the roaring of the sea;they ride on horses,arrayed as a man for battleagainst you, O daughter of Babylon!",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“The king of Babylon heard the report of them,and his hands fell helpless;anguish seized him,pain as of a woman in labor.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20211CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20211CQ\"></sup>“Behold, like a lion coming up from the thicket of the Jordan against a perennial pasture, I will suddenly make them run away from her, and I will appoint over her whomever I choose. For who is like me? Who will summon me? What shepherd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20211CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20211CR\"></sup>can stand before me?",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Therefore hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20212CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20212CS\"></sup>the plan that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made against Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20212CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20212CT\"></sup>and the purposes that he has formed against the land of the Chaldeans: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20212CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20212CU\"></sup>Surely the little ones of their flock shall be dragged away; surely their fold shall be appalled at their fate.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20213CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20213CV\"></sup>At the sound of the capture of Babylon the earth shall tremble, and her cry shall be heard among the nations.”"
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">51 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Behold, I will stir up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20214A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20214A\"></sup>the spirit of a destroyeragainst Babylon,against the inhabitants of Leb-kamai,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and I will send to Babylon winnowers,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20215B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20215B\"></sup>they shall winnow her,and they shall empty her land,when they come against her from every side<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20215C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20215C\"></sup>on the day of trouble.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20216D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20216D\"></sup>Let not the archer bend his bow,and let him not stand up in his armor.Spare not her young men;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20216E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20216E\"></sup>devote to destruction all her army.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They shall fall down slain in the land of the Chaldeans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20217F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20217F\"></sup>and wounded in her streets.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20218G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20218G\"></sup>For Israel and Judah have not been forsakenby their God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,but the land of the Chaldeans is full of guiltagainst the Holy One of Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20219H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20219H\"></sup>“Flee from the midst of Babylon;let every one save his life!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20219I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20219I\"></sup>Be not cut off in her punishment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20219J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20219J\"></sup>for this is the time of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s vengeance,the repayment he is rendering her.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Babylon was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20220K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20220K\"></sup>a golden cup in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20220L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20220L\"></sup>making all the earth drunken;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20220M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20220M\"></sup>the nations drank of her wine;therefore the nations went mad.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20221N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20221N\"></sup>Suddenly Babylon has fallen and been broken;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20221O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20221O\"></sup>wail for her!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20221P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20221P\"></sup>Take balm for her pain;perhaps she may be healed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We would have healed Babylon,but she was not healed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20222Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20222Q\"></sup>Forsake her, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20222R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20222R\"></sup>let us goeach to his own country,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20222S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20222S\"></sup>her judgment has reached up to heavenand has been lifted up even to the skies.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20223T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20223T\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought about our vindication;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20223U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20223U\"></sup>come, let us declare in Zionthe work of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20224V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20224V\"></sup>“Sharpen the arrows!Take up the shields!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20224W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20224W\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has stirred up the spirit of the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20224X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20224X\"></sup>the Medes, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20224Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20224Y\"></sup>his purpose concerning Babylon is to destroy it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20224Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20224Z\"></sup>for that is the vengeance of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the vengeance for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20224AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20224AA\"></sup>his temple.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20225AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20225AB\"></sup>“Set up a standard against the walls of Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20225AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20225AC\"></sup>make the watch strong;set up watchmen;prepare the ambushes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20225AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20225AD\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has both planned and donewhat he spoke concerning the inhabitants of Babylon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20226AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20226AE\"></sup>O you who dwell by many waters,rich in treasures,your end has come;the thread of your life is cut.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20227AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20227AF\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sworn by himself:Surely I will fill you with men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20227AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20227AG\"></sup>as many as locusts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20227AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20227AH\"></sup>and they shall raise the shout of victory over you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20228AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20228AI\"></sup>“It is he who made the earth by his power,who established the world by his wisdom,and by his understanding stretched out the heavens.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When he utters his voice there is a tumult of waters in the heavens,and he makes the mist rise from the ends of the earth.He makes lightning for the rain,and he brings forth the wind from his storehouses.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Every man is stupid and without knowledge;every goldsmith is put to shame by his idols,for his images are false,and there is no breath in them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They are worthless, a work of delusion;at the time of their punishment they shall perish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Not like these is he who is the portion of Jacob,for he is the one who formed all things,and Israel is the tribe of his inheritance;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is his name.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“You are my hammer and weapon of war:with you I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20233AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20233AJ\"></sup>break nations in pieces;with you I destroy kingdoms;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>with you I break in pieces the horse and his rider;with you I break in pieces the chariot and the charioteer;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>with you I break in pieces man and woman;with you I break in pieces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20235AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20235AK\"></sup>the old man and the youth;with you I break in pieces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20235AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20235AL\"></sup>the young man and the young woman;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>with you I break in pieces the shepherd and his flock;with you I break in pieces the farmer and his team;with you I break in pieces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20236AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20236AM\"></sup>governors and commanders.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20237AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20237AN\"></sup>“I will repay Babylon and all the inhabitants of Chaldea before your very eyes for all the evil that they have done in Zion, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Behold, I am against you, O destroying mountain,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,which destroys the whole earth;I will stretch out my hand against you,and roll you down from the crags,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20238AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20238AO\"></sup>and make you a burnt mountain.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20239AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20239AP\"></sup>stone shall be taken from you for a cornerand no stone for a foundation,but you shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20239AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20239AQ\"></sup>a perpetual waste,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AR\"></sup>“Set up a standard on the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AS\"></sup>blow the trumpet among the nations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AT\"></sup>prepare <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AU\"></sup>the nations for war against her;summon against her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AV\"></sup>the kingdoms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AW\"></sup>Ararat, Minni, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AX\"></sup>Ashkenaz;appoint a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AY\"></sup>marshal against her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20240AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20240AZ\"></sup>bring up horses like bristling locusts.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20241BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20241BA\"></sup>Prepare <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20241BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20241BB\"></sup>the nations for war against her,the kings of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20241BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20241BC\"></sup>the Medes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20241BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20241BD\"></sup>with their governors <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20241BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20241BE\"></sup>and deputies,and every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20241BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20241BF\"></sup>land under their dominion.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20242BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20242BG\"></sup>The land trembles and writhes in pain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20242BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20242BH\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s purposes against Babylon stand,to make the land of Babylon a desolation,without inhabitant.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The warriors of Babylon have ceased fighting;they remain in their strongholds;their strength has failed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20243BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20243BI\"></sup>they have become women;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20243BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20243BJ\"></sup>her dwellings are on fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20243BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20243BK\"></sup>her bars are broken.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20244BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20244BL\"></sup>runner runs to meet another,and one messenger to meet another,to tell the king of Babylonthat his city is taken on every side;",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>the fords have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20245BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20245BM\"></sup>seized,the marshes are burned with fire,and the soldiers are in panic.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20246BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20246BN\"></sup>The daughter of Babylon is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20246BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20246BO\"></sup>a threshing floorat the time when it is trodden;yet a little whileand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20246BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20246BP\"></sup>the time of her harvest will come.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Nebuchadnezzar the king of Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20247BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20247BQ\"></sup>has devoured me;he has crushed me;he has made me an empty vessel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20247BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20247BR\"></sup>he has swallowed me like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20247BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20247BS\"></sup>a monster;he has filled his stomach with my delicacies;he has rinsed me out.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The violence done to me and to my kinsmen be upon Babylon,”let the inhabitant of Zion say.“My blood be upon the inhabitants of Chaldea,”let Jerusalem say.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20249BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20249BT\"></sup>I will plead your causeand take vengeance for you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20249BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20249BU\"></sup>I will dry up her seaand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20249BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20249BV\"></sup>make her fountain dry,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>and Babylon shall become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20250BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20250BW\"></sup>a heap of ruins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20250BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20250BX\"></sup>the haunt of jackals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20250BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20250BY\"></sup>a horror <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20250BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20250BZ\"></sup>and a hissing,without inhabitant.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20251CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20251CA\"></sup>“They shall roar together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20251CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20251CB\"></sup>like lions;they shall growl like lions' cubs.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20252CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20252CC\"></sup>While they are inflamed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20252CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20252CD\"></sup>I will prepare them a feastand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20252CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20252CE\"></sup>make them drunk, that they may become merry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20252CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20252CF\"></sup>then sleep a perpetual sleepand not wake, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>I will bring them down like lambs to the slaughter,like rams and male goats.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20254CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20254CG\"></sup>Babylon is taken,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20254CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20254CH\"></sup>the praise of the whole earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20254CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20254CI\"></sup>seized!How Babylon has becomea horror among the nations!",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20255CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20255CJ\"></sup>The sea has come up on Babylon;she is covered with its tumultuous waves.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Her cities have become a horror,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20256CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20256CK\"></sup>a land of drought and a desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20256CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20256CL\"></sup>a land in which no one dwells,and through which no son of man passes.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And I will punish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20257CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20257CM\"></sup>Bel in Babylon,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20257CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20257CN\"></sup>take out of his mouth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20257CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20257CO\"></sup>what he has swallowed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20257CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20257CP\"></sup>The nations shall no longer flow to him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20257CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20257CQ\"></sup>the wall of Babylon has fallen.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“Go out of the midst of her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20258CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20258CR\"></sup>my people!Let every one save his lifefrom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20258CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20258CS\"></sup>the fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Let not your heart faint, and be not fearful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20259CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20259CT\"></sup>at the report heard in the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20259CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20259CU\"></sup>when a report comes in one yearand afterward a report in another year,and violence is in the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20259CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20259CV\"></sup>and ruler is against ruler.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>“Therefore, behold, the days are comingwhen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20260CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20260CW\"></sup>I will punish the images of Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20260CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20260CX\"></sup>her whole land shall be put to shame,and all her slain shall fall in the midst of her.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20261CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20261CY\"></sup>Then the heavens and the earth,and all that is in them,shall sing for joy over Babylon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20261CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20261CZ\"></sup>for the destroyers shall come against them out of the north,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Babylon must fall for the slain of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20262DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20262DA\"></sup>just as for Babylon have fallen the slain of all the earth.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20263DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20263DB\"></sup>“You who have escaped from the sword,go, do not stand still!Remember the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from far away,and let Jerusalem come into your mind:",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20264DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20264DC\"></sup>‘We are put to shame, for we have heard reproach;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20264DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20264DD\"></sup>dishonor has covered our face,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20264DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20264DE\"></sup>for foreigners have comeinto the holy places of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s house.’",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>“Therefore, behold, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20265DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20265DF\"></sup>I will execute judgment upon her images,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20265DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20265DG\"></sup>and through all her landthe wounded shall groan.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>Though Babylon should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20266DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20266DH\"></sup>mount up to heaven,and though she should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20266DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20266DI\"></sup>fortify her strong height,yet destroyers would come from me against her,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20267DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20267DJ\"></sup>“A voice! A cry from Babylon!The noise of great destruction from the land of the Chaldeans!",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is laying Babylon wasteand stilling her mighty voice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20268DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20268DK\"></sup>Their waves roar like many waters;the noise of their voice is raised,",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>for a destroyer has come upon her,upon Babylon;her warriors are taken;their bows are broken in pieces,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20269DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20269DL\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a God of recompense;he will surely repay.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20270DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20270DM\"></sup>I will make drunk her officials and her wise men,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20270DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20270DN\"></sup>her governors, her commanders, and her warriors;they shall sleep a perpetual sleep and not wake,declares <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20270DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20270DO\"></sup>the King, whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:The broad <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20271DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20271DP\"></sup>wall of Babylonshall be leveled to the ground,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20271DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20271DQ\"></sup>and her high gatesshall be burned with fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20271DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20271DR\"></sup>The peoples labor for nothing,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20271DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20271DS\"></sup>the nations weary themselves only for fire.”",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>The word that Jeremiah the prophet commanded Seraiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20272DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20272DT\"></sup>the son of Neriah, son of Mahseiah, when he went with Zedekiah king of Judah to Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20272DU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DU&quot;&gt;DU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20272DU\"></sup>in the fourth year of his reign. Seraiah was the quartermaster.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20273DV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DV&quot;&gt;DV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20273DV\"></sup>Jeremiah wrote in a book all the disaster that should come upon Babylon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20273DW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DW&quot;&gt;DW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20273DW\"></sup>all these words that are written concerning Babylon.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>And Jeremiah said to Seraiah: “When you come to Babylon, see that you read all these words,",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>and say, ‘O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you have said concerning this place that you will cut it off, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20275DX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DX&quot;&gt;DX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20275DX\"></sup>that nothing shall dwell in it, neither man nor beast, and it shall be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20275DY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DY&quot;&gt;DY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20275DY\"></sup>desolate forever.’",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>When you finish reading this book, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20276DZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DZ&quot;&gt;DZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20276DZ\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20276EA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EA&quot;&gt;EA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20276EA\"></sup>tie a stone to it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20276EB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EB&quot;&gt;EB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20276EB\"></sup>and cast it into the midst of the Euphrates,",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>and say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20277EC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EC&quot;&gt;EC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20277EC\"></sup>‘Thus shall Babylon sink, to rise no more, because of the disaster that I am bringing upon her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20277ED&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ED&quot;&gt;ED&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20277ED\"></sup>and they shall become exhausted.’”Thus far are the words of Jeremiah."
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">52 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20278A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20278A\"></sup>Zedekiah was twenty-one years old when he became king, and he reigned eleven years in Jerusalem. His mother's name was Hamutal the daughter of Jeremiah of Libnah.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he did what was evil in the sight of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20279B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20279B\"></sup>according to all that Jehoiakim had done.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For because of the anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> it came to the point in Jerusalem and Judah that he cast them out from his presence.And Zedekiah rebelled against the king of Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20281C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20281C\"></sup>And in the ninth year of his reign, in the tenth month, on the tenth day of the month, Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon came with all his army against Jerusalem, and laid siege to it. And they built siegeworks all around it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So the city was besieged till the eleventh year of King Zedekiah.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On the ninth day of the fourth month the famine was so severe in the city that there was no food for the people of the land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then a breach was made in the city, and all the men of war fled and went out from the city by night by the way of a gate between the two walls, by the king's garden, and the Chaldeans were around the city. And they went in the direction of the Arabah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the army of the Chaldeans pursued the king and overtook Zedekiah in the plains of Jericho, and all his army was scattered from him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then they captured the king and brought him up to the king of Babylon at Riblah in the land of Hamath, and he passed sentence on him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The king of Babylon slaughtered the sons of Zedekiah before his eyes, and also slaughtered all the officials of Judah at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20287D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20287D\"></sup>Riblah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20288E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20288E\"></sup>He put out the eyes of Zedekiah, and bound him in chains, and the king of Babylon took him to Babylon, and put him in prison <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20288F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20288F\"></sup>till the day of his death.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20289G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20289G\"></sup>In the fifth month, on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20289H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20289H\"></sup>the tenth day of the month—that was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20289I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20289I\"></sup>the nineteenth year of King Nebuchadnezzar, king of Babylon—Nebuzaradan the captain of the bodyguard, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20289J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20289J\"></sup>served the king of Babylon, entered Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he burned the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and the king's house and all the houses of Jerusalem; every great house he burned down.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And all the army of the Chaldeans, who were with the captain of the guard, broke down all the walls around Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard carried away captive some of the poorest of the people and the rest of the people who were left in the city and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20292K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20292K\"></sup>the deserters who had deserted to the king of Babylon, together with the rest of the artisans.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard left some of the poorest of the land to be vinedressers and plowmen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20294L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20294L\"></sup>pillars of bronze that were in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and the stands and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20294M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20294M\"></sup>bronze sea that were in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Chaldeans broke in pieces, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20294N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20294N\"></sup>carried all the bronze to Babylon.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And they took away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20295O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20295O\"></sup>the pots and the shovels and the snuffers and the basins and the dishes for incense and all the vessels of bronze used in the temple service;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20296P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20296P\"></sup>also the small bowls and the fire pans and the basins and the pots and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20296Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20296Q\"></sup>the lampstands and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20296R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20296R\"></sup>the dishes for incense <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20296S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20296S\"></sup>and the bowls for drink offerings. What was of gold the captain of the guard took away as gold, and what was of silver, as silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As for the two pillars, the one sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20297T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20297T\"></sup>the twelve bronze bulls that were under the sea, and the stands, which Solomon the king had made for the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the bronze of all these things was beyond weight.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>As for the pillars, the height of the one pillar was eighteen cubits, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20298U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20298U\"></sup>its circumference was twelve cubits, and its thickness was four fingers, and it was hollow.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>On it was a capital of bronze. The height of the one capital was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20299V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20299V\"></sup>five cubits. A network and pomegranates, all of bronze, were around the capital. And the second pillar had the same, with pomegranates.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>There were ninety-six pomegranates on the sides; all the pomegranates were a hundred upon the network all around.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And the captain of the guard took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20301W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20301W\"></sup>Seraiah the chief priest, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20301X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20301X\"></sup>Zephaniah the second priest and the three keepers of the threshold;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and from the city he took an officer who had been in command of the men of war, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20302Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20302Y\"></sup>seven men of the king's council, who were found in the city; and the secretary of the commander of the army, who mustered the people of the land; and sixty men of the people of the land, who were found in the midst of the city.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard took them and brought them to the king of Babylon at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20303Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20303Z\"></sup>Riblah.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And the king of Babylon struck them down and put them to death at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20304AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20304AA\"></sup>Riblah in the land of Hamath. So Judah was taken into exile out of its land.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>This is the number of the people whom Nebuchadnezzar carried away captive: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20305AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20305AB\"></sup>in the seventh year, 3,023 Judeans;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20306AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20306AC\"></sup>in the eighteenth year of Nebuchadnezzar he carried away captive from Jerusalem 832 persons;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>in the twenty-third year of Nebuchadnezzar, Nebuzaradan the captain of the guard carried away captive of the Judeans 745 persons; all the persons were 4,600.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20308AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20308AD\"></sup>And in the thirty-seventh year of the exile of Jehoiachin king of Judah, in the twelfth month, on the twenty-fifth day of the month, Evil-merodach king of Babylon, in the year that he began to reign, graciously freed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20308AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20308AE\"></sup>Jehoiachin king of Judah and brought him out of prison.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And he spoke kindly to him and gave him a seat above the seats of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20309AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20309AF\"></sup>the kings who were with him in Babylon.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So Jehoiachin put off his prison garments. And every day of his life he dined regularly at the king's table,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>and for his allowance, a regular allowance was given him by the king, according to his daily needs, until the day of his death, as long as he lived."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;